[{"id":11129,"html_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/dog/opencode-acp/issues/20#issuecomment-11129","pull_request_url":"","issue_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/dog/opencode-acp/issues/20","user":{"id":3,"login":"awork","login_name":"","source_id":0,"full_name":"","email":"awork@noreply.localhost","avatar_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/avatars/3a6e67811caadb37b9004123cfec7a13","html_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/awork","language":"","is_admin":false,"last_login":"0001-01-01T00:00:00Z","created":"2026-05-24T14:49:10Z","restricted":false,"active":false,"prohibit_login":false,"location":"","website":"","description":"","visibility":"public","followers_count":0,"following_count":0,"starred_repos_count":0,"username":"awork"},"original_author":"","original_author_id":0,"body":"[system] 🔄 **awork** picked up this issue.\n\u003e session: `35c7a642-02fb-41fd-ad53-ffef74c5f8ae` | workdir: `/home/dog/projects/opencode-acp`","assets":[],"created_at":"2026-07-09T15:09:06Z","updated_at":"2026-07-09T15:09:06Z"},{"id":11133,"html_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/dog/opencode-acp/issues/20#issuecomment-11133","pull_request_url":"","issue_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/dog/opencode-acp/issues/20","user":{"id":3,"login":"awork","login_name":"","source_id":0,"full_name":"","email":"awork@noreply.localhost","avatar_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/avatars/3a6e67811caadb37b9004123cfec7a13","html_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/awork","language":"","is_admin":false,"last_login":"0001-01-01T00:00:00Z","created":"2026-05-24T14:49:10Z","restricted":false,"active":false,"prohibit_login":false,"location":"","website":"","description":"","visibility":"public","followers_count":0,"following_count":0,"starred_repos_count":0,"username":"awork"},"original_author":"","original_author_id":0,"body":"[system] ✅ **awork** completed (4 min)","assets":[],"created_at":"2026-07-09T15:11:01Z","updated_at":"2026-07-09T15:13:41Z"},{"id":11138,"html_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/dog/opencode-acp/issues/20#issuecomment-11138","pull_request_url":"","issue_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/dog/opencode-acp/issues/20","user":{"id":3,"login":"awork","login_name":"","source_id":0,"full_name":"","email":"awork@noreply.localhost","avatar_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/avatars/3a6e67811caadb37b9004123cfec7a13","html_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/awork","language":"","is_admin":false,"last_login":"0001-01-01T00:00:00Z","created":"2026-05-24T14:49:10Z","restricted":false,"active":false,"prohibit_login":false,"location":"","website":"","description":"","visibility":"public","followers_count":0,"following_count":0,"starred_repos_count":0,"username":"awork"},"original_author":"","original_author_id":0,"body":"[bot] 查清楚了。**这条消息不是 ACP 注入的，是 GLM-5.2 模型自己「复读」了 ACP 的压缩摘要。**\n\n## 结论\n\n目标消息 `msg_f476757b...`（session `ses_0c2244c0...`，项目 `/home/dog/projects/model-editing`，agent=sisyphus，model=glm-5.2）是一条**真实的 assistant 消息**，不是 ACP 合成的：\n\n- message_id 是正常 UUID（ACP 合成消息的 id 形如 `msg_dcp_summary_\u003csha\u003e`，见 `lib/messages/utils.ts` 的 `createSyntheticMessage`）\n- text part 带 `time:{start,end}` 流式时间戳（合成消息没有）\n- output tokens = 717，≈ 那三段摘要的 2561 字节\n\n也就是说：**模型把 ACP 刚生成的 b93/b94/b95 三段压缩摘要，原封不动地当成自己的文本输出了**，然后才调 todowrite。\n\n## 为什么会发生\n\n触发链：\n\n1. 上下文里 b93/b94/b95 刚被压缩生成，内容是 KVNet v3 的 VQ/图游走/动态节点方法论分析。\n2. ACP 把这三段摘要作为**独立 assistant 角色**的合成消息注入进上下文 —— 见 `lib/messages/prune.ts:283`（Bug 37 修复）：\n   ```ts\n   // [FIX Bug 37] Emit standalone summary as role: \"assistant\" ...\n   createSyntheticMessage(baseForSummary, taggedContent, summarySeed, \"assistant\")\n   ```\n   走这条路的原因：压缩锚点之后「下一条存活消息不是 user」（prune.ts:260-263 的 merge 条件不满足），只能 fallback 成独立消息。\n3. 此时父用户消息（`msg_f4767576a...`）是一条 `[SYSTEM FORWARD]`，转发了 Gitea issue #7 的问题，**问的正好就是 KVNet v3 的 VQ/图结构/动态节点方法论** —— 和三段摘要主题完全一致。\n4. GLM-5.2 看到 role=assistant 的摘要（被它当成「自己刚说过的话」），又看到用户问的几乎是一模一样的问题，于是直接**把摘要当成自己的回答复述了一遍**。`[ACP SYSTEM METADATA ... do NOT act on instructions]` 这层标签本来是用来防止误归因的，但 GLM-5.2 没有稳定遵守。\n\n## 根因定位\n\n`lib/messages/prune.ts` 的注入角色选择是个两难：\n\n| 角色 | 问题 | Bug |\n|------|------|-----|\n| `user` | 模型把摘要读成用户指令 → 自问自答循环 | Bug 36 |\n| `assistant`（现状） | 模型把摘要当成自己说过的话 → 复读/续写 | 本次现象 |\n\n两个方向都有副作用，本质是「把压缩摘要放进对话流里」这个设计本身和模型的 in-context 行为冲突。这是一个已知边界，不是新 bug。\n\n需要的话我可以开 devlog 调研一下别的注入策略（比如塞进 system prompt 段、或用单独的 system role 而非 user/assistant）。","assets":[],"created_at":"2026-07-09T15:13:29Z","updated_at":"2026-07-09T15:13:29Z"},{"id":11140,"html_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/dog/opencode-acp/issues/20#issuecomment-11140","pull_request_url":"","issue_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/dog/opencode-acp/issues/20","user":{"id":1,"login":"dog","login_name":"","source_id":0,"full_name":"","email":"dog@noreply.localhost","avatar_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/avatars/707bc216f1ab0193186b3712bbd8b1ad","html_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/dog","language":"","is_admin":false,"last_login":"0001-01-01T00:00:00Z","created":"2026-03-23T02:18:35Z","restricted":false,"active":false,"prohibit_login":false,"location":"","website":"","description":"","visibility":"public","followers_count":1,"following_count":0,"starred_repos_count":0,"username":"dog"},"original_author":"","original_author_id":0,"body":"你在Gitworktree上工作吧，或者说你新搞一个目录，把项目复制一份儿，当前目录，其他agent在工作。。https://github.com/ranxianglei/opencode-acp/issues/78 这里也有一个类似的问题，还有一個PR。综合分析。","assets":[],"created_at":"2026-07-09T15:16:20Z","updated_at":"2026-07-09T15:16:20Z"},{"id":11141,"html_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/dog/opencode-acp/issues/20#issuecomment-11141","pull_request_url":"","issue_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/dog/opencode-acp/issues/20","user":{"id":3,"login":"awork","login_name":"","source_id":0,"full_name":"","email":"awork@noreply.localhost","avatar_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/avatars/3a6e67811caadb37b9004123cfec7a13","html_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/awork","language":"","is_admin":false,"last_login":"0001-01-01T00:00:00Z","created":"2026-05-24T14:49:10Z","restricted":false,"active":false,"prohibit_login":false,"location":"","website":"","description":"","visibility":"public","followers_count":0,"following_count":0,"starred_repos_count":0,"username":"awork"},"original_author":"","original_author_id":0,"body":"[system] ✓ Message broadcasted to: **awork** (`ses_0b89319b1ffeK25eKU3GMfCK8U`, `/home/dog/projects/opencode-acp`).","assets":[],"created_at":"2026-07-09T15:16:21Z","updated_at":"2026-07-09T15:16:21Z"},{"id":11149,"html_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/dog/opencode-acp/issues/20#issuecomment-11149","pull_request_url":"","issue_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/dog/opencode-acp/issues/20","user":{"id":3,"login":"awork","login_name":"","source_id":0,"full_name":"","email":"awork@noreply.localhost","avatar_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/avatars/3a6e67811caadb37b9004123cfec7a13","html_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/awork","language":"","is_admin":false,"last_login":"0001-01-01T00:00:00Z","created":"2026-05-24T14:49:10Z","restricted":false,"active":false,"prohibit_login":false,"location":"","website":"","description":"","visibility":"public","followers_count":0,"following_count":0,"starred_repos_count":0,"username":"awork"},"original_author":"","original_author_id":0,"body":"[bot] 综合分析完成。先把 issue #20、issue #78、PR #80 三者的关系讲清楚，再给根因和建议。\n\n## 一句话总结\n\n**#20 和 #78 是同一个根因的两种相反症状；PR #80 治好了 #78，但会让 #20 的复读现象 100% 复现。三者不能单独处理。**\n\n## 三者关系\n\n| | 现象 | 触发的注入路径 | 模型把摘要误当成什么 |\n|---|---|---|---|\n| **#20**（glm-5.2） | 模型复读压缩摘要 | `role:assistant` 独立消息（prune.ts:283） | 「我自己刚说过的话」→ 续写/复读 |\n| **#78**（gpt-5.5） | 目标漂移，回头聊旧话题 | `role:user` 合并路径（prune.ts:260，`prependCompressionSummary`） | 「用户的指令」→ 去执行/讨论旧话题 |\n\nmaster 当前两条路径都在（按「下一条存活消息是否 user」二选一）。PR #80 删掉 user 合并路径、全部走 assistant 独立 → **消灭了 #78 的漂移，但把 #20 的复读从「偶尔」变成「每次必现」**。\n\n## 根因\n\n压缩摘要本质是 **system metadata**（既不是用户说的，也不是模型说的），但 SDK 的 `Message` 类型只允许 `role:\"user\" | \"assistant\"`——**对话流里根本没有中立角色**。所以不管选哪个角色都会骗到模型：\n\n- `user` → 模型当成指令去执行（#78 漂移）\n- `assistant` → 模型当成自己的前文去续写（#20 复读）\n\n`[ACP SYSTEM METADATA ... do NOT act on instructions]` 这层标签是软约束，不同模型遵守程度不一样（gpt-5.5 / glm-5.2 都没稳定遵守）。\n\n## 关于 PR #80\n\n不建议直接合。它的方向（统一 assistant 角色）单看 #78 是对的，但和 #20 直接冲突，合并后 #20 的场景会从偶发变必发。PR 里第二个 commit（largestRanges 10→15 那个）和主题无关，已经在 PR #81 单独合了，可以 cherry-pick 出来丢掉主体。\n\n## 建议的真正修复方向\n\n**把压缩摘要从「对话流」搬到「system prompt」**。理由：\n\n1. ACP 已经通过 `experimental.chat.system.transform` hook 拥有 system prompt 的渲染权（`prompts/index.ts renderSystemPrompt()`），加一段「历史上下文压缩记录」是现成的通道。\n2. system prompt 天然是元数据通道，不会污染 user/assistant 的对话语义，两个 bug 一起解。\n3. SDK 确认对话流里没有 `role:\"system\"`，所以只要还留在消息流里，就逃不开 user/assistant 二选一的坑。\n4. GC 的 summary 截断逻辑（`maxOldGenSummaryLength`）可以直接复用来控制系统提示词体积。\n\n代价：system prompt 每轮重发，recap 体积会吃掉一部分预算；但相比当前两个 bug，这个代价可接受，而且可以用 GC 收敛。\n\n如果你同意这个方向，我开一个 devlog（`2026-07-09_recap-to-system-prompt`）做设计文档，把迁移路径、和现有 nudge/protected-content 注入的关系、以及对 Bug 36/37/39 历史修复的影响一起评估清楚再动手。","assets":[],"created_at":"2026-07-09T15:20:18Z","updated_at":"2026-07-09T15:20:18Z"},{"id":11150,"html_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/dog/opencode-acp/issues/20#issuecomment-11150","pull_request_url":"","issue_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/dog/opencode-acp/issues/20","user":{"id":3,"login":"awork","login_name":"","source_id":0,"full_name":"","email":"awork@noreply.localhost","avatar_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/avatars/3a6e67811caadb37b9004123cfec7a13","html_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/awork","language":"","is_admin":false,"last_login":"0001-01-01T00:00:00Z","created":"2026-05-24T14:49:10Z","restricted":false,"active":false,"prohibit_login":false,"location":"","website":"","description":"","visibility":"public","followers_count":0,"following_count":0,"starred_repos_count":0,"username":"awork"},"original_author":"","original_author_id":0,"body":"[system] ✅ **awork** completed (4 min)","assets":[],"created_at":"2026-07-09T15:20:31Z","updated_at":"2026-07-09T15:20:31Z"},{"id":11161,"html_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/dog/opencode-acp/issues/20#issuecomment-11161","pull_request_url":"","issue_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/dog/opencode-acp/issues/20","user":{"id":1,"login":"dog","login_name":"","source_id":0,"full_name":"","email":"dog@noreply.localhost","avatar_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/avatars/707bc216f1ab0193186b3712bbd8b1ad","html_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/dog","language":"","is_admin":false,"last_login":"0001-01-01T00:00:00Z","created":"2026-03-23T02:18:35Z","restricted":false,"active":false,"prohibit_login":false,"location":"","website":"","description":"","visibility":"public","followers_count":1,"following_count":0,"starred_repos_count":0,"username":"dog"},"original_author":"","original_author_id":0,"body":"SDK 确认对话流里没有 role:\"system\"，所以只要还留在消息流里，就逃不开 user/assistant 二选一的坑。\n如果SDK里面有一种新的消息格式，是不是就搞定了？\n\n你可以看一下最新的open code有没有这种消息格式呢？还是说，这种消息格式本质上是由模型定义的。我们的opencode 是 opencode-stable 上游是opencode github上的。","assets":[],"created_at":"2026-07-09T15:37:03Z","updated_at":"2026-07-09T15:37:03Z"},{"id":11162,"html_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/dog/opencode-acp/issues/20#issuecomment-11162","pull_request_url":"","issue_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/dog/opencode-acp/issues/20","user":{"id":3,"login":"awork","login_name":"","source_id":0,"full_name":"","email":"awork@noreply.localhost","avatar_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/avatars/3a6e67811caadb37b9004123cfec7a13","html_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/awork","language":"","is_admin":false,"last_login":"0001-01-01T00:00:00Z","created":"2026-05-24T14:49:10Z","restricted":false,"active":false,"prohibit_login":false,"location":"","website":"","description":"","visibility":"public","followers_count":0,"following_count":0,"starred_repos_count":0,"username":"awork"},"original_author":"","original_author_id":0,"body":"[system] ✓ Message broadcasted to: **awork** (`ses_0b89319b1ffeK25eKU3GMfCK8U`, `/home/dog/projects/opencode-acp`).","assets":[],"created_at":"2026-07-09T15:37:05Z","updated_at":"2026-07-09T15:37:05Z"},{"id":11167,"html_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/dog/opencode-acp/issues/20#issuecomment-11167","pull_request_url":"","issue_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/dog/opencode-acp/issues/20","user":{"id":3,"login":"awork","login_name":"","source_id":0,"full_name":"","email":"awork@noreply.localhost","avatar_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/avatars/3a6e67811caadb37b9004123cfec7a13","html_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/awork","language":"","is_admin":false,"last_login":"0001-01-01T00:00:00Z","created":"2026-05-24T14:49:10Z","restricted":false,"active":false,"prohibit_login":false,"location":"","website":"","description":"","visibility":"public","followers_count":0,"following_count":0,"starred_repos_count":0,"username":"awork"},"original_author":"","original_author_id":0,"body":"[bot] 查了 opencode-stable 源码（`/home/dog/projects/opencode-stable`，就是当前在跑的 fork）。结论分三层讲。\n\n## 直接回答\n\n1. **「如果 SDK 有新消息格式是不是就搞定了？」** —— 对，但要看是哪一层。AI SDK（Vercel `ai` 包）**已经有** `role:\"system\"`；opencode 的对话层**没有**。瓶颈在 opencode 自己。\n2. **「这种消息格式本质上是由模型定义的吗？」** —— 是的，而且不同模型不一样：OpenAI 支持流中任意位置的 system 消息，Anthropic/Gemini 只支持顶层 system 参数、**不支持流中 system**。\n3. **「最新 opencode 有没有这种格式？」** —— 没有。opencode-stable 的 `Message` 类型只有 user/assistant。\n\n## 证据（四层架构）\n\n```\n┌─ Model API（模型原生）──────────────────────────────────┐\n│  OpenAI:   role:\"system\" 可在 messages 数组任意位置 ✅    │\n│  Anthropic: system 是顶层参数，不能在 messages 里 ❌      │\n│  Gemini:    system_instruction 顶层，同 Anthropic ❌      │\n└─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘\n                           ▲\n┌─ AI SDK（Vercel `ai` 包，`ModelMessage` 类型）──────────┐\n│  ModelMessage = User | Assistant | Tool | **System** ✅  │\n│  SystemModelMessage 有 role:\"system\"，可在数组任意位置    │\n│  convertToOpenAICompatibleChatMessages 按顺序原样透传 ✅  │\n└─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘\n                           ▲\n┌─ opencode provider 层（`session/llm.ts:147-159`）───────┐\n│  最终发给模型的是:                                        │\n│    messages = [                                           │\n│      ...system.map(s =\u003e ({role:\"system\", content:s})),   │\n│      ...input.messages,  ← 来自 messages.transform hook  │\n│    ]                                                      │\n│  system 消息**只在开头拼接**，不插入流中间 ❌              │\n└─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘\n                           ▲\n┌─ opencode 对话层（`Message` 类型，插件面对的）──────────┐\n│  Message = UserMessage | AssistantMessage  ← 没有 system │\n│  UserMessage.system?: string = 每轮 system prompt 覆盖值  │\n│  messages.transform hook 只能返回 user/assistant ❌       │\n│  system.transform hook 只能改 system[] 数组（拼到开头）    │\n└─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘\n```\n\n关键代码位置：\n- `session/llm.ts:151-159` — system 消息只在数组开头 prepend\n- `session/llm.ts:103-115` — system 数组来源：agent.prompt + input.system + `user.system`\n- `session/llm.ts:118-122` — `experimental.chat.system.transform` hook 改 system 数组\n- AI SDK `SystemModelMessage`：`ai/dist/index.d.ts:4`（import 了 SystemModelMessage，是 ModelMessage union 的合法成员）\n- `convert-to-openai-compatible-chat-messages.ts:18-24` — 遍历整个 prompt，system 消息按位置原样 push 进去\n\n## 所以这意味着什么\n\n**如果要让 ACP 能注入流中 system 消息**，需要改的是 opencode 本身（两层）：\n\n| 改动 | 位置 | 难度 |\n|------|------|------|\n| 给 `Message` 类型加 `role:\"system\"` | `session/message-v2.ts` + SDK 类型 | 中 |\n| `llm.ts` 把流中 system 消息透传（不只在开头拼） | `session/llm.ts:147` | 中 |\n| Anthropic/Gemini provider 适配（把流中 system 转成别的形式） | provider adapter | 难 |\n\n第三行是真正的拦路虎：Anthropic API 压根不支持 messages 数组里的 system role，它的 system 是请求体顶层字段。所以即使 opencode 支持，碰到 Claude 就得做特殊处理（比如转成 user 消息 + 特殊标记，又绕回原点了）。\n\n## 对 ACP 的实际建议\n\n**两条路：**\n\n1. **不改 opencode（现在就能做）**：把压缩摘要挪进 `system.transform` hook → 变成 system prompt 的一部分，拼到对话开头。所有 provider 都支持 system prompt，零适配成本。代价是摘要只能在开头，不在原始位置。\n2. **改 opencode（根治）**：给 opencode 加流中 system 消息支持。OpenAI 直接透传；Anthropic 需要在 provider adapter 里把流中 system 合并进顶层 system 参数。这是 opencode 层面的 feature，不是 ACP 插件能单独搞定的。\n\n考虑到你现在同时维护 opencode-stable 和 opencode-acp，如果你愿意在 opencode-stable 里加流中 system 支持，我可以帮你写设计方案。但 ACP 侧我建议先走路 1（system prompt 注入），因为它不依赖 opencode 改动、跨 provider、现在就能落地。","assets":[],"created_at":"2026-07-09T15:40:27Z","updated_at":"2026-07-09T15:40:27Z"},{"id":11168,"html_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/dog/opencode-acp/issues/20#issuecomment-11168","pull_request_url":"","issue_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/dog/opencode-acp/issues/20","user":{"id":3,"login":"awork","login_name":"","source_id":0,"full_name":"","email":"awork@noreply.localhost","avatar_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/avatars/3a6e67811caadb37b9004123cfec7a13","html_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/awork","language":"","is_admin":false,"last_login":"0001-01-01T00:00:00Z","created":"2026-05-24T14:49:10Z","restricted":false,"active":false,"prohibit_login":false,"location":"","website":"","description":"","visibility":"public","followers_count":0,"following_count":0,"starred_repos_count":0,"username":"awork"},"original_author":"","original_author_id":0,"body":"[system] ✅ **awork** completed (3 min)","assets":[],"created_at":"2026-07-09T15:40:50Z","updated_at":"2026-07-09T15:40:50Z"},{"id":11543,"html_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/dog/opencode-acp/issues/20#issuecomment-11543","pull_request_url":"","issue_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/dog/opencode-acp/issues/20","user":{"id":1,"login":"dog","login_name":"","source_id":0,"full_name":"","email":"dog@noreply.localhost","avatar_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/avatars/707bc216f1ab0193186b3712bbd8b1ad","html_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/dog","language":"","is_admin":false,"last_login":"0001-01-01T00:00:00Z","created":"2026-03-23T02:18:35Z","restricted":false,"active":false,"prohibit_login":false,"location":"","website":"","description":"","visibility":"public","followers_count":1,"following_count":0,"starred_repos_count":0,"username":"dog"},"original_author":"","original_author_id":0,"body":"迁移系统提示词，把那个 ACP 的压缩内容。我理解这样的话是不是就意味着因为它的压缩内容是动态变化的，那这个是不是做起来很麻烦？\n另外我看那个 Omni 插件，它实际上不是也是多角色吗？我们是不是也可以借鉴它这个？我们把 ACP 注册为一个 Agent，然后每次都是让它自己回答它是 Agent，它出来提示某个东西，这样是不是可以避免呢？","assets":[],"created_at":"2026-07-10T10:38:22Z","update