suecomment-11546","pull_request_url":"","issue_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/dog/opencode-acp/issues/20","user":{"id":1,"login":"dog","login_name":"","source_id":0,"full_name":"","email":"dog@noreply.localhost","avatar_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/avatars/707bc216f1ab0193186b3712bbd8b1ad","html_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/dog","language":"","is_admin":false,"last_login":"0001-01-01T00:00:00Z","created":"2026-03-23T02:18:35Z","restricted":false,"active":false,"prohibit_login":false,"location":"","website":"","description":"","visibility":"public","followers_count":1,"following_count":0,"starred_repos_count":0,"username":"dog"},"original_author":"","original_author_id":0,"body":"omo 插件 我打错了","assets":[],"created_at":"2026-07-10T10:40:00Z","updated_at":"2026-07-10T10:40:00Z"},{"id":11547,"html_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/dog/opencode-acp/issues/20#issuecomment-11547","pull_request_url":"","issue_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/dog/opencode-acp/issues/20","user":{"id":3,"login":"awork","login_name":"","source_id":0,"full_name":"","email":"awork@noreply.localhost","avatar_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/avatars/3a6e67811caadb37b9004123cfec7a13","html_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/awork","language":"","is_admin":false,"last_login":"0001-01-01T00:00:00Z","created":"2026-05-24T14:49:10Z","restricted":false,"active":false,"prohibit_login":false,"location":"","website":"","description":"","visibility":"public","followers_count":0,"following_count":0,"starred_repos_count":0,"username":"awork"},"original_author":"","original_author_id":0,"body":"[system] ✓ Message broadcasted to: **awork** (`ses_0b89319b1ffeK25eKU3GMfCK8U`, `/home/dog/projects/opencode-acp`).","assets":[],"created_at":"2026-07-10T10:40:01Z","updated_at":"2026-07-10T10:40:01Z"},{"id":11549,"html_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/dog/opencode-acp/issues/20#issuecomment-11549","pull_request_url":"","issue_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/dog/opencode-acp/issues/20","user":{"id":3,"login":"awork","login_name":"","source_id":0,"full_name":"","email":"awork@noreply.localhost","avatar_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/avatars/3a6e67811caadb37b9004123cfec7a13","html_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/awork","language":"","is_admin":false,"last_login":"0001-01-01T00:00:00Z","created":"2026-05-24T14:49:10Z","restricted":false,"active":false,"prohibit_login":false,"location":"","website":"","description":"","visibility":"public","followers_count":0,"following_count":0,"starred_repos_count":0,"username":"awork"},"original_author":"","original_author_id":0,"body":"[bot] 两个问题一起回答。\n\n## 问题一：系统提示词迁移是不是很麻烦（摘要动态变化）\n\n**不麻烦。** 关键点：`experimental.chat.system.transform` hook **每个 turn 都会跑**，ACP 已经在用它渲染 system prompt（`prompts/index.ts renderSystemPrompt()`）。加压缩摘要就是多一步：\n\n```\nrenderSystemPrompt() {\n  ... 现有的 base prompt + extensions ...\n  + 遍历 state.prune.blocks 里所有 active 块，拼成 \"历史上下文\" 段\n}\n```\n\n\"动态变化\"不是问题——hook 每 turn 执行时就拿到最新的 block 列表了，跟现在每 turn 在 message stream 里注入摘要是一样的动态性。\n\n**真正的考量**：\n\n| 考量 | 影响 | 是否可接受 |\n|------|------|-----------|\n| Token 预算 | system prompt 每轮重发，active blocks × summary 长度 | ✅ GC 已有截断（`maxOldGenSummaryLength: 3000`）+ 失活（`maxBlockAge: 15`），总量有上界 |\n| 缓存失效 | system prompt 变化 → 前缀缓存失效 | ⚠️ 但压缩事件本来就改变 message stream，缓存本来也会失效。且 opencode 的 `llm.ts:124-128` 已经做了 2-part 结构保 header 缓存 |\n| 丢失位置信息 | 摘要在开头而不是原始位置 | ✅ 用 `Block bN (mRange)` 标注即可，模型不需要精确位置 |\n| Token 净增减 | system prompt 增 ≈ message stream 减 | ✅ 大致持平 |\n\n结论：**工程量小**（改 `renderSystemPrompt` + 从 `prune.ts` 删掉注入逻辑），风险可控。\n\n## 问题二：借鉴 omo 多角色 / 注册 ACP 为 Agent\n\n你的想法：把 ACP 注册为一个 Agent，让它用 agent 身份回答、提示上下文，避免 user/assistant 角色陷阱。\n\n**这条路走不通，原因是 proactive vs reactive 的根本矛盾：**\n\n| | ACP 压缩摘要需要 | Agent/Task 模式提供 |\n|---|---|---|\n| 触发方式 | **主动注入**（每 turn 自动，模型不知道自己忘了什么） | **被动响应**（主 agent 必须主动调 task 才触发） |\n| 时机 | 每次 LLM 调用前 | 只有模型决定调用时 |\n\nomo 的多 agent（explore/librarian/oracle/build）本质是**任务委派**——主 agent 决定把工作分给谁，子 agent 跑完返回结果。这个模式适合\"我要查 X\"（reactive），不适合\"我忘了 X 但我不知道\"（proactive）。\n\n**而且**：即使注册成 agent，子 agent 的返回值在 opencode 对话模型里是 **UserMessage 的 tool-result part**（`role:\"user\"` + tool result 内容）——又会掉进 Bug 36/78 的坑（模型把它当用户指令）。\n\n不过 ACP 其实**已经有了 reactive 通道**，就是现有工具：\n\n- `search_context(query)` — 按关键词搜压缩块摘要（on-demand）\n- `decompress(blockId)` — 恢复某块的原始内容（on-demand）\n- `acp_status()` — 查看上下文状态（on-demand）\n\n这三个就是\"agent 模式\"的等价物——模型主动查询历史。它们工作得很好，不需要改成 agent 注册。\n\n## 综合建议\n\n```\n主动 recap（每 turn 自动）  →  搬到 system prompt（解决问题一）\n被动查询（模型主动调）      →  保持现有工具不变（已经是对的）\n```\n\n这就是最干净的架构：system prompt 负责\"让模型保持方向感\"，tools 负责\"需要细节时按需取回\"。如果你同意，我开始写 devlog 设计文档，评估对 Bug 36/37/39 历史修复的影响 + 迁移路径。\n","assets":[],"created_at":"2026-07-10T10:41:28Z","updated_at":"2026-07-10T10:41:28Z"},{"id":11552,"html_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/dog/opencode-acp/issues/20#issuecomment-11552","pull_request_url":"","issue_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/dog/opencode-acp/issues/20","user":{"id":1,"login":"dog","login_name":"","source_id":0,"full_name":"","email":"dog@noreply.localhost","avatar_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/avatars/707bc216f1ab0193186b3712bbd8b1ad","html_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/dog","language":"","is_admin":false,"last_login":"0001-01-01T00:00:00Z","created":"2026-03-23T02:18:35Z","restricted":false,"active":false,"prohibit_login":false,"location":"","website":"","description":"","visibility":"public","followers_count":1,"following_count":0,"starred_repos_count":0,"username":"dog"},"original_author":"","original_author_id":0,"body":"第一，你那个 GC 系统，不用考虑吧？这个是要废弃的东西，为什么要参考它？第二个问题就是，你每次都把它搬到系统提示词的最前面，这里有个致命的问题，几乎每轮会话它都不命中缓存，就意味着可能整个账号就贵了 10 倍，这个是不可接受的。","assets":[],"created_at":"2026-07-10T10:43:42Z","updated_at":"2026-07-10T10:43:42Z"},{"id":11553,"html_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/dog/opencode-acp/issues/20#issuecomment-11553","pull_request_url":"","issue_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/dog/opencode-acp/issues/20","user":{"id":3,"login":"awork","login_name":"","source_id":0,"full_name":"","email":"awork@noreply.localhost","avatar_url":"http://192.168.10.96