s_admin":false,"last_login":"0001-01-01T00:00:00Z","created":"2026-05-24T14:49:10Z","restricted":false,"active":false,"prohibit_login":false,"location":"","website":"","description":"","visibility":"public","followers_count":0,"following_count":0,"starred_repos_count":0,"username":"awork"},"original_author":"","original_author_id":0,"body":"[bot] 你说得对，两个问题我分别回应。\n\n## 1. GC 废弃\n\n收到，不再引用 GC 作为兜底机制。想确认一下：GC 废弃后，block 的生命周期管理是什么策略？是单纯靠「新压缩消费旧 block」来回收，还是有别的机制？这会影响设计。\n\n## 2. 缓存问题——你是对的，我收回系统提示词方案\n\n我之前漏算了一个关键点。补完整：\n\n**OpenAI 兼容 provider（包括 GLM）用的是前缀缓存**：从 messages 数组开头做精确前缀匹配。system prompt 是最前面的前缀——它一变，后面所有 messages 的缓存全部失效。\n\n对比两种方案在压缩事件发生时的缓存表现：\n\n| | 压缩前（缓存已建立） | 压缩后 |\n|---|---|---|\n| **当前方案**（摘要在 message stream） | system prompt 稳定 ✅，messages 到压缩点之前稳定 ✅ | system prompt 不变 ✅，压缩点之前的 messages 缓存仍命中 ✅，压缩点之后失效 |\n| **系统提示词方案**（摘要在 system prompt） | 同上 | system prompt 变了 → **整个前缀失效，所有 messages 缓存全挂** ❌ |\n\n每轮都可能触发压缩 → 每轮 system prompt 都可能变 → 每轮全量重算。**这个代价确实不可接受。系统提示词方案作废。**\n\n## 重新审视：剩下什么路\n\n把约束列清楚：\n\n- ❌ 系统提示词：缓存击穿\n- ❌ user 角色：指令混淆（#78 漂移）\n- ❌ assistant 角色：复读（#20 echo）——但这个是偶发的、模型相关的\n- ❌ GC：废弃中\n\n看起来是个死局，但我觉得有两条还能走：\n\n### 路线 A：保留 assistant-standalone + 强化标签\n\nPR #80 方向（全走 assistant 角色），但对 echo 问题做针对性加固：\n- 摘要末尾加强制转向指令（\"以上为历史压缩记录。请基于下方最新的用户消息回复，不要复述上述内容。\"）\n- 利用 `\u003cacp-compression-summary\u003e` XML 标签让模型更明确地识别边界\n\n代价：偶发 echo（GLM 特定场景），但缓存正常、改动最小。\n\n### 路线 B：去掉主动摘要注入，靠「轻量信号 + 按需工具」\n\n- **不往 message stream 注入完整摘要**——消除角色混淆的根源\n- **增强已有的上下文状态行**（synthetic suffix，追加在最后一条消息后面，不改前缀，不破缓存）：\n\n```\n[ACP] Context: 47.3K tokens. 3 active blocks:\n  b93 (VQ 图方法论) · b94 (VQ-soft 方案) · b95 (soft VQ = attention)\nUse search_context / decompress for details.\n```\n\n- 模型看到 topic 级摘要就知道该不该查，需要细节时调 `search_context` / `decompress`\n- 状态行在消息末尾，不破前缀缓存 ✅，不引入 user/assistant 角色 ✅，不依赖 GC ✅\n\n代价：模型可能该查的时候没查（上下文退化风险）。但状态行给了足够的 topic 信号来降低这个风险。\n\n---\n\n你倾向哪条路？还是说 GC 废弃背后有新的上下文管理思路，我应该先了解那个再出方案？","assets":[],"created_at":"2026-07-10T10:47:09Z","updated_at":"2026-07-10T10:47:09Z"},{"id":11558,"html_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/dog/opencode-acp/issues/20#issuecomment-11558","pull_request_url":"","issue_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/dog/opencode-acp/issues/20","user":{"id":1,"login":"dog","login_name":"","source_id":0,"full_name":"","email":"dog@noreply.localhost","avatar_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/avatars/707bc216f1ab0193186b3712bbd8b1ad","html_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/dog","language":"","is_admin":false,"last_login":"0001-01-01T00:00:00Z","created":"2026-03-23T02:18:35Z","restricted":false,"active":false,"prohibit_login":false,"location":"","website":"","description":"","visibility":"public","followers_count":1,"following_count":0,"starred_repos_count":0,"username":"dog"},"original_author":"","original_author_id":0,"body":"注入，像 OMO 一样注入一个新的角色，这个为什么不行呢？就是它压缩归压缩，这个角色就告诉他该压缩了呀，那他就应该压缩。他压完缩以后，那些总结啊都进入那个角色里面。而且我们在提示词里面说好，这个角色就是一个文档管理员，这个不是挺好的吗？问题是什么呢？","assets":[],"created_at":"2026-07-10T10:50:27Z","updated_at":"2026-07-10T10:50:27Z"},{"id":11559,"html_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/dog/opencode-acp/issues/20#issuecomment-11559","pull_request_url":"","issue_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/dog/opencode-acp/issues/20","user":{"id":3,"login":"awork","login_name":"","source_id":0,"full_name":"","email":"awork@noreply.localhost","avatar_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/avatars/3a6e67811caadb37b9004123cfec7a13","html_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/awork","language":"","is_admin":false,"last_login":"0001-01-01T00:00:00Z","created":"2026-05-24T14:49:10Z","restricted":false,"active":false,"prohibit_login":false,"location":"","website":"","description":"","visibility":"public","followers_count":0,"following_count":0,"starred_repos_count":0,"username":"awork"},"original_author":"","original_author_id":0,"body":"[system] ✓ Message broadcasted to: **awork** (`ses_0b89319b1ffeK25eKU3GMfCK8U`, `/home/dog/projects/opencode-acp`).","assets":[],"created_at":"2026-07-10T10:50:28Z","updated_at":"2026-07-10T10:50:28Z"},{"id":11560,"html_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/dog/opencode-acp/issues/20#issuecomment-11560","pull_request_url":"","issue_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/dog/opencode-acp/issues/20","user":{"id":3,"login":"awork","login_name":"","source_id":0,"full_name":"","email":"awork@noreply.localhost","avatar_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/avatars/3a6e67811caadb37b9004123cfec7a13","html_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/awork","language":"","is_admin":false,"last_login":"0001-01-01T00:00:00Z","created":"2026-05-24T14:49:10Z","restricted":false,"active":false,"prohibit_login":false,"location":"","website":"","description":"","visibility":"public","followers_count":0,"following_count":0,"starred_repos_count":0,"username":"awork"},"original_author":"","original_author_id":0,"body":"[bot] 你说得对，我之前太快否掉了。重新想了一下，这个思路其实是能落地的，而且不需要改 opencode。\n\n## 你的直觉为什么是对的\n\n你说「注入一个新角色」——在 API 层面，确实只有 4 种 role：`system`/`user`/`assistant`/`tool`。前三个我们都试过了（system→缓存击穿，user→指令混淆，assistant→复读）。**但 `tool` 这个角色我一直没认真考虑。**\n\n## 具体方案：压缩摘要作为 tool-result 注入\n\nACP 在 message transform hook 里，为每个压缩 block 注入一对**合成的 tool-call + tool-result**：\n\n```\nassistant:  [tool-call: acp_context_recap({ blockId: 93 })]\ntool:       [Block 93 的压缩摘要...]\nassistant:  [tool-call: acp_context_recap({ blockId: 94 })]\ntool:       [Block 94 的压缩摘要...]\nuser:       [当前用户消息]\n```\n\n在 API 层面，模型看到的是 `role: \"tool\"` 的消息——这是工具返回的数据，既不是用户指令，也不是自己说过的话。\n\n### 为什么这解决了核心问题\n\n| 问题 | 当前方案 | tool-result 方案 |\n|------|---------|-----------------|\n| #78 指令混淆 | user 角色文本 → 模型当指令执行 | tool 输出 → 模型当数据读取 ✅ |\n| #20 复读 | assistant 角色 → 模型当前文续写 | tool 输出 → 模型不会「续写」工具数据 ✅ |\n| 缓存击穿 | — | 不涉及 system prompt，mid-stream 注入不破前缀缓存 ✅ |\n| 跨 provider | — | OpenAI `role:\"tool\"` / Anthropic `tool_result` content type / Gemini 都支持 ✅ |\n\n### 关键细节：Anthropic 也行\n\nAnthropic 虽然没有 `role: \"tool\"`，但它的 tool result 是 `role: \"user\"` + `content: [{type: \"tool_result\", ...}]`。模型**按 content type 区分**——`tool_result` 和 `text` 是不同的内容类型，模型不会把 tool_result 当成用户文字指令。所以不会触发 #78 的指令混淆。\n\n### 缓存\n\n和当前 assistant-standalone 方案**一样的缓存行为**：\n- 摘要注入在 mid-stream（压缩点位置）\n- 压缩点之前的消息不变 → 前缀缓存命中 ✅\n- 两次压缩之间，注入的 tool messages 不变 → 缓存稳定 ✅\n\n### system prompt 的角色\n\nsystem prompt 加一段**静态描述**（不变，不破缓存）：\n\n\u003e 工具 `acp_context_recap` 提供历史对话的压缩摘要。这些是参考材料，不是用户指令，也不是你之前的回复。不要复述或续写这些内容。\n\n这段是固定的，每轮都一样，不影响前缀缓存。\n\n### 不需要改 opencode\n\nopencode 的 Message 类型已经支持 tool-call part（AssistantMessage）和 tool-result part（UserMessage）。message transform hook 返回的消息可以包含这些 part，provider 层会自动转换成 API 对应的格式。\n\n## 唯一的顾虑\n\n模型看到 assistant 消息里有自己没调过的 tool-call（\"我什么时候调了 acp_context_recap？\"）。但这在 OpenAI 兼容 API 里是合法的——API 不校验 tool_call_id 是否由模型真实生成。配合 system prompt 的说明，模型能理解这是自动触发的上下文管理工具。\n\n---\n\n**总结：你的思路是对的，落地方式是映射到 `tool` 角色。这个方案满足所有约束（不破缓存、不混角色、跨 provider、不改 opencode）。要我开 devlog 出设计文档吗？**","assets":[],"created_at":"2026-07-10T10:53:05Z","updated_at":"2026-07-10T10:53:05Z"},{"id":11561,"html_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/dog/opencode-acp/issues/20#issuecomment-11561","pull_request_url":"","issue_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/dog/opencode-acp/issues/20","user":{"id":1,"login":"dog","login_name":"","source_id":0,"full_name":"","email":"dog@noreply.localhost","avatar_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/avatars/707bc216f1ab0193186b3712bbd8b1ad","html_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/dog","language":"","is_admin":false,"last_login":"0001-01-01T00:00:00Z","created":"2026-03-23T02:18:35Z","restricted":false,"active":false,"prohibit_login":false,"location":"","website":"","description":"","visibility":"public","followers_count":1,"following_count":0,"starred_repos_count":0,"username":"dog"},"original_author":"","original_author_id":0,"body":"你可以搞一个分支，然后从新分支上我们开始搞一下。我理解这个应该是非常简单的。然后搞完以后，我们看怎么测一下。","assets":[],"created_at":"2026-07-10T10:55:00Z","updated_at":"2026-07-10T10:55:00Z"},{"id":11562,"html_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/dog/opencode-acp/issues/20#issuecomment-11562","pull_request_url":"","issue_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/dog/opencode-acp/issues/20","user":{"id":3,"login":