tive blocks。\n\n### 从模型视角的体验\n\n我现在看到的压缩块是这样的：\n```\nacp_context_recap(blockId=5): [Compressed conversation section]\n## Tool-result recap implementation (complete) ...\n```\n\n而不是之前的：\n```\n[ACP SYSTEM METADATA — recap of compressed conversation (block 5)...]\n```\n\ntool-result 的语义是「工具返回的数据」，不是我自己的前文，也不是用户指令。这样就不会出现 #20 的复读和 #78 的漂移。\n\n---\n\n下一步建议：\n1. 继续在实战中观察——多压缩几次，看 echo/drift 是否消失\n2. 如果效果好，我来创建 PR 到 master\n3. PR #80 可以关掉（它的方向被我们的方案取代了）","assets":[],"created_at":"2026-07-10T11:30:37Z","updated_at":"2026-07-10T11:30:37Z"},{"id":11618,"html_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/dog/opencode-acp/issues/20#issuecomment-11618","pull_request_url":"","issue_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/dog/opencode-acp/issues/20","user":{"id":1,"login":"dog","login_name":"","source_id":0,"full_name":"","email":"dog@noreply.localhost","avatar_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/avatars/707bc216f1ab0193186b3712bbd8b1ad","html_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/dog","language":"","is_admin":false,"last_login":"0001-01-01T00:00:00Z","created":"2026-03-23T02:18:35Z","restricted":false,"active":false,"prohibit_login":false,"location":"","website":"","description":"","visibility":"public","followers_count":1,"following_count":0,"starred_repos_count":0,"username":"dog"},"original_author":"","original_author_id":0,"body":"你部署的时候有没有看那个 agents 点 md 的规范呢？按照那个部署，否则你根本就部署不上去。","assets":[],"created_at":"2026-07-10T11:30:51Z","updated_at":"2026-07-10T11:30:51Z"},{"id":11619,"html_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/dog/opencode-acp/issues/20#issuecomment-11619","pull_request_url":"","issue_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/dog/opencode-acp/issues/20","user":{"id":3,"login":"awork","login_name":"","source_id":0,"full_name":"","email":"awork@noreply.localhost","avatar_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/avatars/3a6e67811caadb37b9004123cfec7a13","html_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/awork","language":"","is_admin":false,"last_login":"0001-01-01T00:00:00Z","created":"2026-05-24T14:49:10Z","restricted":false,"active":fa