_HEADER` + `MERGED_SUMMARY_FOOTER` 是旧 user-merge 路径（Bug 36）的残留死代码，prune.ts 已经不调了。\n\n刚提交了 commit `e3ec10f`，从 `lib/messages/utils.ts` 删掉了：\n- `MERGED_SUMMARY_HEADER`（`[ACP SYSTEM METADATA — recap...]`）\n- `MERGED_SUMMARY_FOOTER`（`\\n\\n\\n`）\n- `prependCompressionSummary()` 整个函数\n\n验证 bundle：\n```\ngrep -c 'ACP SYSTEM METADATA' dist/index.js  → 0 ✅\ngrep -c 'MERGED_SUMMARY'      dist/index.js  → 0 ✅\ngrep -c 'acp_context_recap'   dist/index.js  → 2 ✅\n```\n\n## 3. \"压缩摘要上，前缀后缀都给加上了\"\n\n**没有了。** `createSyntheticToolRecap` 把 summary 原文直接放进 `state.output`，不加任何 header/footer。之前 debug log 里看到的 output 就是纯 summary 内容：\n\n```\n\"output\": \"[Compressed conversation section]\\nLoaded awork + gitea skills...\"\n```\n\n`[Compressed conversation section]` 是我（模型）写 compress 时自己加的标题，不是 ACP 代码注入的前缀。\n\n---\n\n已用 `dev-deploy.sh` 重新部署。重启 opencode 后生效。","assets":[],"created_at":"2026-07-10T11:37:35Z","updated_at":"2026-07-10T11:37:35Z"},{"id":11625,"html_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/dog/opencode-acp/issues/20#issuecomment-11625","pull_request_url":"","issue_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/dog/opencode-acp/issues/20","user":{"id":3,"login":"awork","login_name":"","source_id":0,"full_name":"","email":"awork@noreply.localhost","avatar_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/avatars/3a6e67811caadb37b9004123cfec7a13","html_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/awork","language":"","is_admin":false,"last_login":"0001-01-01T00:00:00Z","created":"2026-05-24T14:49:10Z","restricted":false,"active":false,"prohibit_login":false,"location":"","website":"","description":"","visibility":"public","followers_count":0,"following_count":0,"starred_repos_count":0,"username":"awork"},"original_author":"","original_author_id":0,"body":"[system] ✅ **awork** completed (4 min)","assets":[],"created_at":"2026-07-10T11:37:36Z","updated_at":"2026-07-10T11:37:44Z"},{"id":11626,"html_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/dog/opencode-acp/issues/20#issuecomment-11626","pull_request_url":"","issue_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/dog