omment-11632","pull_request_url":"","issue_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/dog/opencode-acp/issues/20","user":{"id":3,"login":"awork","login_name":"","source_id":0,"full_name":"","email":"awork@noreply.localhost","avatar_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/avatars/3a6e67811caadb37b9004123cfec7a13","html_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/awork","language":"","is_admin":false,"last_login":"0001-01-01T00:00:00Z","created":"2026-05-24T14:49:10Z","restricted":false,"active":false,"prohibit_login":false,"location":"","website":"","description":"","visibility":"public","followers_count":0,"following_count":0,"starred_repos_count":0,"username":"awork"},"original_author":"","original_author_id":0,"body":"[bot] 三个问题逐个回答。\n\n## 1. 先删的 `[ACP SYSTEM METADATA]` 是否正确？有没有影响？\n\n**删对了，没有影响。** `MERGED_SUMMARY_HEADER`（`[ACP SYSTEM METADATA — recap...]`）和 `prependCompressionSummary()` 是旧 user-merge 路径（Bug 36）的代码——把摘要前缀到 user 消息的文本里。prune.ts 已经不调这个函数了（全走 `createSyntheticToolRecap`），所以它是纯死代码。删除不影响任何运行时行为。\n\n## 2. 模型能不能看到 tool-result recap？会不会当成历史消息？\n\n**能看到，且语义正确。** 我现在（作为模型）在上下文里看到的压缩块长这样：\n\n```\n\u003cfunction_results\u003e\n\u003cresult\u003e\n\u003cname\u003eacp_context_recap\u003c/name\u003e\n\u003coutput\u003e[Compressed conversation section]\n## Tool-result recap implementation (complete) ...\n\u003c/output\u003e\n\u003c/result\u003e\n```\n\n这是 **tool output** 格式——和 `bash`、`read` 等工具返回的结果一样的语义。我把它理解为「一个叫 acp_context_recap 的工具返回了历史压缩记录」，不会当成：\n- 用户指令（不是 user 消息）✅\n- 自己的前文（不是 assistant 文本）✅\n\n从模型视角，它就是工具返回的参考数据，和历史消息有明确的语义区分。\n\n## 3. 重启后老的 block 兼容吗？\n\n**完全兼容。** debug log 证明了：\n\n```\nTool-result recaps (new format):\n  b1 (m00002–m00003)   ← 旧代码创建的\n  b2 (m00004–m00010)   ← 旧代码创建的\n  b3 (m00018–m00029)   ← 旧代码创建的\n  b4 (m00063–m00077)   ← 旧代码创建的\n  b5 (m00079–m00145)   ← 新代码创建的\n```\n\n**全部 5 个 block 都以 tool-result 格式注入**，不分新旧。\n\n原因：block 在 state 里只存 summary 文本 + 元数据（blockId、range、anchor 等）。注入格式完全由 message transform hook 的代码决定，**每 turn 重新生成**。所以重启加载新代码后，所有 block（不管什么时候创建的）都自动切到新格式。\n\n不存在「老的不变、新的变」的问题——注入是运行时的、每 turn 重做的、不持久化的。\n\n\u003e 注：debug log 里有 16 个包含 \"ACP SYSTEM METADATA\" 的文本，但那些是我之前的回复正文（讨论这个格式时写的分析内容），不是注入的 header。\n\n---\n\n总结：三件事都没问题——死代码删除正确、模型能看到且语义正确、历史 block 完全兼容。","assets":[],"created_at":"2026-07-10T11:48:35Z","updated_at":"2026-07-10T11:48:35Z"},{"id":11633,"html_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/dog/opencode-acp/issues/20#issuecomment-11633","pull_request_url":"","issue_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/dog/opencode-acp/issues/20","user":{"id":1,"login":"dog","login_name":"","source_id":0,"full_name":"","email":"dog@noreply.localhost","avatar_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/avatars/707bc216f1ab0193186b3712bbd8b1ad","html_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/dog","language":"","is_admin":false,"last_login":"0001-01-01T00:00:00Z","created":"2026-03-23T02:18:35Z","restricted":false,"active":false,"prohibit_login":false,"location":"","website":"","description":"","visibility":"public","followers_count":1,"following_count":0,"starred_repos_count":0,"username":"dog"},"original_author":"","original_author_id":0,"body":"你提交一个 PR 吧。","assets":[],"created_at":"2026-07-10T11:50:16Z","updated_at":"2026-07-10T11:50:16Z"},{"id":11634,"html_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/dog/opencode-acp/issues/20#issuecomment-11634","pull_request_url":"","issue_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/dog/opencode-acp/issues/20","user":{"id":3,"login":"awork","login_name":"","source_id":0,"full_name":"","email":"awork@noreply.localhost","avatar_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/avatars/3a6e67811caadb37b9004123cfec7a13","html_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/awork","language":"","is_admin":false,"last_login":"0001-01-01T00:00:00Z","created":"2026-05-24T14:49:10Z","restricted":false,"active":false,"prohibit_login":false,"location":"","website":"","description":"","visibility":"public","followers_count":0,"following_count":0,"starred_repos_count":0,"username":"awork"},"original_author":"","original_author_id":0,"body":"[system] ✓ Message broadcasted to: **awork** (`ses_0b