":0,"username":"awork"},"original_author":"","original_author_id":0,"body":"[system] ✓ Message broadcasted to: **awork** (`ses_0b89319b1ffeK25eKU3GMfCK8U`, `/home/dog/projects/opencode-acp`).","assets":[],"created_at":"2026-07-10T13:47:42Z","updated_at":"2026-07-10T13:47:42Z"},{"id":11700,"html_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/dog/opencode-acp/issues/20#issuecomment-11700","pull_request_url":"","issue_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/dog/opencode-acp/issues/20","user":{"id":3,"login":"awork","login_name":"","source_id":0,"full_name":"","email":"awork@noreply.localhost","avatar_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/avatars/3a6e67811caadb37b9004123cfec7a13","html_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/awork","language":"","is_admin":false,"last_login":"0001-01-01T00:00:00Z","created":"2026-05-24T14:49:10Z","restricted":false,"active":false,"prohibit_login":false,"location":"","website":"","description":"","visibility":"public","followers_count":0,"following_count":0,"starred_repos_count":0,"username":"awork"},"original_author":"","original_author_id":0,"body":"[bot] 模型**看不到**每条消息的 token 大小。\n\n模型只能看到消息的文本内容（通过 `\u003cdcp-message-id\u003em00001\u003c/dcp-message-id\u003e` 标签标识），但没有任何内置的 token 计数器。它无法知道：\n- 某条消息是 100 token 还是 20K token\n- 一个看起来很短的消息（比如带大量 tool output 的）实际可能很大\n- 自己的上下文里哪条消息最占空间\n\n所以 breakdown 里的 `m00175 (20.7K)` 这个大小信息是**模型无法自行推导的**。如果不写大小，模型只能靠「文本看起来长 = 可能大」来猜，这很不可靠——比如一个 bash 命令返回了 500 行输出，模型可能觉得只是一次普通调用。\n\n**结论：压缩候选列表的大小标注是必要的，不能去掉。** 这是 ACP 提供给模型的「元信息」——模型自己看不到的上下文消耗分布。","assets":[],"created_at":"2026-07-10T13:48:20Z","updated_at":"2026-07-10T13:48:20Z"},{"id":11704,"html_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/dog/opencode-acp/issues/20#issuecomment-11704","pull_request_url":"","issue_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/dog/opencode-acp/issues/20","user":{"id":1,"login":"dog","login_name":"","source_id":0,"full_name":"","email":"dog@noreply.localhost","avatar_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/avatars/707bc216f1ab0193186b3712bbd8b1ad","html_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/dog