t":"2026-07-10T14:21:38Z","updated_at":"2026-07-10T14:21:38Z"},{"id":11735,"html_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/dog/opencode-acp/issues/20#issuecomment-11735","pull_request_url":"","issue_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/dog/opencode-acp/issues/20","user":{"id":3,"login":"awork","login_name":"","source_id":0,"full_name":"","email":"awork@noreply.localhost","avatar_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/avatars/3a6e67811caadb37b9004123cfec7a13","html_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/awork","language":"","is_admin":false,"last_login":"0001-01-01T00:00:00Z","created":"2026-05-24T14:49:10Z","restricted":false,"active":false,"prohibit_login":false,"location":"","website":"","description":"","visibility":"public","followers_count":0,"following_count":0,"starred_repos_count":0,"username":"awork"},"original_author":"","original_author_id":0,"body":"[bot] 已生效 ✅\n\n我能看到当前上下文里的消息标签已经带上了 tokens 和 type：\n\n```\n\u003cdcp-message-id tokens=\"198\" type=\"text\"\u003em00413\u003c/dcp-message-id\u003e\n\u003cdcp-message-id tokens=\"93\" type=\"text\"\u003em00415\u003c/dcp-message-id\u003e\n\u003cdcp-message-id tokens=\"466\" type=\"tool:reply\"\u003em00416\u003c/dcp-message-id\u003e\n```\n\n回答你的三个问题：\n\n1. **每条消息都带** ✅ — injectMessageIds 遍历所有 visible messages，不只新消息\n2. **用 Anthropic tokenizer 算的** ✅ — `countAllMessageTokens` → `@anthropic-ai/tokenizer`，不是按字数。和 breakdown 计算用的是同一个 tokenizer，结果一致\n3. **所有消息都有** ✅ — 标签每 turn 动态注入，不持久化，不管消息什么时候创建的都会被标注\n\n从我自己的上下文就能验证：`text` 类型消息标了 `type=\"text\"`，`reply` 工具调用标了 `type=\"tool:reply\"`，token 大小也准确反映了实际内容量。","assets":[],"created_at":"2026-07-10T14:21:53Z","updated_at":"2026-07-10T14:21:53Z"},{"id":11736,"html_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/dog/opencode-acp/issues/20#issuecomment-11736","pull_request_url":"","issue_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/dog/opencode-acp/issues/20","user":{"id":3,"login":"awork","login_name":"","source_id":0,"full_name":"","email":"awork@noreply.localhost","avatar_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/avatars/3a6e67811caadb37b9