ncode 进程缓存了旧的 ACP 模块）。","assets":[],"created_at":"2026-07-10T15:51:41Z","updated_at":"2026-07-10T15:51:41Z"},{"id":11967,"html_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/dog/opencode-acp/issues/20#issuecomment-11967","pull_request_url":"","issue_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/dog/opencode-acp/issues/20","user":{"id":1,"login":"dog","login_name":"","source_id":0,"full_name":"","email":"dog@noreply.localhost","avatar_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/avatars/707bc216f1ab0193186b3712bbd8b1ad","html_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/dog","language":"","is_admin":false,"last_login":"0001-01-01T00:00:00Z","created":"2026-03-23T02:18:35Z","restricted":false,"active":false,"prohibit_login":false,"location":"","website":"","description":"","visibility":"public","followers_count":1,"following_count":0,"starred_repos_count":0,"username":"dog"},"original_author":"","original_author_id":0,"body":"http://m1.redoxos.org:1195/dog/opencode-acp/issues/23#comment-11962\n看下这个审核意见 我理解改成实际大小即可 ？因为定性而已？比如实际多少?不需要精确 或者估算？","assets":[],"created_at":"2026-07-11T01:43:53Z","updated_at":"2026-07-11T01:43:53Z"},{"id":11968,"html_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/dog/opencode-acp/issues/20#issuecomment-11968","pull_request_url":"","issue_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/dog/opencode-acp/issues/20","user":{"id":3,"login":"awork","login_name":"","source_id":0,"full_name":"","email":"awork@noreply.localhost","avatar_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/avatars/3a6e67811caadb37b9004123cfec7a13","html_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/awork","language":"","is_admin":false,"last_login":"0001-01-01T00:00:00Z","created":"2026-05-24T14:49:10Z","restricted":false,"active":false,"prohibit_login":false,"location":"","website":"","description":"","visibility":"public","followers_count":0,"following_count":0,"starred_repos_count":0,"username":"awork"},"original_author":"","original_author_id":0,"body":"[system] ✓ Message broadcasted to: **awork** (`ses_0b89319b1ffeK25eKU3GMfCK8U`, `/home/dog/projects/opencode-acp`).","assets":[],"cr