ssues/20","user":{"id":3,"login":"awork","login_name":"","source_id":0,"full_name":"","email":"awork@noreply.localhost","avatar_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/avatars/3a6e67811caadb37b9004123cfec7a13","html_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/awork","language":"","is_admin":false,"last_login":"0001-01-01T00:00:00Z","created":"2026-05-24T14:49:10Z","restricted":false,"active":false,"prohibit_login":false,"location":"","website":"","description":"","visibility":"public","followers_count":0,"following_count":0,"starred_repos_count":0,"username":"awork"},"original_author":"","original_author_id":0,"body":"[system] ✅ **awork** completed (5 min)","assets":[],"created_at":"2026-07-14T04:55:44Z","updated_at":"2026-07-14T05:00:20Z"},{"id":13705,"html_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/dog/opencode-acp/issues/20#issuecomment-13705","pull_request_url":"","issue_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/dog/opencode-acp/issues/20","user":{"id":3,"login":"awork","login_name":"","source_id":0,"full_name":"","email":"awork@noreply.localhost","avatar_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/avatars/3a6e67811caadb37b9004123cfec7a13","html_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/awork","language":"","is_admin":false,"last_login":"0001-01-01T00:00:00Z","created":"2026-05-24T14:49:10Z","restricted":false,"active":false,"prohibit_login":false,"location":"","website":"","description":"","visibility":"public","followers_count":0,"following_count":0,"starred_repos_count":0,"username":"awork"},"original_author":"","original_author_id":0,"body":"[bot] 查清了。**上下文满了没压缩，根因是 token 计数严重低估。**\n\n## 问题诊断\n\n**session `ses_0a3be0cdeffezb9pLzfifH7lzK`**：\n- 实际上下文：1.03M tokens（从 API 返回的 token usage 确认）\n- ACP 估计的上下文：**100K tokens**（低估了 10 倍！）\n- 4 个 active block 压缩了 355 条消息，只留了 ~37 条可见消息\n- 16 次 API 400 错误（\"messages 参数非法\"）\n\n## 根因链\n\n```\n1. 最近 6 条 assistant 消息 output=0（finish=other，隐藏 agent 请求或中断）\n   ↓\n2. getCurrentTokenUsage() 跳过 output=0 的消息\n   ↓\n3. 回退到内容估算（sum of text parts token count）\n   ↓\n4. 大部分内容已被压缩掉 → 可见文本很少 → 估算 = ~100K\n   ↓\n5. ACP 认为上下文只有 100K / 1M = 10%\n   ↓\n6. 10% \u003c 55% maxContextLimit → 不触发 nudge\n   10% \u003c 100% GC threshold → 不触发紧急 GC\n   ↓\n7. 模型不知道上下文快满了 → 不压缩 → 上下文继续增长 → 400 错误\n```\n\n## 关键代码位置\n\n`lib/token-utils.ts:9-53` — `getCurrentTokenUsage()`：\n- 第 17 行：`if ((assistantInfo.tokens?.output || 0) \u003c= 0) continue` — 跳过 output=0\n- 第 44-53 行：fallback 估算只看 text parts，不看 tool output 体积\n\n## 修复方向\n\n`getCurrentTokenUsage` 的 fallback 逻辑有缺陷。当找不到带 output 的 assistant 消息时，应该：\n\n1. **优先用 cache.read token**——即使 output=0，cache.read 仍然反映了上一次的实际输入大小\n2. **或者用 systemPromptTokens + 全部 part 的字符数 / 4 估算**——不要只看 text parts，还要看 tool output\n\n你要我开分支修这个 bug 吗？这是个影响所有长会话的严重问题。","assets":[],"created_at":"2026-07-14T05:00:06Z","updated_at":"2026-07-14T05:00:06Z"},{"id":13706,"html_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/dog/opencode-acp/issues/20#issuecomment-13706","pull_request_url":"","issue_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/dog/opencode-acp/issues/20","user":{"id":1,"login":"dog","login_name":"","source_id":0,"full_name":"","email":"dog@noreply.localhost","avatar_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/avatars/707bc216f1ab0193186b3712bbd8b1ad","html_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/dog","language":"","is_admin":false,"last_login":"0001-01-01T00:00:00Z","created":"2026-03-23T02:18:35Z","restricted":false,"active":false,"prohibit_login":false,"location":"","website":"","description":"","visibility":"public","followers_count":1,"following_count":0,"starred_repos_count":0,"username":"dog"},"original_author":"","original_author_id":0,"body":"你的上下文先压缩一下 也快爆了 然后你也检查下是不是我配置了上下文 20% reach limit 如果超过这个是不是 acp 就不再提示压缩了 导致很长时间不压缩","assets":[],"created_at":"2026-07-14T05:03:18Z","updated_at":"2026-07-14T05:03:18Z"},{"id":13707,"html_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/dog/opencode-acp/issues/20#issuecomment-13707","pull_request_url":"","issue_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/dog/opencode-acp/issues/20","user":{"id":3,"login":"awork","login_name":"","source_id":0,"full_name":"","email":"awork@noreply.