题\n\n| 层 | 问题 | 影响 |\n|---|------|------|\n| **Bug（必须修）** | `getCurrentTokenUsage` fallback 低估 10x | ACP 认为上下文很小 → 不 nudge → 不压缩 → 爆 |\n| **配置（建议调）** | `maxBlockAge: 999999` | 旧 block 永不清除，summary 累积 |\n\n配置不需要改 20%——如果 token 计数准确，20% 阈值是合理的。关键是修 `getCurrentTokenUsage` 的 fallback 逻辑。\n\n要我现在开分支修这个 bug 吗？","assets":[],"created_at":"2026-07-14T05:04:33Z","updated_at":"2026-07-14T05:04:33Z"},{"id":13709,"html_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/dog/opencode-acp/issues/20#issuecomment-13709","pull_request_url":"","issue_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/dog/opencode-acp/issues/20","user":{"id":1,"login":"dog","login_name":"","source_id":0,"full_name":"","email":"dog@noreply.localhost","avatar_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/avatars/707bc216f1ab0193186b3712bbd8b1ad","html_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/dog","language":"","is_admin":false,"last_login":"0001-01-01T00:00:00Z","created":"2026-03-23T02:18:35Z","restricted":false,"active":false,"prohibit_login":false,"location":"","website":"","description":"","visibility":"public","followers_count":1,"following_count":0,"starred_repos_count":0,"username":"dog"},"original_author":"","original_author_id":0,"body":"你先压缩你的上下文 用 acp status 看 然后开分支解决这个问题","assets":[],"created_at":"2026-07-14T05:06:09Z","updated_at":"2026-07-14T05:06:09Z"},{"id":13710,"html_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/dog/opencode-acp/issues/20#issuecomment-13710","pull_request_url":"","issue_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/dog/opencode-acp/issues/20","user":{"id":3,"login":"awork","login_name":"","source_id":0,"full_name":"","email":"awork@noreply.localhost","avatar_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/avatars/3a6e67811caadb37b9004123cfec7a13","html_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/awork","language":"","is_admin":false,"last_login":"0001-01-01T00:00:00Z","created":"2026-05-24T14:49:10Z","restricted":false,"active":false,"prohibit_login":false,"location":"","website":"","description":"","visibility":"public","followers_count":0,"following_count":0,"starred_repos_count":0,"