 | **249438** | 249.4K |\n| msg_f61592d7b (被错误使用) | 115809 | 26 | 38592 | 326 | **154753** | **154.8K** ← 匹配通知 |\n\n## 修复效果\n\n我刚才提交的 PR #133 修复了这个 bug。新代码接受 `input\u003e0` 的消息（即使 `output=0`），所以：\n\n- **修复前**：`getCurrentTokenUsage` → 154.8K（用了旧消息）→ `154.8K - 169.9K + 3.5K = 0`\n- **修复后**：`getCurrentTokenUsage` → 249.4K（用了正确的消息）→ `249.4K - 169.9K + 3.5K = 83.0K`\n\n用户会看到 `Context 249.4K → 83.0K` 而不是 `154.8K → 0`。\n\n**需要重启 opencode 才能生效。**","assets":[],"created_at":"2026-07-14T16:16:36Z","updated_at":"2026-07-14T16:16:36Z"},{"id":13912,"html_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/dog/opencode-acp/issues/20#issuecomment-13912","pull_request_url":"","issue_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/dog/opencode-acp/issues/20","user":{"id":1,"login":"dog","login_name":"","source_id":0,"full_name":"","email":"dog@noreply.localhost","avatar_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/avatars/707bc216f1ab0193186b3712bbd8b1ad","html_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/dog","language":"","is_admin":false,"last_login":"0001-01-01T00:00:00Z","created":"2026-03-23T02:18:35Z","restricted":false,"active":false,"prohibit_login":false,"location":"","website":"","description":"","visibility":"public","followers_count":1,"following_count":0,"starred_repos_count":0,"username":"dog"},"original_author":"","original_author_id":0,"body":"解压以后又触发了压缩提示，然后又解压。解压了以后又触发了压缩提示的循环吗？因为它的动作很快，然后计数又不准导致的吗？\n现在你修的那个早就合并了，应该是部署的是当前目录的当前分支，可能是新的问题。另外，有可能这个压缩体是不太准，你自己掂量着，别过度压缩","assets":[],"created_at":"2026-07-14T16:19:42Z","updated_at":"2026-07-14T16:19:42Z"},{"id":13913,"html_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/dog/opencode-acp/issues/20#issuecomment-13913","pull_request_url":"","issue_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/dog/opencode-acp/issues/20","user":{"id":3,"login":"awork","login_name":"","source_id":0,"full_name":"","email":"awork@noreply.localhost","avatar_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/avatars/3a6e67811caadb37b9004123cfec7a13","html_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/awork","language":"","is_admin":false,"last_login":"0001-01-01T00:00