e":"","description":"","visibility":"public","followers_count":0,"following_count":0,"starred_repos_count":0,"username":"awork"},"original_author":"","original_author_id":0,"body":"[system] ✅ **awork** completed (7 min)","assets":[],"created_at":"2026-07-14T16:20:45Z","updated_at":"2026-07-14T16:27:37Z"},{"id":13920,"html_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/dog/opencode-acp/issues/20#issuecomment-13920","pull_request_url":"","issue_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/dog/opencode-acp/issues/20","user":{"id":3,"login":"awork","login_name":"","source_id":0,"full_name":"","email":"awork@noreply.localhost","avatar_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/avatars/3a6e67811caadb37b9004123cfec7a13","html_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/awork","language":"","is_admin":false,"last_login":"0001-01-01T00:00:00Z","created":"2026-05-24T14:49:10Z","restricted":false,"active":false,"prohibit_login":false,"location":"","website":"","description":"","visibility":"public","followers_count":0,"following_count":0,"starred_repos_count":0,"username":"awork"},"original_author":"","original_author_id":0,"body":"[bot] 查清楚了。**没有循环**，\"→ 0\" 是计数不准导致的显示问题。\n\n## 没有循环\n\n完整时间线（session `ses_0a3be0cdeffezb9pLzfifH7lzK`）：\n\n```\n1784044596 (user)  TODO CONTINUATION 提示\n1784044628 (user)  [SYSTEM FORWARD] 用户新评论\n1784044648 (asst)  decompress b72 (+81.2K)  ← 模型主动解压\n1784044662 (asst)  decompress b70 (+18.8K)\n1784044662 (asst)  decompress b68 (+47.8K)\n1784044678 (asst)  compress → b73-b78       ← 模型主动压缩\n1784044678 (user)  Nudge: \"Context: 154.8K\"  ← nudge 在压缩之后才触发\n1784044769 (user)  通知: \"154.8K → 0\"\n```\n\nnudge 在 compress **之后** 57ms 才触发，不是在 decompress 之后。所以不是 \"decompress → nudge → compress\" 循环。模型解压了 3 个 block 拿到旧 review 数据，用完之后自己压缩回去了——这是正常的 decompress-use-compress 行为，30 分钟只发生了 2 次。\n\n## \"→ 0\" 的根因\n\n`pipeline.ts:119` 在 compress 完成后计算 `contextTokensBefore = getCurrentTokenUsage(state, rawMessages)`。`rawMessages` 是 `prepareSession` 时 fetch 的。\n\n问题：compress 调用消息 `msg_f61596ec1` 在 fetch 时 **token 数据还没写入 DB**（`input=0, output=0`）。\n\n- 我的 PR #133 修复条件 `input \u003c= 0 \u0026\u0026 output \u003c= 0 → skip` **正确跳过了它**\n- fallback 到 decompress 调用消息 `msg_f61592d7b`（input=115809 + cache=38592 + output=26 + reasoning=326 = 154753）\n- 但这个值是**解压前**的 context（不含 3 次 decompress 恢复的 147.8K），实际 context ~300K\n- 通知计算：`154.8K - 169.9K + 3.5K = -11.6K` → `Math.max(0, -11.6K)` → **0**\n\n## 根本限制\n\n`getCurrentTokenUsage` 用的是**最后一次 LLM 调用**的 token 数据。decompress 恢复的内容不经过 LLM 调用，所以 token 数据不反映解压后的真实 context 大小。这是设计限制，不是 bug。\n\n另外，compress 调用消息本身在 `fetchSessionMessages` 时 token 数据可能还没落盘——这是 opencode 的异步写入行为。\n\n## 要不要修？\n\n两个可选方向：\n\n1. **通知显示**：当 `compressedTokens \u003e contextTokensBefore` 时，不显示 \"→ 0\"，而是显示 \"≈ N (imprecise)\" 或省略箭头。改动在 `notification.ts:225-228`，1 行。\n\n2. **token 估算**：如果最新消息没有 token 数据，用 `countAllMessageTokens` 估算最近几条消息的增量，加上前一条有 token 数据的消息的值。更复杂但更准确。\n\n你觉得需要修哪个？还是先放着？","assets":[],"created_at":"2026-07-14T16:27:25Z","updated_at":"2026-07-14T16:27:25Z"},{"id":13923,"html_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/dog/opencode-acp/issues/20#issuecomment-13923","pull_request_url":"","issue_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/dog/opencode-acp/issues/20","user":{"id":1,"login":"dog","login_name":"","source_id":0,"full_name":"","email":"dog@noreply.localhost","avatar_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/avatars/707bc216f1ab0193186b3712bbd8b1ad","html_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/dog","language":"","is_admin":false,"last_login":"0001-01-01T00:00:00Z","created":"2026-03-23T02:18:35Z","restricted":false,"active":false,"prohibit_login":false,"location":"","website":"","description":"","visibility":"public","followers_count":1,"following_count":0,"starred_repos_count":0,"username":"dog"},"original_author":"","original_author_id":0,"body":"http://m1.redoxos.org:1195/sessions/ses_0a3eb940effe5BagbSlJni47N0#mmsg_f617574e0001QCDpYYjyzI3CFA\n你看一下为什么这个会话在 5 万 token 上下的时候注入让它压缩呢？它的压缩基线是多少呢？变成 0 了吗？还是有什么 bug？我感觉没有找到根本原因。","assets":[],"created_at":"2026-07-14T16:30:47Z","updated_at":"2026-07-14T