,"issue_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/dog/opencode-acp/issues/20","user":{"id":3,"login":"awork","login_name":"","source_id":0,"full_name":"","email":"awork@noreply.localhost","avatar_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/avatars/3a6e67811caadb37b9004123cfec7a13","html_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/awork","language":"","is_admin":false,"last_login":"0001-01-01T00:00:00Z","created":"2026-05-24T14:49:10Z","restricted":false,"active":false,"prohibit_login":false,"location":"","website":"","description":"","visibility":"public","followers_count":0,"following_count":0,"starred_repos_count":0,"username":"awork"},"original_author":"","original_author_id":0,"body":"[system] ✅ **awork** completed (7 min)","assets":[],"created_at":"2026-07-14T16:35:45Z","updated_at":"2026-07-14T16:38:01Z"},{"id":13927,"html_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/dog/opencode-acp/issues/20#issuecomment-13927","pull_request_url":"","issue_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/dog/opencode-acp/issues/20","user":{"id":3,"login":"awork","login_name":"","source_id":0,"full_name":"","email":"awork@noreply.localhost","avatar_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/avatars/3a6e67811caadb37b9004123cfec7a13","html_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/awork","language":"","is_admin":false,"last_login":"0001-01-01T00:00:00Z","created":"2026-05-24T14:49:10Z","restricted":false,"active":false,"prohibit_login":false,"location":"","website":"","description":"","visibility":"public","followers_count":0,"following_count":0,"starred_repos_count":0,"username":"awork"},"original_author":"","original_author_id":0,"body":"[bot] 找到根本原因了。**是 commit `914f004` 引入的 bug——growth floor 替换了主阈值，导致 nudge 在 22.5K 增长时就触发，而不是设计预期的 50K。**\n\n## 数据\n\n```\nmodelContextLimit:     1,000,000 (1M)\nnudgeGrowthTokens:     50,000    (resolveAdaptiveNudgeGrowth: 5% of 1M, capped at 50K)\ngrowthFloor:           22,500    (max(5000, 0.45 × 50000))\nminLimit (20%):        200,000\n```\n\n会话实际值：\n```\n上一次压缩后 baseline:  ~33.1K  (通知显示 \"56.3K → 33.1K\")\nnudge 触发时 context:   56.3K   (仅为 1M 的 5.6%)\n增长量:                 23.2K\n```\n\n**23.2K ≥ 22.5K (growthFloor) → nudge 触发。但 23.2K \u003c 50K (nudgeGrowthTokens) → 本不该触发。**\n\n## 根因\n\ncommit `914f004`（\"feat: growth floor gate for compress nudges\"）做了这个替换：\n\n```typescript\n// 旧代码（替换前）：\nstate.nudges.shouldInjectThisTurn = decision.shouldNudge\n// decision.shouldNudge 检查 growth \u003e= nudgeGrowthTokens (50K) || overMaxLimit\n\n// 新代码（替换后）：\nconst nudgeAllowed = emergencyOverride || (growthSinceBaseline \u003e= growthFloor)\nstate.nudges.shouldInjectThisTurn = nudgeAllowed\n// growthFloor = 22.5K — 远低于 nudgeGrowthTokens (50K)\n```\n\n`computeShouldNudge` 的返回值 `decision.shouldNudge` 现在只用于决定 `tipsVariant`（显示样式），**不再参与 nudge 是否触发的判断**。实际的触发门控完全由 `nudgeAllowed`（基于 growthFloor）决定。\n\ngrowth floor 本意是**反抖动的额外抑制门**（\"Nudge output is suppressed unless...\"），但实际效果是**降低了触发阈值**，从 50K 降到 22.5K。\n\n## 关于基线\n\n基线不是 0。上一次压缩后 `lastPerMessageNudgeTokens` 被设为 undefined（`153f2af` fix），下一次 transform 重建为当前 context（~33.1K）。然后 context 增长到 56.3K（+23.2K），超过 growthFloor（22.5K）→ 触发。\n\n## 修复方向\n\n`nudgeAllowed` 应该同时要求 `decision.shouldNudge` AND `growth \u003e= growthFloor`：\n\n```typescript\nconst nudgeAllowed = emergencyOverride ||\n    (decision.shouldNudge \u0026\u0026 growthSinceBaseline !== undefined \u0026\u0026 growthSinceBaseline \u003e= growthFloor)\n```\n\n这样 nudge 只在 growth ≥ 50K（nudgeGrowthTokens）时触发，growthFloor 作为额外的反抖动门。要我现在修吗？","assets":[],"created_at":"2026-07-14T16:37:11Z","updated_at":"2026-07-14T16:37:11Z"},{"id":13928,"html_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/dog/opencode-acp/issues/20#issuecomment-13928","pull_request_url":"","issue_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/dog/opencode-acp/issues/20","user":{"id":1,"login":"dog","login_name":"","source_id":0,"full_name":"","email":"dog@noreply.localhost","avatar_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/avatars/707bc216f1ab0193186b3712bbd8b1ad","html_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/dog","language":"","is_admin":false,"last_login":"0001-01-01T00:00:00Z","created":"2026-03-23T02:18:35Z","restricted":false,"active":false,"prohibit_login":false,"location":"","website":"","description":"","visibility":"public","followers_count":1,"following_count":0,"starred_repos_count":0,"username":"dog"},"original_author":"","original_author_id":0,"body":"这个之前是有一个时限，就是比如说它增长了 5 万 token，然后它只压缩了其中的一小部分，比如说压缩了 1 万、2 万。那么下一次的阈值应该并不是增长 5 万，而是只增长 1 万到 2 万，或者说是压缩 2 万，增长 1 万。是这样的应该，不知道这个跟这个是否有关系。","assets":[],"created_at":"2026-07-14T16:40:00Z","updated_at":"2026-07-14T16:40:00Z"},{"id":13929,"html_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/dog/opencode-acp/issues/20#issuecomment-13929","pull_request_url":"","issue_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/dog/opencode-acp/issues/20","user":{"id":3,"login":"awork","login_name":"","source_id":0,"full_name":"","email":"awork@noreply.localhost","avatar_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/avatars/3a6e67811caadb37b9004123cfec7a13","html_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/awork","language":"","is_admin":false,"last_login":"0001-01-01T00:00:00Z","created":"2026-05-24T14:49:10Z","restricted":false,"active":false,"prohibit_login":false,"location":"","website":"","description":"","visibility":"public","followers_count":0,"following_count":0,"starred_repos_count":0,"username":"awork"},"original_author":"","original_author_id":0,"body":"[system] ✓ Message broadcasted to: **awork** (`ses_0b89319b1ffeK25eKU3GMfCK8U`, `/home/dog/projects/opencode-acp`).","assets":[],"created_at":"2026-07-14T16:40:02Z","updated_at":"2026-07-14T16:40:02Z"},{"id":13930,"html_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/dog/opencode-acp/issues/20#issuecomment-13930","pull_request_url":"","issue_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/dog/opencode-acp/issues/20","user":{"id":3,"login":"awork","login_name":"","source_id":0,"full_name":"","email":"awork@noreply.localhost","avatar_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/avatars/3a6e67811caadb37b9004123cfec7a13","html_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/awork","language":"","is_admin":false,"last_login":"0001-01-01T00:00:00Z","created":"2026-05-24T1