wing_count":0,"starred_repos_count":0,"username":"awork"},"original_author":"","original_author_id":0,"body":"[bot] 你说的这个逻辑（压缩一小部分后下次阈值降低）**已经实现了**，在 `inject.ts:113-147`。但有两个问题导致它没生效。\n\n## 已实现的 proportional baseline 调整\n\n```typescript\n// inject.ts:132-139\nconst growth = preCompress - baseline        // 本次增长量\nconst compressed = preCompress - postCompress // 实际压缩量\nconst ratio = Math.min(1, compressed / growth)\nconst adjustment = Math.min(1, ratio * 2)    // 50%压缩→1.0, 25%→0.5, 10%→0.2\nconst newBaseline = baseline + (postCompress - baseline) * adjustment\n```\n\n举个例子：baseline=0, 增长50K, 压缩了15K:\n- ratio = 15/50 = 0.3\n- adjustment = min(1, 0.6) = 0.6\n- newBaseline = 0 + 35K×0.6 = 21K\n- 下次 nudge 触发 = baseline(21K) + 阈值\n\n**问题**：这个\"阈值\"应该是 50K（`nudgeGrowthTokens`），但实际用的是 22.5K（`growthFloor`）。所以：\n- 预期：下次在 21K + 50K = 71K 触发\n- 实际：下次在 21K + 22.5K = 43.5K 触发（太早）\n\n## 两个 bug 叠加\n\n1. **`growthFloor` 替换了 `nudgeGrowthTokens` 作为主门控**（commit `914f004`）→ 阈值从 50K 降到 22.5K\n2. **`preCompressTokens` 可能不准** → 如果 `getCurrentTokenUsage` 低估了 preCompress（比如之前的 output=0 问题），proportional 计算就会失准\n\n你说的场景——\"压缩了 2 万，增长 1 万，下次阈值应该是 1-2 万\"——需要的是：**剩余增长预算 = nudgeGrowthTokens - 本次压缩量**。当前公式是调整 baseline 的位置来近似这个效果，但被 growthFloor bug 破坏了。\n\n## 建议\n\n先修 growthFloor bug（恢复 `decision.shouldNudge` 作为主门控），然后看 proportional 公式是否需要调整。要我现在动手吗？两个修复合一个 PR。","assets":[],"created_at":"2026-07-14T16:43:04Z","updated_at":"2026-07-14T16:43:04Z"},{"id":13933,"html_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/dog/opencode-acp/issues/20#issuecomment-13933","pull_request_url":"","issue_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/dog/opencode-acp/issues/20","user":{"id":1,"login":"dog","login_name":"","source_id":0,"full_name":"","email":"dog@noreply.localhost","avatar_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/avatars/707bc216f1ab0193186b3712bbd8b1ad","html_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/dog","language":"","is_admin":false,"last_login":"0001-01-01T00:00:00Z","created":"2026-03-23T02:18:35Z","restricted":false,"active":false,"prohibit_lo