vatars/3a6e67811caadb37b9004123cfec7a13","html_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/awork","language":"","is_admin":false,"last_login":"0001-01-01T00:00:00Z","created":"2026-05-24T14:49:10Z","restricted":false,"active":false,"prohibit_login":false,"location":"","website":"","description":"","visibility":"public","followers_count":0,"following_count":0,"starred_repos_count":0,"username":"awork"},"original_author":"","original_author_id":0,"body":"[bot] 能解决。分析一下为什么：\n\n## 之前的问题\n\ncommit `914f004` 把 nudge 阈值从 50K（`nudgeGrowthTokens`）降到了 22.5K（`growthFloor`）。所以：\n\n1. 解压后 context 从 33K 涨到 56K（+23K）\n2. 23K \u003e 22.5K（growthFloor）→ 立马触发 nudge\n3. 模型压缩 → 下次又涨 22.5K → 又触发\n\n## 修复后\n\n阈值恢复为 50K（`nudgeGrowthTokens`）：\n\n1. 解压后 context 从 33K 涨到 56K（+23K）\n2. 23K \u003c 50K（nudgeGrowthTokens）→ **不触发**\n3. context 继续涨到 83K（+50K）→ 才触发\n\n加上 proportional baseline 调整（`inject.ts:113-147`），如果模型压缩时只压了一部分，baseline 会按比例前移，下次阈值相应降低——但不会再出现 22.5K 就触发的情况。\n\n## 一个注意点\n\n解压本身不经过 LLM 调用，所以 `getCurrentTokenUsage` 不会立即反映解压后的真实 context。nudge 是在下一次 LLM 调用的 transform 里检查的，用的是**上一次** LLM 调用的 token 数据。这意味着：\n\n- 解压后如果模型立马做了下一次 LLM 调用，那次的 input tokens 会反映解压后的真实大小\n- 但 nudge 判断用的是**再上一次**的数据（不含解压内容）\n- 所以解压不会直接触发 nudge——nudge 只会在后续 LLM 调用 token 数据更新后才可能触发\n\n**结论：修复后解压不会导致立马提示压缩。**","assets":[],"created_at":"2026-07-14T16:58:17Z","updated_at":"2026-07-14T16:58:17Z"},{"id":13955,"html_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/dog/opencode-acp/issues/20#issuecomment-13955","pull_request_url":"","issue_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/dog/opencode-acp/issues/20","user":{"id":1,"login":"dog","login_name":"","source_id":0,"full_name":"","email":"dog@noreply.localhost","avatar_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/avatars/707bc216f1ab0193186b3712bbd8b1ad","html_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/dog","language":"","is_admin":false,"last_login":"0001-01-01T00:00:00Z","created":"2026-03-23T02:18:35Z","restricted":false,"active":false,"prohibit_login":false,"location":"","website":"","description":"","visibility":"public","followers_count":1,"following_count":0,"starred_repos_count":0,"username":"dog"},"original_author":"","original_author_id":0,"body":"现在你的上下文可以压缩了 应该不会过度提示了 再解决另外一个问题 就是我们注入给模型压缩 但是最后一段 会标记可能在用 这一段不应该压缩 但是模型会压缩导致不知道自己在干嘛 但是实际上不应该完全阻止他压缩 应该第一次失败 告诉他要谨慎 是否确认真的需要压缩这块 是否主任务还需要 如果他继续压缩会成功 。\n\n第二 推荐的压缩列表 如果只有一段消息 一般最新消息 又不应该压缩 理论上不应该推荐 除非他高于用户增长百分比比如 5％的 5 倍以上。\n第三 推荐的压缩列表 除了最后一条消息 其他都是受保护的 或者 70%以上都是受保护的 或者剩余受保护的不足用户配置的 5% 则不推荐 除非满足第二条 \n\n从 master 切 在你的 work tree 上 pull 下 master  前面的合并了 看这个需求好搞吗 \n\n另外你可以按需压缩了","assets":[],"created_at":"2026-07-14T17:06:05Z","updated_at":"2026-07-14T17:06:05Z"},{"id":13956,"html_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/dog/opencode-acp/issues/20#issuecomment-13956","pull_request_url":"","issue_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/dog/opencode-acp/issues/20","user":{"id":3,"login":"awork","login_name":"","source_id":0,"full_name":"","email":"awork@noreply.localhost","avatar_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/avatars/3a6e67811caadb37b9004123cfec7a13","html_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/awork","language":"","is_admin":false,"last_login":"0001-01-01T00:00:00Z","created":"2026-05-24T14:49:10Z","restricted":false,"active":false,"prohibit_login":false,"location":"","website":"","description":"","visibility":"public","followers_count":0,"following_count":0,"starred_repos_count":0,"username":"awork"},"original_author":"","original_author_id":0,"body":"[system] ✓ Message broadcasted to: **awork** (`ses_0b89319b1ffeK25eKU3GMfCK8U`, `/home/dog/projects/opencode-acp`).","assets":[],"created_at":"2026-07-14T17:06:06Z","updated_at":"2026-07-14T17:06:06Z"},{"id":13957,"html_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/dog/opencode-acp/issues/20#issuecomment-13957","pull_request_url":"","issue_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/dog/opencode-acp/issues/20","user":{"id":3,"login":"awork","login_name":"","source_id":0,"full_name":"","email":"awork@noreply.localhost","avatar_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/avatars/3a6e67811caadb37b9004123cfec7a13","html_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/awork",