ible+protected 的 70%+\n3. **剩余可压缩的**（去掉 protected 后）\u003c 用户配置的 5%（modelContextLimit × 5%）\n\n**需求 3 的第 3 点有个歧义**：你写的是\"剩余受保护的不足 5%\"，但受保护的少应该更值得推荐才对。我理解你的意思是\"**剩余可压缩的**不足 5%\"（去掉 protected 后能压的太少，不值得推荐）。对吗？\n\n---\n\n**复杂度**：中等，都是纯逻辑。需求 1 要加 state 字段 + range.ts 检测；需求 2/3 是 `formatCompressibleRanges` 的过滤逻辑。预估改 3 个文件 + 测试。\n\n确认需求 3 第 3 点的理解后我就开搞。","assets":[],"created_at":"2026-07-14T17:09:46Z","updated_at":"2026-07-14T17:09:46Z"},{"id":13961,"html_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/dog/opencode-acp/issues/20#issuecomment-13961","pull_request_url":"","issue_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/dog/opencode-acp/issues/20","user":{"id":3,"login":"awork","login_name":"","source_id":0,"full_name":"","email":"awork@noreply.localhost","avatar_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/avatars/3a6e67811caadb37b9004123cfec7a13","html_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/awork","language":"","is_admin":false,"last_login":"0001-01-01T00:00:00Z","created":"2026-05-24T14:49:10Z","restricted":false,"active":false,"prohibit_login":false,"location":"","website":"","description":"","visibility":"public","followers_count":0,"following_count":0,"starred_repos_count":0,"username":"awork"},"original_author":"","original_author_id":0,"body":"[system] ✅ **awork** completed (3 min)","assets":[],"created_at":"2026-07-14T17:09:58Z","updated_at":"2026-07-14T17:09:58Z"},{"id":13968,"html_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/dog/opencode-acp/issues/20#issuecomment-13968","pull_request_url":"","issue_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/dog/opencode-acp/issues/20","user":{"id":1,"login":"dog","login_name":"","source_id":0,"full_name":"","email":"dog@noreply.localhost","avatar_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/avatars/707bc216f1ab0193186b3712bbd8b1ad","html_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/dog","language":"","is_admin":false,"last_login":"0001-01-01T00:00:00Z","created":"2026-03-23T02:18:35Z","restricted":false,"active":false,"prohibit_login":false,"location":"","website":"","description":"","visibility":"public","followers_count