://192.168.10.96:3300/dog/opencode-acp/issues/20","user":{"id":1,"login":"dog","login_name":"","source_id":0,"full_name":"","email":"dog@noreply.localhost","avatar_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/avatars/707bc216f1ab0193186b3712bbd8b1ad","html_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/dog","language":"","is_admin":false,"last_login":"0001-01-01T00:00:00Z","created":"2026-03-23T02:18:35Z","restricted":false,"active":false,"prohibit_login":false,"location":"","website":"","description":"","visibility":"public","followers_count":1,"following_count":0,"starred_repos_count":0,"username":"dog"},"original_author":"","original_author_id":0,"body":"受保护占比高不推荐 和最后一条大 同时发生推荐吗 还有最后一条大应该是提供了压缩危险模式 这个矛盾如何处理的","assets":[],"created_at":"2026-07-14T17:58:20Z","updated_at":"2026-07-14T17:58:20Z"},{"id":14002,"html_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/dog/opencode-acp/issues/20#issuecomment-14002","pull_request_url":"","issue_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/dog/opencode-acp/issues/20","user":{"id":3,"login":"awork","login_name":"","source_id":0,"full_name":"","email":"awork@noreply.localhost","avatar_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/avatars/3a6e67811caadb37b9004123cfec7a13","html_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/awork","language":"","is_admin":false,"last_login":"0001-01-01T00:00:00Z","created":"2026-05-24T14:49:10Z","restricted":false,"active":false,"prohibit_login":false,"location":"","website":"","description":"","visibility":"public","followers_count":0,"following_count":0,"starred_repos_count":0,"username":"awork"},"original_author":"","original_author_id":0,"body":"[system] ✓ Message broadcasted to: **awork** (`ses_0b89319b1ffeK25eKU3GMfCK8U`, `/home/dog/projects/opencode-acp`).","assets":[],"created_at":"2026-07-14T17:58:22Z","updated_at":"2026-07-14T17:58:22Z"},{"id":14003,"html_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/dog/opencode-acp/issues/20#issuecomment-14003","pull_request_url":"","issue_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/dog/opencode-acp/issues/20","user":{"id":3,"login":"awork","login_name":"","source_id":0,"full_name":"","email":"awork@noreply.localhost","avatar_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/avatars/3a6e67811caadb37b9004123cfec7a13","html_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/awork","language":"","is_admin":false,"last_login":"0001-01-01T00:00:00Z","created":"2026-05-24T14:49:10Z","restricted":false,"active":false,"prohibit_login":false,"location":"","website":"","description":"","visibility":"public","followers_count":0,"following_count":0,"starred_repos_count":0,"username":"awork"},"original_author":"","original_author_id":0,"body":"[bot] 好问题。让我梳理清楚当前逻辑的交互：\n\n## 问题 1：受保护占比高 + 最后一条很大 → 推荐吗？\n\n**是的，推荐。** 代码逻辑（`filterRecommendedRanges`）：\n\n```\nhasHugeRange = compressible.some(r =\u003e r.tokens \u003e hugeThreshold)  // 25%\nif (hasHugeRange) return filtered  ← 直接返回，跳过所有 protected 检查\n```\n\n大段（\u003e 25%）覆盖了 Req 3 的所有 protected-dominated 条件。这是按你的原始需求设计的：\"除非满足第二条\"。\n\n## 问题 2：推荐了但需要 dangerous → 矛盾\n\n**你说得对，这里有矛盾。** 当前行为：\n\n1. `filterRecommendedRanges` → 最后一段 18K tokens \u003e 25%（1M context）→ **保留在推荐列表**\n2. `formatCompressibleRanges` → 最后一段标注 `⚠️ NOT recommended unless you are certain. Pass dangerous: true.`\n3. 模型看到推荐 → 尝试压缩 → 被拒（需要 `dangerous: true`）→ 必须重试\n\n**这确实矛盾**：一方面告诉模型\"这个值得压\"（通过 filter），另一方面说\"别压\"（通过 annotation + dangerous 门槛）。\n\n## 我的建议\n\n**方案 A（推荐）：最后一段永远不进推荐列表，但仍可 dangerous 压缩**\n- `filterRecommendedRanges` 里，识别最后一段（refNum 最大），直接排除\n- 不管它多大、不管 protected 占比\n- 模型仍可通过 `dangerous: true` 主动压缩\n- **推荐列表 = 只推荐安全的、非尾部的段**\n\n**方案 B（当前）：保留在列表但标注警告**\n- 信号分层：大小（值得压）vs 位置（要小心）\n- 模型看到两个信号自行判断\n\n你觉得哪个？我倾向 A — 推荐列表应该只包含\"可以安全压缩\"的段，需要 dangerous 的不应该出现在推荐里。","assets":[],"created_at":"2026-07-14T17:59:24Z","updated_at":"2026-07-14T17:59:24Z"},{"id":14004,"html_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/dog/opencode-acp/issues/20#issuecomment-14004","pull_request_url":"","issue_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/dog/opencode-acp/issues/20","user":{"id":1,"login":"dog","login_name":"","source_id":0,"full_name":"","email":"dog@noreply.localhost","avatar_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/avatars/707bc216f1ab0193186b3712bbd8b1ad","html_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/dog","language":"","is_admin":false,"last_login":"0001-01-01T00:00:00Z","created":"2026-03-23T02:18:35Z","restricted":false,"active":false,"prohibit_login":false,"location":"","website":"","description":"","visibility":"public","followers_count":1,"following_count":0,"starred_repos_count":0,"username":"dog"},"original_author":"","original_author_id":0,"body":"案 A（推荐）：最后一段永远不进推荐列表，但仍可 dangerous 压缩\n如果这样我理解 25%也就是 5 倍就太大了 很容易泄露 这样 判断最后一段 如果小于 10% 不推荐 就是 2 倍 不要写死 否则推荐但是标记 dangerous 模式才可以压缩掉 \n这样就没有 25％上限了 \n\n不管是否只有一条消息 这个都适用 \n\n然后受保护的我理解就不需要特殊对待了 \n\n只需要区分 可压缩的是否大于 5%\n\n所谓可压缩的 就是 \n1.非受保护的\n2.如果最后一段 大于 10%的部分 \n\n看这样是不是更清晰","assets":[],"created_at":"2026-07-14T18:06:11Z","updated_at":"2026-07-14T18:06:11Z"},{"id":14005,"html_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/dog/opencode-acp/issues/20#issuecomment-14005","pull_request_url":"","issue_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/dog/opencode-acp/issues/20","user":{"id":3,"login":"awork","login_name":"","source_id":0,"full_name":"","email":"awork@noreply.localhost","avatar_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/avatars/3a6e67811caadb37b9004123cfec7a13","html_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/awork","language":"","is_admin":false,"last_login":"0001-01-01T00:00:00Z","created":"2026-05-24T14:49:10Z","restricted":false,"active":false,"prohibit_login":false,"location":"","website":"","description":"","visibility":"public","followers_count":0,"following_count":0,"starred_repos_count":0,"username":"awork"},"original_author":"","original_author_id":0,"body":"[system] ✓ Message broadcasted to: **awork** (`ses_0b89319b1ffeK25eKU3GMfCK8U`, `/home/dog/projects/opencode-acp`).","assets":[],"created_at":"2026-07-14T18:06:13Z","updated_at":"2026-07-14T18:06:13Z"},{"id":14006,"html_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/dog/opencode-acp/issues/20#issuecomment-14006","pull_request_url":"","issue_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/dog/opencode-acp/issues/20","user":{"id":3,"login":"awork","login_name":"","source_id":0,"full_name":"","email":"awork@noreply.localhost","avatar_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/avatars/3a6e67811caadb37b9004123cfec7a13","html_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/awork","language":"","is_admin":false,"last_login":"0001-01-01T00:00:00Z","created":"2026-05-24T14:49:10Z","restricted":false,"active":false,"prohibit_login":false,"location":"","website":"","description":"","visibility":"public","followers_count":0,"following_count":0,"starred_repos_count":0,"username":"awork"},"original_author":"","original_author_id":0,"body":"[bot] 你的设计更清晰。让我确认我的理解：\n\n## 新逻辑（替换之前的 Req 2 + Req 3）\n\n### 最后一段处理\n- 最后一段 tokens \u003c 2×增长比（10%）→ **不推荐**（从列表剔除）\n- 最后一段 tokens \u003e= 2×增长比 → **推荐，标记 dangerous**\n- 不管是否单条消息，都适用\n- 删掉之前的 25%（5×）阈值\n\n### 推荐门槛\n**有效可压缩** = 非受保护的 + 最后一段超过 10% 的部分\n- 有效可压缩 \u003c 1×增长比（5%）→ 不推荐任何\n- 有效可压缩 \u003e= 5% → 推荐列表\n\n### 受保护内容\n- 不需要特殊规则——天然不算可压缩\n\n### 举例（1M context, 增长比 5%）\n- 非尾部段 40K + 最后一段 80K（8%）→ 8% \u003c 10% → 最后一段剔除。有效可压缩 = 40K \u003c 50K → 不推荐\n- 非尾部段 40K + 最后一段 150K（15%）→ 最后段保留(标记dangerous)。有效可压缩 = 40K + (150K-100K) = 90K \u003e 50K → 推荐\n- 非尾部段 80K + 最后一段 80K（8%）→ 最后段剔除。有效可压缩 = 80K \u003e 50K → 推荐非尾部段\n\n对吗？确认后我直接改。","assets":[],"created_at":"2026-07-14T18:07:52Z","updated_at":"2026-07-14T18:07:52Z"},{"id":14007,"html_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/dog/opencode-acp/issues/20#issuecomment-14007","pull_request_url":"","issue_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/dog/opencode-acp/issues/20","user":{"id":1,"login":"dog","login_name":"","source_id":0,"full_name":"","email":"dog@noreply.localhost","avatar_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/avatars/707bc216f1ab0193186b3712bbd8b1ad","html_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/dog","language":"","is_admin":false,"last_login":"0001-01-01T00:00:00Z","created":"2026-03-23T02:18:35Z","restricted":false,"active":false,"prohibit_login":false,"location":"","website":"","description":"","visibility":"public","followers_count":1,"following_count":0,"starred_repos_cou