tputRanges=0\n```\n\n**分析**：\n1. 整个会话只有 1 个可压缩段（24.5K tokens）\n2. 该段 \u003c lastSegmentFloor（100K = 2× growthThreshold）→ 被排除（全是\"最后一段\"，模型正在用）\n3. 有效可压缩 = 0 \u003c 50K → **全部抑制**（推荐列表为空 ✅）\n\n**Bug 在哪**：`nudgeAllowed` 只检查 growth \u003e threshold（64K \u003e 50K → 触发），但没检查 `recommendedRanges.length \u003e 0`。结果是：\n- nudge 注入了\"去压缩！\"\n- 但推荐列表是空的 → 模型被告知去压缩，却没给任何范围\n- 浪费 context + 困扰模型\n\n**修复方案**：在 `inject.ts` 的 nudge 门控里加一个条件 — 如果 `recommendedRanges.length === 0` 且不是 `emergencyOverride`，跳过 nudge 注入。\n\n需要我修吗？","assets":[],"created_at":"2026-07-15T05:50:13Z","updated_at":"2026-07-15T05:50:13Z"},{"id":14112,"html_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/dog/opencode-acp/issues/20#issuecomment-14112","pull_request_url":"","issue_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/dog/opencode-acp/issues/20","user":{"id":1,"login":"dog","login_name":"","source_id":0,"full_name":"","email":"dog@noreply.localhost","avatar_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/avatars/707bc216f1ab0193186b3712bbd8b1ad","html_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/dog","language":"","is_admin":false,"last_login":"0001-01-01T00:00:00Z","created":"2026-03-23T02:18:35Z","restricted":false,"active":false,"prohibit_login":false,"location":"","website":"","description":"","visibility":"public","followers_count":1,"following_count":0,"starred_repos_count":0,"username":"dog"},"original_author":"","original_author_id":0,"body":"是的 修复吧","assets":[],"created_at":"2026-07-15T05:56:03Z","updated_at":"2026-07-15T05:56:03Z"},{"id":14113,"html_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/dog/opencode-acp/issues/20#issuecomment-14113","pull_request_url":"","issue_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/dog/opencode-acp/issues/20","user":{"id":3,"login":"awork","login_name":"","source_id":0,"full_name":"","email":"awork@noreply.localhost","avatar_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/avatars/3a6e67811caadb37b9004123cfec7a13","html_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/awork","language":"","is_admin":false,"last_login":"0001-01-01T00:00:00Z","created":"2026-05-24T14:49:10Z","restricte