lic","followers_count":0,"following_count":0,"starred_repos_count":0,"username":"awork"},"original_author":"","original_author_id":0,"body":"[bot] **空推荐列表 nudge 修复完成** — PR #147\n\n**问题**：当所有可压缩范围都低于 last-segment floor（1M 模型 = 100K tokens）时，filter 会过滤掉所有范围，但 nudge 仍然触发 → 注入\"去压缩\"文本但推荐列表为空，浪费 context 且让模型困惑。\n\n**修复**：在 `injectCompressNudges()` 中添加 `filterSuppressed` 门控：\n- 当范围存在但全部被过滤 → 抑制 nudge 文本注入\n- 紧急 override（maxLimit）始终触发\n- 无 message ID 的场景（0 范围）不受影响\n\n713/713 测试通过，已部署。\nPR: https://github.com/ranxianglei/opencode-acp/pull/147","assets":[],"created_at":"2026-07-15T06:40:42Z","updated_at":"2026-07-15T06:40:42Z"},{"id":14140,"html_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/dog/opencode-acp/issues/20#issuecomment-14140","pull_request_url":"","issue_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/dog/opencode-acp/issues/20","user":{"id":1,"login":"dog","login_name":"","source_id":0,"full_name":"","email":"dog@noreply.localhost","avatar_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/avatars/707bc216f1ab0193186b3712bbd8b1ad","html_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/dog","language":"","is_admin":false,"last_login":"0001-01-01T00:00:00Z","created":"2026-03-23T02:18:35Z","restricted":false,"active":false,"prohibit_login":false,"location":"","website":"","description":"","visibility":"public","followers_count":1,"following_count":0,"starred_repos_count":0,"username":"dog"},"original_author":"","original_author_id":0,"body":"http://m1.redoxos.org:1195/sessions/ses_0a3be0cdeffezb9pLzfifH7lzK#mmsg_f65d0a166001FHeQKZTT7k71nJ 我看到了这个消息，你给我看一下，这个日志是每次注入的时候都会打吗？它连续打了好几次。","assets":[],"created_at":"2026-07-15T12:47:16Z","updated_at":"2026-07-15T12:47:16Z"},{"id":14141,"html_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/dog/opencode-acp/issues/20#issuecomment-14141","pull_request_url":"","issue_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/dog/opencode-acp/issues/20","user":{"id":3,"login":"awork","login_name":"","source_id":0,"full_name":"","email":"awork@noreply.localhost","avatar_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/avatars/3a6e67811caadb37b9004123c