"assets":[],"created_at":"2026-07-15T12:48:21Z","updated_at":"2026-07-15T12:48:21Z"},{"id":14146,"html_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/dog/opencode-acp/issues/20#issuecomment-14146","pull_request_url":"","issue_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/dog/opencode-acp/issues/20","user":{"id":1,"login":"dog","login_name":"","source_id":0,"full_name":"","email":"dog@noreply.localhost","avatar_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/avatars/707bc216f1ab0193186b3712bbd8b1ad","html_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/dog","language":"","is_admin":false,"last_login":"0001-01-01T00:00:00Z","created":"2026-03-23T02:18:35Z","restricted":false,"active":false,"prohibit_login":false,"location":"","website":"","description":"","visibility":"public","followers_count":1,"following_count":0,"starred_repos_count":0,"username":"dog"},"original_author":"","original_author_id":0,"body":"审查一下我们目前的修复相对正式版本是否引入了过度压缩问题 有用户报告类似问题","assets":[],"created_at":"2026-07-15T12:56:49Z","updated_at":"2026-07-15T12:56:49Z"},{"id":14147,"html_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/dog/opencode-acp/issues/20#issuecomment-14147","pull_request_url":"","issue_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/dog/opencode-acp/issues/20","user":{"id":3,"login":"awork","login_name":"","source_id":0,"full_name":"","email":"awork@noreply.localhost","avatar_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/avatars/3a6e67811caadb37b9004123cfec7a13","html_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/awork","language":"","is_admin":false,"last_login":"0001-01-01T00:00:00Z","created":"2026-05-24T14:49:10Z","restricted":false,"active":false,"prohibit_login":false,"location":"","website":"","description":"","visibility":"public","followers_count":0,"following_count":0,"starred_repos_count":0,"username":"awork"},"original_author":"","original_author_id":0,"body":"[system] ✓ Message broadcasted to: **awork** (`ses_0b89319b1ffeK25eKU3GMfCK8U`, `/home/dog/projects/opencode-acp`).","assets":[],"created_at":"2026-07-15T12:56:50Z","updated_at":"2026-07-15T12:56:50Z"},{"id":14148,"html_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/dog/opencode-acp/issues/20#issuecomment-14148","pull_request_url":"","issue_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/dog/opencode-acp/issues/20","user":{"id":3,"login":"awork","login_name":"","source_id":0,"full_name":"","email":"awork@noreply.localhost","avatar_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/avatars/3a6e67811caadb37b9004123cfec7a13","html_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/awork","language":"","is_admin":false,"last_login":"0001-01-01T00:00:00Z","created":"2026-05-24T14:49:10Z","restricted":false,"active":false,"prohibit_login":false,"location":"","website":"","description":"","visibility":"public","followers_count":0,"following_count":0,"starred_repos_count":0,"username":"awork"},"original_author":"","original_author_id":0,"body":"[system] ✅ **awork** completed (2 min)","assets":[],"created_at":"2026-07-15T13:00:47Z","updated_at":"2026-07-15T13:27:01Z"},{"id":14151,"html_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/dog/opencode-acp/issues/20#issuecomment-14151","pull_request_url":"","issue_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/dog/opencode-acp/issues/20","user":{"id":3,"login":"awork","login_name":"","source_id":0,"full_name":"","email":"awork@noreply.localhost","avatar_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/avatars/3a6e67811caadb37b9004123cfec7a13","html_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/awork","language":"","is_admin":false,"last_login":"0001-01-01T00:00:00Z","created":"2026-05-24T14:49:10Z","restricted":false,"active":false,"prohibit_login":false,"location":"","website":"","description":"","visibility":"public","followers_count":0,"following_count":0,"starred_repos_count":0,"username":"awork"},"original_author":"","original_author_id":0,"body":"[bot] 审查完成。**结论：我们的修复没有引入过度压缩——恰好相反，全部是减少压缩频率的措施。用户报告的\"类似问题\"是另一个未修的 bug。**\n\n## 一、版本对照：防过度压缩措施在哪一层\n\n| 版本 | 包含的防过度压缩机制 |\n|------|---------------------|\n| **v1.12.6**（stable/latest） | `growthFloor` 门控：nudge 必须 growth ≥ max(5000, 0.45×nudgeGrowthTokens) 才触发。1M 模型 = 22.5K。已发布。 |\n| **v1.12.7-dev.1**（dev） | 新增 `filterRecommendedRanges`（有效可压缩 \u003c 5% 则抑制全部推荐）+ `dangerous` 参数（last segment 必须显式 opt-in）+ `checkLastSegmentDangerous` 无状态守卫 |\n| **PR #147**（当前分支，未发布） | 新增 no-recs-skip：filter 无推荐时不注入 nudge 文本 |\n\n**每一条改动都是让压缩更难触发，不是更容易。** diff `v1.12.6..HEAD` 在 `lib/messages/inject/` + `lib/compress/` 的 233 行净增里，没有任何新开的压缩触发路径。\n\n## 二、用户报告的\"类似问题\"真实根因 ≠ nudge 系统\n\nGitHub **#135**（外部用户 Trollgeir，ChatGPT-5.6）：\"Compresses zero, creates summary\" + 循环压缩同一 range。日志：\n```\n▣ Compression #43 → b45 -0 removed, +482 summary\n→ Range: b45: m01309–m02150\n```\n**-0 removed 但仍创建块**——这是 **#93 phantom block bug**，不是过度频繁压缩。\n\n根因在 **compress 工具的 state 应用层**（`lib/compress/state.ts:246-272`）：\n\n```typescript\nconst newlyCompressedMessageIds: string[] = []\nfor (const messageId of effectiveMessageIds) {\n    if (isNowActive \u0026\u0026 !wasActive) {           // 只收\"新激活\"的消息\n        newlyCompressedMessageIds.push(messageId)\n    }\n}\nblock.directMessageIds = [...newlyCompressedMessageIds]  // 可能为 []\nblock.compressedTokens = compressedTokens                 // 可能为 0\n// ← 这里没有 guard：if (newlyCompressedMessageIds.length === 0) reject\n```\n\n当模型压缩一个**已经被压缩过的范围**（所有消息 `wasActive=true`）时：\n- `newlyCompressedMessageIds = []`，`compressedTokens = 0`\n- 但块**照样创建**（`directMessageIds: []`, `effectiveMessageIds` 从 consumed blocks 继承 1692 条）\n- 模型看到上下文没缩小 → 再压一次 → 又一个空块 → **死循环**\n\n这个 bug **v1.12.6 就存在**，与我们的 nudge-gating / filter / dangerous 工作完全无关。#93 仍然 OPEN，未修。\n\n## 三、一个低风险点（已防护）\n\n`filterRecommendedRanges` 在 last segment ≥ 2× growth threshold 时会把它列入推荐并标 `dangerous: true` + ⚠️ 注释。理论上列出该 range 可能**弱诱导**部分模型去压缩它。但有两层守卫：\n1. `checkLastSegmentDangerous`（pipeline.ts）——覆盖 last segment 且未传 `dangerous:true` → 直接 throw\n2. 注释明确写\"NOT recommended unless you are certain\"\n\n风险低，但值得观察。\n\n## 四、建议\n\n**修 #93 才是解决用户报告的正确方向**——在 `applyCompressionState` 或 `range.ts` 执行前加一个守卫：\n\n```typescript\n// range.ts，在 minCompressRange 检查之后\nif (newlyCompressedMessageIds.length === 0) {\n    throw new Error(\n        \"Selected range contains only already-compressed messages (0 new direct messages). \" +\n        \"Nothing to compress — pick a range with visible, uncompressed content.\"\n    )\n}\n```\n\n这能同时解决 #135 的\"compresses zero\"和循环问题。要不要我开个分支修？走 devlog + PR + 双 review 流程。","assets":[],"created_at":"2026-07-15T13:02:37Z","updated_at":"2026-07-15T13:02:37Z"},{"id":14154,"html_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/dog/opencode-acp/issues/20#issuecomment-14154","pull_request_url":"","issue_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/dog/opencode-acp/issues/20","user":{"id":1,"login":"dog","login_name":"","source_id":0,"full_name":"","email":"dog@noreply.localhost","avatar_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/avatars/707bc216f1ab0193186b3712bbd8b1ad","html_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/dog","language":"","is_admin":false,"last_login":"0001-01-01T00:00:00Z","created":"2026-03-23T02:18:35Z","restricted":false,"active":false,"prohibit_login":false,"location":"","website":"","description":"","visibility":"public","followers_count":1,"following_count":0,"starred_repos_count":0,"username":"dog"},"original_author":"","original_author_id":0,"body":"前面的两个修复都已经 merge 了，你从 master 切吧，然后修复这个问题。","assets":[],"created_at":"2026-07-15T13:06:27Z","updated_at":"2026-07-15T13:06:27Z"},{"id":14155,"html_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/dog/opencode-acp/issues/20#issuecomment-14155","pull_request_url":"","issue_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/dog/opencode-acp/issues/20","user":{"id":3,"login":"awork","login_name":"","source_id":0,"full_name":"","email":"awork@noreply.localhost","avatar_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/avatars/3a6e67811caadb37b9004123cfec7a13","html_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/awork","language":"","is_admin":false,"last_login":"0001-01-01T00:00:00Z","created":"2026-05-24T14:49:10Z","restricted":false,"active":false,"prohibit_login":false,"location":"","website":"","description":"","visibility":"public","followers_count":0,"following_count":0,"starred_repos_count":0,"username":"awork"},"original_author":"","original_author_id":0