ncode-acp/pull/148\n\n## 修复内容\n\n`lib/compress/pipeline.ts` 新增 `checkPhantomBlock()` 无状态守卫——在压缩循环之前检查每个 plan 的有效消息集是否**全部已激活**（已在某个 block 下）。如果是 → 直接 throw，不创建块。\n\n调用点：\n- `range.ts`：在 `checkLastSegmentDangerous` 之后、snapshot 之前\n- `message.ts`：同位置（message 模式 consumedBlockIds 恒为 `[]`）\n\n## 算法\n\n一条消息是\"新的\"（会被新压缩）当且仅当它当前没有在任何 block 下激活（`activeBlockIds.length === 0`）。被 consume 的 block 下的消息**不算新**——换了块标签但原本就是隐藏的，不算新压缩。这与 `applyCompressionState` 的 `newlyCompressedMessageIds` 计算一致。\n\n## 验证\n\n- typecheck: 0 errors\n- 新增 12 个测试（`tests/phantom-block.test.ts`）\n- 全量 **725/725 pass**（713 原有 + 12 新增）\n- devlog: `devlog/2026-07-15_reject-empty-blocks/`\n\n3 个原子 commit：实现 / 测试 / devlog。等你 review + 确认 merge。","assets":[],"created_at":"2026-07-15T13:23:32Z","updated_at":"2026-07-15T13:23:32Z"},{"id":14160,"html_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/dog/opencode-acp/issues/20#issuecomment-14160","pull_request_url":"","issue_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/dog/opencode-acp/issues/20","user":{"id":1,"login":"dog","login_name":"","source_id":0,"full_name":"","email":"dog@noreply.localhost","avatar_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/avatars/707bc216f1ab0193186b3712bbd8b1ad","html_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/dog","language":"","is_admin":false,"last_login":"0001-01-01T00:00:00Z","created":"2026-03-23T02:18:35Z","restricted":false,"active":false,"prohibit_login":false,"location":"","website":"","description":"","visibility":"public","followers_count":1,"following_count":0,"starred_repos_count":0,"username":"dog"},"original_author":"","original_author_id":0,"body":"这个压缩块，比如说我们一次性可以压缩一个范围。那么如果是这样的话。它这个范围内的分好几个主题，它如果其中一个主题是空的，会发生什么？也会报错吗？还是说全部是空的才会报错？另外，为什么会发生这种空主题的情况呢？","assets":[],"created_at":"2026-07-15T13:24:56Z","updated_at":"2026-07-15T13:24:56Z"},{"id":14161,"html_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/dog/opencode-acp/issues/20#issuecomment-14161","pull_request_url":"","issue_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/dog/opencode-acp/issues/20","user":{"id":3,"login":"awork","login_name":"","source_id":0,"full_name":"","email":"awork@noreply.localhost","avatar_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/avatars/3a6e67811caadb37b9004123cfec7a13","html_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/awork","language":"","is_admin":false,"last_login":"0001-01-01T00:00:00Z","created":"2026-05-24T14:49:10Z","restricted":false,"active":false,"prohibit_login":false,"location":"","website":"","description":"","visibility":"public","followers_count":0,"following_count":0,"starred_repos_count":0,"username":"awork"},"original_author":"","original_author_id":0,"body":"[system] ✓ Message broadcasted to: **awork** (`ses_0b89319b1ffeK25eKU3GMfCK8U`, `/home/dog/projects/opencode-acp`).","assets":[],"created_at":"2026-07-15T13:24:58Z","updated_at":"2026-07-15T13:24:58Z"},{"id":14163,"html_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/dog/opencode-acp/issues/20#issuecomment-14163","pull_request_url":"","issue_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/dog/opencode-acp/issues/20","user":{"id":3,"login":"awork","login_name":"","source_id":0,"full_name":"","email":"awork@noreply.localhost","avatar_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/avatars/3a6e67811caadb37b9004123cfec7a13","html_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/awork","language":"","is_admin":false,"last_login":"0001-01-01T00:00:00Z","created":"2026-05-24T14:49:10Z","restricted":false,"active":false,"prohibit_login":false,"location":"","website":"","description":"","visibility":"public","followers_count":0,"following_count":0,"starred_repos_count":0,"username":"awork"},"original_author":"","original_author_id":0,"body":"[bot] 好问题，两个都回答一下：\n\n## 1. 只要有一个主题是空的，就会报错（fail-fast）\n\n`checkPhantomBlock`（`lib/compress/pipeline.ts:169-203`）是**逐个 plan 检查**的：\n\n```typescript\nfor (let i = 0; i \u003c plans.length; i++) {\n    // ... 计算 effective 消息集 ...\n    const hasNew = [...effective].some(mid =\u003e /* 至少有一条未压缩消息 */)\n    if (!hasNew) {\n        return new Error(`Compression range ${i + 1} contains only already-compressed messages ...`)\n    }\n}\n```\n\n一次 `compress` 调用可以带多个 `content` 条目（多个范围/主题），每个条目 = 一个 plan。**只要其中任意一个 plan 是空的（phantom），整个调用立即报错被拒绝**，不会部分执行。不是全部为空才报错。\n\n报错信息会指明是第几个范围出了问题（`Compression range 2 contains only...`），模型可以据此调整。\n\n这是故意设计成 fail-fast 的：如果允许部分执行，状态会不一致——有的 block 创建了、有的没有，模型看到部分成功很难判断下一步。\n\n## 2. 为什么会出现空主题（phantom）\n\nPhantom = 范围内**所有消息都已经被压缩过了**，没有一条是新的。\n\n根因是**模型对\"哪些消息已经压缩了\"没有完美的可见性**。具体场景：\n\n**场景 A：重复压缩同一范围（最常见）**\n1. 模型之前压缩了 m10–m20，创建了 block b5\n2. 模型在上下文里看到 b5 的 summary，但没意识到这些消息已经压缩了\n3. 模型再次调用 `compress(m10, m20)` → b5 被消耗，它的 effectiveMessageIds 被继承 → m10–m20 全部已在 b5 下 active → 没有新消息 → phantom\n\n**场景 B：嵌套压缩的边界模糊**\n1. b3 覆盖 m5–m15，b7 覆盖 m12–m25（嵌套，b7 消耗了 b3）\n2. 模型看到 b3 的 summary 还在（因为 b7 嵌套了它），以为 m5–m15 还能压缩\n3. 调用 `compress(m5, m15)` → 这些消息现在 active 在 b7 下 → phantom\n\n**本质**：模型看到的是 summary 文本，不是精确的\"这条消息是否已压缩\"的标记。当它选的范围恰好完全落在已压缩区域，就会触发 phantom。\n\n修复前（v1.12.6 及更早）：phantom block 照样创建（0 tokens saved, +N bytes summary overhead），模型看到\"压缩了 0 tokens\"，以为没压成功，再试一次 → 又是 phantom → **死循环**（issue #93）。修复后（PR #148）：直接拒绝，报错引导模型选一个真正有未压缩内容的范围。","assets":[],"created_at":"2026-07-15T13:26:47Z","updated_at":"2026-07-15T13:26:47Z"},{"id":14168,"html_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/dog/opencode-acp/issues/20#issuecomment-14168","pull_request_url":"","issue_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/dog/opencode-acp/issues/20","user":{"id":1,"login":"dog","login_name":"","source_id":0,"full_name":"","email":"dog@noreply.localhost","avatar_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/avatars/707bc216f1ab0193186b3712bbd8b1ad","html_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/dog","language":"","is_admin":false,"last_login":"0001-01-01T00:00:00Z","created":"2026-03-23T02:18:35Z","restricted":false,"active":false,"prohibit_login":false,"location":"","website":"","description":"","visibility":"public","followers_count":1,"following_count":0,"starred_repos_count":0,"username":"dog"},"original_author":"","original_author_id":0,"body":"假设它压缩了 10 个子主题，那只有 3 个是空的，那它压缩的第一个就报错了，报完错以后重试，把这个踢出去，又压，第二个又报错了。然后把这个踢出去又压，第三次报错。那我理解，三次报错以后，模型应该不会再尝试了。","assets":[],"created_at":"2026-07-15T14:02:18Z","updated_at":"2026-07-15T14:02:18Z"},{"id":14169,"html_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/dog/opencode-acp/issues/20#issuecomment-14169","pull_request_url":"","issue_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/dog/opencode-acp/issues/20","user":{"id":3,"login":"awork","login_name":"","source_id":0,"full_name":"","email":"awork@noreply.localhost","avatar_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/avatars/3a6e67811caadb37b9004123cfec7a13","html_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/awork","language":"","is_admin":false,"last_login":"0001-01-01T00:00:00Z","created":"2026-05-24T14:49:10Z","restricted":false,"active":false,"prohibit_login":false,"location":"","website":"","description":"","visibility":"public","followers_count":0,"following_count":0,"starred_repos_count":0,"username":"awork"},"original_author":"","original_author_id":0,"body":"[system] ✓ Message broadcasted to: **awork** (`ses_0b89319b1ffeK25eKU3GMfCK8U`, `/home/dog/projects/opencode-acp`).","assets":[],"created_at":"2026-07-15T14:02:19Z","updated_at":"2026-07-15T14:02:19Z"},{"id":14171,"html_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/dog/opencode-acp/issues/20#issuecomment-14171","pull_request_url":"","issue_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/dog/opencode-acp/issues/20","user":{"id":3,"login":"awork","login_name":"","source_id":0,"full_name":"","email":"awork@noreply.localhost","avatar_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/avatars/3a6e67811caadb37b9004123cfec7a13","html_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/awork","language":"","is_admin":false,"last_login":"0001-01-01T00:00:00Z","created":"2026-05-24T14:49:10Z","restricted":false,"active":false,"prohibit_login":false,"location":"","website":"","description":"","visibility":"public","followers_count":0,"following_count":0,"starred_repos_count":0,"username":"awork"},"original_author":"","original_author_id":0,"body":"[bot] 你的分析完全正确，而且实际上比你说的情况还要更差一点：\n\n## 当前行为确认\n\n`checkPhantomBlock`（`pipeline.ts:193-200`）是 **return on first hit** —— 遇到第一个 phantom 就立刻 `return new Error()`，报错信息只包含**一个** phantom 的编号（`Compression range 2 contains...`）。\n\n所以模型不仅要重试 3 次，而且每次只能知道一个 phantom 的位置。如果 10 个 plan 里有 3 个 phantom，模型需要：\n1. 第一次调用 → 报错说 range 2 是空的 → 模型删掉 range 2，重试\n2. 第二次调用 → 报错说 range X 是空的（原来排第3的现在变成第2）→ 删掉，重试\n3. 第三次调用 → 又报错 → 删掉，重试\n4. 第四次调用 → 终于全部有效 → 成功\n\n4 次 API 调用才压一次。如果模型在第 3 次报错后就放弃（很常见），那 7 个有效 plan 也跟着遭殃，一个都没压成。\n\n## 更好的方案：跳过 phantom，只压有效的\n\nPhantom plan 本身就是 0 token 收益的空操作（所有消息已被压缩过），跳过它没有任何损失。所以：\n\n- **部分有效** → 跳过 phantom plan，压缩有效 plan，在返回结果里告知模型哪些被跳过了\n- **全部 phantom** → 报错（确实没东西可压）\n\n这样 10 个 plan 里 3 个 phantom 的情况：一次调用就成功，7 个有效 plan 全部压缩，跳过 3 个空的。0 次重试。\n\n改动很小：`checkPhantomBlock` 从\"返回第一个 Error\"改成\"过滤掉 phantom plans + 如果全空才报错\"，调用方把过滤后的 plans 传给压缩循环。\n\n要改吗？","assets":[],"created_at":"2026-07-15T14:03:54Z","updated_at":"2026-07-15T14:03:54Z"},{"id":14175,"html_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/dog/opencode-acp/issues/20#issuecomment-14175","pull_request_url":"","issue_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/dog/opencode-acp/issues/20","user":{"id":1,"login":"dog","login_name":"","source_id":0,"full_name":"","email":"dog@noreply.localhost","avatar_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/avatars/707bc216f1ab0193186b3712bbd8b1ad","html_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/dog","language":"","is_admin":false,"last_login":"0001-01-01T00:00:00Z","created":"2026-03-23T02:18:35Z","restricted":false,"active":false,"prohibit_login":false,"location":"","website":"","description":"","visibility":"public","followers_count":1,"following_count":0,"starred_repos_count":0,"username":"dog"},"original_author":"","original_author_id":0,"body":"这个模型在压缩的时候，我们不是有提示它这个范围内有多大吗？难道它是已经压缩过了吗？才导致压缩为空的吗？现在先搞清楚这个原因，看一下它属于哪种情况。","assets":[],"created_at":"2026-07-15T14:07:40Z","updated_at":"2026-07-15T14:07:40Z"},{"id":14176,"html_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/dog/opencode-acp/issues/20#issuecomment-14176","pull_request_url":"","issue_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/dog/opencode-acp/issues/20","user":{"id":3,"login":"awork","login_name":"","source_id":0,"full_name":"","email":"awork@noreply.loc