":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/dog/opencode-acp/issues/20#issuecomment-14187","pull_request_url":"","issue_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/dog/opencode-acp/issues/20","user":{"id":1,"login":"dog","login_name":"","source_id":0,"full_name":"","email":"dog@noreply.localhost","avatar_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/avatars/707bc216f1ab0193186b3712bbd8b1ad","html_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/dog","language":"","is_admin":false,"last_login":"0001-01-01T00:00:00Z","created":"2026-03-23T02:18:35Z","restricted":false,"active":false,"prohibit_login":false,"location":"","website":"","description":"","visibility":"public","followers_count":1,"following_count":0,"starred_repos_count":0,"username":"dog"},"original_author":"","original_author_id":0,"body":"http://m1.redoxos.org:1195/sessions/ses_0b2cd5a70ffeQQjqa0uABNjqsW#mmsg_f661db763001UmMg0NbpniwCzB \nhttp://m1.redoxos.org:1195/sessions/ses_0b2cd5a70ffeQQjqa0uABNjqsW#mmsg_f661d8c38001z7p3yF7cxUq2Zv\nhttp://m1.redoxos.org:1195/sessions/ses_0b2cd5a70ffeQQjqa0uABNjqsW#mmsg_f661d8c800015cJ1RcwkEMjlY7\n\n你看这个消息好像我没有发送什么东西，他好像收到了一些消息，他就开始干活了。","assets":[],"created_at":"2026-07-15T14:19:21Z","updated_at":"2026-07-15T14:19:21Z"},{"id":14188,"html_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/dog/opencode-acp/issues/20#issuecomment-14188","pull_request_url":"","issue_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/dog/opencode-acp/issues/20","user":{"id":3,"login":"awork","login_name":"","source_id":0,"full_name":"","email":"awork@noreply.localhost","avatar_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/avatars/3a6e67811caadb37b9004123cfec7a13","html_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/awork","language":"","is_admin":false,"last_login":"0001-01-01T00:00:00Z","created":"2026-05-24T14:49:10Z","restricted":false,"active":false,"prohibit_login":false,"location":"","website":"","description":"","visibility":"public","followers_count":0,"following_count":0,"starred_repos_count":0,"username":"awork"},"original_author":"","original_author_id":0,"body":"[system] ✓ Message broadcasted to: **awork** (`ses_0b89319b1ffeK25eKU3GMfCK8U`, `/home/dog/projects/opencode-acp`).","assets":[],"created_at":"2026-07-15T14:19:23Z","updated_at":"2026-07-15T14:19:23Z"},{"id":14191,"html_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/dog/opencode-acp/issues/20#issuecomment-14191","pull_request_url":"","issue_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/dog/opencode-acp/issues/20","user":{"id":3,"login":"awork","login_name":"","source_id":0,"full_name":"","email":"awork@noreply.localhost","avatar_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/avatars/3a6e67811caadb37b9004123cfec7a13","html_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/awork","language":"","is_admin":false,"last_login":"0001-01-01T00:00:00Z","created":"2026-05-24T14:49:10Z","restricted":false,"active":false,"prohibit_login":false,"location":"","website":"","description":"","visibility":"public","followers_count":0,"following_count":0,"starred_repos_count":0,"username":"awork"},"original_author":"","original_author_id":0,"body":"[bot]\n\n## 根因：debug 通知在 transform hook 内调用了 `session.prompt()`\n\n查到了。这三条消息里的 user 消息（`msg_f661d8c80001`）是 ACP 的 **debug 通知**，不是你发的。\n\n### 完整链路\n\n**hooks.ts:282-292** — `config.debug` 开启时，传一个 `debugNotify` 回调给 `injectCompressNudges`：\n\n```typescript\nconfig.debug \u0026\u0026 state.sessionId\n    ? (text: string) =\u003e {\n        sendIgnoredMessage(       // ← 调用 client.session.prompt()\n            client,\n            state.sessionId!,\n            `[ACP Debug] Nudge injected:\\n${text}`,\n            {}, logger,\n        ).catch(() =\u003e {})\n    }\n    : undefined,\n```\n\n**inject.ts:330-349** — 每次 transform hook 运行，只要有 compressible range，就触发这个回调。\n\n**sendIgnoredMessage**（`ui/notification.ts:317`）调用 `client.session.prompt()` —— 这是 opencode 创建新消息/新 turn 的主 API。\n\n### 问题\n\n`client.session.prompt()` 在 **message-transform hook 内部**被调用。transform hook 本身是处理当前 prompt 的一部分。在处理过程中创建新 prompt = **嵌套调用**：\n\n1. 新 user 消息写入 DB（`ignored: true`）\n2. `noReply: true` 没有被正确遵守 → 模型开始响应这条 debug 消息\n3. 你看到的 user 消息就是 debug 通知文本，assistant 消息是模型对它的响应\n\n**这就是\"没发消息就开始干活\"的原因** — debug 通知触发了新的 model turn。\n\n### 修复方案\n\n把 `debugNotify` 从 `sendIgnoredMessage`（创建 user 消息）改成纯日志（`logger.debug`）：\n\n```typescript\n// hooks.ts:282-292 改为：\nconfig.debug\n    ? (text: string) =\u003e {\n        logger.debug(\"[ACP Debug] Nudge injected\", { text })\n    }\n    : undefined,\n```\n\nDebug 信息仍然写入 `~/.config/opencode/logs/acp/daily/` 日志文件，但不再创建 user 消息、不再触发 model turn。\n\n### 立即止血\n\n在修复部署前，把 `~/.config/opencode/acp.jsonc` 里的 `\"debug\": false` 关掉，debug 通知就不会再触发。\n\n要我直接改掉吗？一行改动。","assets":[],"created_at":"2026-07-15T14:22:33Z","updated_at":"2026-07-15T14:22:33Z"},{"id":14194,"html_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/dog/opencode-acp/issues/20#issuecomment-14194","pull_request_url":"","issue_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/dog/opencode-acp/issues/20","user":{"id":1,"login":"dog","login_name":"","source_id":0,"full_name":"","email":"dog@noreply.localhost","avatar_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/avatars/707bc216f1ab0193186b3712bbd8b1ad","html_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/dog","language":"","is_admin":false,"last_login":"0001-01-01T00:00:00Z","created":"2026-03-23T02:18:35Z","restricted":false,"active":false,"prohibit_login":false,"location":"","website":"","description":"","visibility":"public","followers_count":1,"following_count":0,"starred_repos_count":0,"username":"dog"},"original_author":"","original_author_id":0,"body":"你这个根因不太对吧？我们之前也会有类似的消息。我理解这种消息模型，不是看不见吗？它怎么会响应呢？我给你的那个链接是我能看到的消息，不一定是模型能看到的。现在你需要确认：模型是不是能看到那条消息。另一个问题是：模型说他好像看到了有人重复他说的话，那明显不像是那条消息","assets":[],"created_at":"2026-07-15T14:24:19Z","updated_at":"2026-07-15T14:24:19Z"},{"id":14195,"html_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/dog/opencode-acp/issues/20#issuecomment-14195","pull_request_url":"","issue_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/dog/opencode-acp/issues/20","user":{"id":3,"login":"awork","login_name":"","source_id":0,"full_name":"","email":"awork@noreply.localhost","avatar_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/avatars/3a6e67811caadb37b9004123cfec7a13","html_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/awork","language":"","is_admin":false,"last_login":"0001-01-01T00:00:00Z","created":"2026-05-24T14:49:10Z","restricted":false,"active":false,"prohibit_login":false,"location":"","website":"","description":"","visibility":"public","followers_count":0,"following_count":0,"starred_repos_count":0,"username":"awork"},"original_author":"","original_author_id":0,"body":"[system] ✓ Message broadcasted to: **awork** (`ses_0b89319b1ffeK25eKU3GMfCK8U`, `/home/dog/projects/opencode-acp`).","assets":[],"created_at":"2026-07-15T14:24:21Z","updated_at":"2026-07-15T14:24:21Z"},{"id":14197,"html_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/dog/opencode-acp/issues/20#issuecomment-14197","pull_request_url":"","issue_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/dog/opencode-acp/issues/20","user":{"id":3,"login":"awork","login_name":"","source_id":0,"full_name":"","email":"awork@noreply.localhost","avatar_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/avatars/3a6e67811caadb37b9004123cfec7a13","html_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/awork","language":"","is_admin":false,"last_login":"0001-01-01T00:00:00Z","created":"2026-05-24T14:49:10Z","restricted":false,"active":false,"prohibit_login":false,"location":"","website":"","description":"","visibility":"public","followers_count":0,"following_count":0,"starred_repos_count":0,"username":"awork"},"original_author":"","original_author_id":0,"body":"[bot]\n\n你说得对，我之前的根因分析有误。修正如下：\n\n## 确认结果\n\n**模型看不到那条 debug 消息。** 我查了 ACP context log（`~/.config/opencode/logs/acp/context/ses_0b2cd5a70ffeQQjqa0uABNjqsW/2026-07-15T14-10-51-431Z.json`），模型收到的 240 条消息里：\n\n- `ignored: true` 的消息：**0 条**\n- `[ACP Debug]` 内容：**0 条**\n\n`isIgnoredUserMessage()` 正确过滤了。模型确实看不见。\n\n## 真正的问题\n\n但 `session.prompt()` **触发了一个不该发生的 model turn**。\n\n时间线（从 DB 查的精确时间戳）：\n\n| 时间戳 | 消息 | 说明 |\n|--------|------|------|\n| 1784124640312 | assistant `f661d8c38` | \"这个方案有法律风险...\" |\n| 1784124640384 | user `f661d8c80` | **debug 通知**（72ms 后） |\n| 1784124651363 | assistant `f661db763` | \"理解正确...\"（11s 后） |\n\n`sendIgnoredMessage` 调用 `client.session.prompt({ noReply: true, ... })`。`noReply: true` **没有被遵守** — opencode 仍然创建了一个 model turn。\n\n这个 turn 的 context（14:10:51 log）：\n- 最后一条 user 消息：msg 237（[SYSTEM FORWARD] AGPL/MIT 问题）\n- msg 237 之后全是 assistant（238-239 = 刚才的法律分析）\n- **最后一条消息是 assistant** — 模型看不到任何新的 user 输入\n\n模型被调用了，但上下文里没有新的 user 消息。它看到自己的法律分析是最后一条消息，于是推理出：\n\n\u003e \"The user sent a message that looks like a summary of my previous reply.\"\n\n这就是\"有人重复他说的话\"的来源 — 模型在**合理化**为什么自己被调用。它看不到新 user 消息，只能假设 user 发了什么东西。\n\n## 根因\n\n`sendIgnoredMessage` → `client.session.prompt()` 在 transform hook 内被调用，`noReply: true` 没有阻止 model turn。通知本身被正确过滤，但 **turn 被触发了**，模型在无新输入的情况下被调用 → 困惑 → 幻觉。\n\n## 修复\n\n和之前一样：把 hooks.ts 的 `debugNotify` 从 `sendIgnoredMessage` 改成 `logger.debug`。一行改动，要我现在改吗？","assets":[],"created_at":"2026-07-15T14:29:46Z","updated_at":"2026-07-15T14:29:46Z"},{"id":14198,"html_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/dog/opencode-acp/issues/20#issuecomment-14198","pull_request_url":"","issue_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/dog/opencode-acp/issues/20","user":{"id":1,"login":"dog","login_name":"","source_id":0,"full_name":"","email":"dog@noreply.localhost","avatar_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/avatars/707bc216f1ab0193186b3712bbd8b1ad","html_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/dog","language":"","is_admin":false,"last_login":"0001-01-01T00:00:00Z","created":"2026-03-23T02:18:35Z","restricted":false,"active":false,"prohibit_login":false,"location":"","website":"","description":"","visibility":"public","followers_count":1,"following_count":0,"starred_repos_count":0,"username":"dog"},"original_author":"","original_author_id":0,"body":"通知本身被正确过滤，但 turn 被触发了，模型在无新输入的情况下被调用 → 困惑 → 幻觉。 这个能不触发新的一轮绘画吗？我理解它应该是个空画、空消息。我看你后台也在不停地发待命。","assets":[],"created_at":"2026-07-15T14:31:36Z","updated_at":"2026-07-15T14:31:36Z"},{"id":14199,"html_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/dog/opencode-acp/issues/20#issuecomment-14199","pull_request_url":"","issue_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/dog/opencode-acp/issues/20","user":{"id":3,"login":"awork","login_name":"","source_id":0,"full_name":"","email":"awork@noreply.localhost","avatar_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/avatars/3a6e67811caadb37b9004123cfec7a13","html_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/awork","language":"","is_admin":false,"last_login":"0001-01-01T00:00:00Z","created":"2026-05-24T14:49:10Z","restricted":false,"active":false,"prohibit_login":false,"location":"","website":"","description":"","visibility":"public","followers_count":0,"following_count":0,"starred_repos_count":0,"username":"awork"},"original_author":"","original_author_id":0,"body":"[system] ✓ Message broadcasted to: **awork** (`ses_0b89319b1ffeK25eKU3GMfCK8U`, `/home/dog/projects/opencode-acp`).","assets":[],"created_at":"2026-07-15T14:31:37Z","updated_at":"2026-07-15T14:31:37Z"},{"id":14200,"html_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/dog/opencode-acp/issues/20#issuecomment-14200","pull_request_url":"","issue_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/dog/opencode-acp/issues/20","user":{"id":3,"login":"awork","login_name":"","source_id":0,"full_name":"","email":"awork@noreply.localhost","avatar_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/avatars/3a6e67811caadb37b9004123cfec7a13","html_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/awork","language":"","is_admin":false,"last_login":"0001-01-01T00:00:00Z","created":"2026-05-24T14:49:10Z","restricted":false,"active":false,"prohibit_login":false,"location":"","website":"","description":"","visibility":"public","followers_count":0,"following_count":0,"starred_repos_count":0,"username":"awork"},"original_author":"","original_author_id":0,"body":"[bot]\n\n确认你的理解完全正确——它**本应该**是空画/空消息，但 opencode 没有真正尊重 `noReply: true`。\n\n**根因**：`sendIgnoredMessage()`（`lib/ui/notification.ts:317`）通过 `client.session.prompt({ body: { noReply: true, ... } })` 发送通知。opencode 在收到这个 prompt 调用后**仍然触发了一个完整的模型 turn**，无视 `noReply`。\n\n**循环机制**（你看到的\"不停发待命\"）：\n1. transform hook 运行 → `debugNotify` 调用 `sendIgnoredMessage`\n2. `session.prompt()` 触发模型 turn\n3. 模型上下文最后一条是自己的 assistant 输出（通知被 `isIgnoredUserMessage` 正确过滤了，模型看不到）→ 困惑 → 输出\"待命\"\n4. \"待命\"又触发 transform hook → 回到第 1 步 → 死循环\n\n**修复方案**：把 `debugNotify`（`lib/hooks.ts:282-292`）从 `sendIgnoredMessage` 改成 `logger.debug`（纯文件日志，不调用 `session.prompt`，不触发任何 turn）。debug 信息仍然写入 `logs/acp/daily/` 日志文件，只是不再出现在聊天 UI 里。\n\n这是插件层面能做的最干净的修复——`noReply` 不被尊重是 opencode 核心行为，插件无法绕过。我现在从 master 切分支实现。","assets":[],"created_at":"2026-07-15T14:33:14Z","updated_at":"2026-07-15T14:33:14Z"},{"id":14204,"html_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/dog/opencode-acp/issues/20#issuecomment-14204","pull_request_url":"","issue_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/dog/opencode-acp/issues/20","user":{"id":3,"login":"awork","login_name":"","source_id":0,"full_name":"","email":"awork@noreply.localhost","avatar_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/avatars/3a6e67811caadb37b9004123cfec7a13","html_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/awork","language":"","is_admin":false,"last_login":"0001-01-01T00:00:00Z","created":"2026-05-24T14:49:10Z","restricted":false,"active":false,"prohibit_login":false,"location":"","website":"","description":"","visibility":"public","followers_count":0,"following_count":0,"starred_repos_count":0,"username":"awork"},"original_author":"","original_author_id":0,"body":"[bot]\n\n已修复并部署。PR #149：https://github.com/ranxianglei/opencode-acp/pull/149\n\n**改动**（1 个 commit，`lib/hooks.ts`）：\n- `debugNotify` 回调从 `sendIgnoredMessage(...)` 改为 `logger.debug(...)`\n- 不再调用 `session.prompt()` → 不触发任何模型 turn\n- debug 信息仍写入 `logs/acp/daily/` 日志文件，只是不在聊天 UI 显示\n\n**验证**：\n- typecheck 0 errors\n- 713/713 测试通过\n- 已 dev-deploy 部署，bundle 验证 `logger.debug` 替换了原调用\n\n**重启 opencode 后生效**。你的\"待命\"循环应该会停止——debug 通知不再触发 phantom turn。\n\n`sendIgnoredMessage` 保留给压缩通知等其他路径使用，只有 debug 回调改了。","assets":[],"created_at":"2026-07-15T14:36:15Z","updated_at":"2026-07-15T14:36:15Z"},{"id":14213,"html_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/dog/opencode-acp/issues/20#issuecomment-14213","pull_request_url":"","issue_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/dog/opencode-ac