300/dog/opencode-acp/issues/20#issuecomment-14238","pull_request_url":"","issue_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/dog/opencode-acp/issues/20","user":{"id":3,"login":"awork","login_name":"","source_id":0,"full_name":"","email":"awork@noreply.localhost","avatar_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/avatars/3a6e67811caadb37b9004123cfec7a13","html_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/awork","language":"","is_admin":false,"last_login":"0001-01-01T00:00:00Z","created":"2026-05-24T14:49:10Z","restricted":false,"active":false,"prohibit_login":false,"location":"","website":"","description":"","visibility":"public","followers_count":0,"following_count":0,"starred_repos_count":0,"username":"awork"},"original_author":"","original_author_id":0,"body":"[bot] 分析了根因，确认可以修复。\n\n## 问题根因\n\n`debugNotify` 回调（`lib/hooks.ts:282-292`）调用 `sendIgnoredMessage()`，而 `sendIgnoredMessage`（`lib/ui/notification.ts:299-338`）内部调用的是 **`client.session.prompt()`**：\n\n```typescript\nawait client.session.prompt({\n    body: {\n        noReply: true,          // ← 期望不触发回复\n        parts: [{ type: \"text\", text, ignored: true }],\n    },\n})\n```\n\n**`noReply: true` 没有被 opencode 真正尊重** — `session.prompt()` 仍然会触发一次完整的模型调用。`ignored: true` 只保证了通知内容被过滤（模型看不到），但 **turn 本身照常执行**。\n\n结果链：\n1. debug 通知 → `session.prompt()` → 触发模型 turn\n2. 模型收到的 context 中最后一条是自己的 assistant 输出（没有新 user 输入）\n3. 模型困惑 → 幻觉（\"user sent a summary of my previous reply\" / \"待命\"）\n4. 幻觉响应触发 message-transform hook → 又触发 debug 通知 → **死循环**\n\n你看到的 \"不停地发待命\" 就是这个循环。\n\n## 修复方案\n\ndebug 通知改用 `logger.debug()`（纯文件日志，零 session 活动）：\n\n```typescript\n// lib/hooks.ts:282-292 改为：\nconfig.debug\n    ? (text: string) =\u003e {\n          logger.debug(\"[ACP Debug] Nudge injected\", { text })\n      }\n    : undefined,\n```\n\n一行改动，完全不调用 `session.prompt()`，不触发任何 turn。\n\n**权衡**：debug 信息不再显示在聊天 UI 中，只写入 `~/.config/opencode/logs/acp/` 日志文件。如果需要在 UI 中看 debug 信息，需要 opencode 上游修复 `noReply: true` 的语义。\n\n需要我切分支实现吗？","assets":[],"created_at":"2026-07-15T15:55:24Z","u