20% 阈值 |\n\nACP 认为 GLM-5.2 有 1M context，实际只用了 ~8%，所以不触发 nudge。\n\n### 为什么模型自己说满了？\n\n模型 **自己知道它的 context limit 不是 1M**（可能 128K 或 256K）。它看到：\n- 308 条消息\n- 44 个压缩摘要（recap tool results）\n- 每条消息的 `\u003cdcp-message-id tokens=\"...\"\u003e` 标注\n\n→ 自己算出来 ~78K / 128K ≈ **61%**，或者看到 308 条消息觉得很多，就主动说\"上下文已满\"。\n\n### 根本原因：**modelContextLimit 检测不准**\n\nACP 检测到 1M，但模型实际 context limit 可能小得多。这是一个配置/检测问题。\n\n要不要我查一下 `modelContextLimit` 是怎么检测出来的？如果是 SDK 给的值不对，可能需要用模型实际返回的 token 数据来校准。","assets":[],"created_at":"2026-07-15T16:42:29Z","updated_at":"2026-07-15T16:42:29Z"},{"id":14265,"html_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/dog/opencode-acp/issues/20#issuecomment-14265","pull_request_url":"","issue_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/dog/opencode-acp/issues/20","user":{"id":1,"login":"dog","login_name":"","source_id":0,"full_name":"","email":"dog@noreply.localhost","avatar_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/avatars/707bc216f1ab0193186b3712bbd8b1ad","html_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/dog","language":"","is_admin":false,"last_login":"0001-01-01T00:00:00Z","created":"2026-03-23T02:18:35Z","restricted":false,"active":false,"prohibit_login":false,"location":"","website":"","description":"","visibility":"public","followers_count":1,"following_count":0,"starred_repos_count":0,"username":"dog"},"original_author":"","original_author_id":0,"body":"那么一定是吧压缩提示的到用户消息注入关闭了 消息任何压缩都看不到注入 怀疑又有新 bug","assets":[],"created_at":"2026-07-15T16:59:05Z","updated_at":"2026-07-15T16:59:05Z"},{"id":14266,"html_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/dog/opencode-acp/issues/20#issuecomment-14266","pull_request_url":"","issue_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/dog/opencode-acp/issues/20","user":{"id":3,"login":"awork","login_name":"","source_id":0,"full_name":"","email":"awork@noreply.localhost","avatar_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/avatars/3a6e67811caadb37b9004123cfec7a13","html_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/awork","language":"","is_admin":false,"last_login":"0001-01-01T00:00:00Z","created":"2026-05-24T14:49:10Z","restricte