← 第一层：growth \u003e= 50K\n    \u0026\u0026 (!filterSuppressed     // ← 第二层：filter 必须有推荐\n        || emergencyOverride)\n```\n\n### 三层阻断（全部是我加的）\n\n| 提交 | 改动 | 效果 |\n|------|------|------|\n| `914f004` growth floor gate | `nudgeAllowed` 需要 growth \u003e= 22.5K | 模型在 50K growth 前自压缩 → 永远不达标 |\n| `f0cfbb5` nudgeAllowed requires shouldNudge | growth 需要 \u003e= 50K (1M model) | 阈值太高 |\n| `0bae749` PR #147 filterSuppressed | filter 无推荐时阻断 | 即使 growth 达标，filter 也能阻断 |\n\n**三层叠加 = nudge 永远不注入。** v1.12.6 的 `hasActiveNudgeAnchors` 旁路（anchors 活跃就注入 breakdown）被我删了。\n\n### 为什么模型还在压缩\n\n模型看到 `\u003cdcp-message-id tokens=\"...\" type=\"...\"\u003e` 标注，自己算 token 总量，自己判断满了就压缩。**不需要 ACP nudge 也能压缩——但缺少推荐范围列表，所以盲目压缩（包括危险的最后一段）。**\n\n### 修复方案\n\n回退到 v1.12.6 的行为：\n1. `applyAnchoredNudges` 恢复无条件调用（或至少 `hasActiveNudgeAnchors` 时调用）\n2. breakdown 注入条件恢复 `decision.shouldNudge || hasActiveNudgeAnchors`\n3. 删除或大幅降低 `filterSuppressed` 门\n\n要我从 master 切分支修吗？","assets":[],"created_at":"2026-07-15T17:11:30Z","updated_at":"2026-07-15T17:11:30Z"},{"id":14287,"html_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/dog/opencode-acp/issues/20#issuecomment-14287","pull_request_url":"","issue_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/dog/opencode-acp/issues/20","user":{"id":1,"login":"dog","login_name":"","source_id":0,"full_name":"","email":"dog@noreply.localhost","avatar_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/avatars/707bc216f1ab0193186b3712bbd8b1ad","html_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/dog","language":"","is_admin":false,"last_login":"0001-01-01T00:00:00Z","created":"2026-03-23T02:18:35Z","restricted":false,"active":false,"prohibit_login":false,"location":"","website":"","description":"","visibility":"public","followers_count":1,"following_count":0,"starred_repos_count":0,"username":"dog"},"original_author":"","original_author_id":0,"body":"http://m1.redoxos.org:1195/sessions/ses_0b2cd5a70ffeQQjqa0uABNjqsW#mmsg_f66c908a50012RqwmB5NRx5z19\n你这个不能走这个极端或者就走那个极端呀。现在问题是，我看每个模型都在压缩，但是并没有注入压缩的消息。需要确定为什么它们都在压缩，你给的那个理由根本就不充分。有一个标签就不代表它一定要压缩，之前有那个标签它也不会压缩。现在我看它隔一段时间就压缩，压缩的频率也不是太频繁，也没有过度压缩。问题是现在我根本就看不到注入消息，之前有一个注入消息会打到用户列表里面。自从你把一些 Debug 消息都打到日志里面去，我连原来的用户消息都看不见了。这里需要确认是没有注入，还是注入了只是没打到用户消息里面。","assets":[],"created_at":"2026-07-16T00:05:17Z","updated_at":"2026-07-16T00:05:17Z"},{"id":14288,"html_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/dog/opencode-acp/issues/20#issuecomment-14288","pull_request_url":"","issue_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/dog/opencode-acp/issues/20","user":{"id":3,"login":"awork","login_name":"","source_id":0,"full_name":"","email":"awork@noreply.localhost","avatar_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/avatars/3a6e67811caadb37b9004123cfec7a13","html_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/awork","language":"","is_admin":false,"last_login":"0001-01-01T00:00:00Z","created":"2026-05-24T14:49:10Z","restricted":false,"active":false,"prohibit_login":false,"location":"","website":"","description":"","visibility":"public","followers_count":0,"following_count":0,"starred_repos_count":0,"username":"awork"},"original_author":"","original_author_id":0,"body":"[system] ✓ Message broadcasted to: **awork** (`ses_0b89319b1ffeK25eKU3GMfCK8U`, `/home/dog/projects/opencode-acp`).","assets":[],"created_at":"2026-07-16T00:05:19Z","updated_at":"2026-07-16T00:05:19Z"},{"id":14289,"html_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/dog/opencode-acp/issues/20#issuecomment-14289","pull_request_url":"","issue_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/dog/opencode-acp/issues/20","user":{"id":3,"login":"awork","login_name":"","source_id":0,"full_name":"","email":"awork@noreply.localhost","avatar_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/avatars/3a6e67811caadb37b9004123cfec7a13","html_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/awork","language":"","is_admin":false,"last_login":"0001-01-01T00:00:00Z","created":"2026-05-24T14:49:10Z","restricted":false,"active":false,"prohibit_login":false,"location":"","website":"","description":"","visibility":"public","followers_count":0,"following_count":0,"starred_repos_count":0,"username":"awork"},"original_author":"","original_author_id":0,"body":"[system] ✅ **awork** completed (3 min)","assets":[],"created_at":"2026-07-16T00:05:47Z","updated_at":"2026-07-16T00:09:07Z"},{"id":14291,"html_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/dog/opencode-acp/issues/20#issuecomment-14291","pull_request_url":"","issue_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/dog/opencode-acp/issues/20","user":{"id":3,"login":"awork","login_name":"","source_id":0,"full_name":"","email":"awork@noreply.localhost","avatar_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/avatars/3a6e67811caadb37b9004123cfec7a13","html_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/awork","language":"","is_admin":false,"last_login":"0001-01-01T00:00:00Z","created":"2026-05-24T14:49:10Z","restricted":false,"active":false,"prohibit_login":false,"location":"","website":"","description":"","visibility":"public","followers_count":0,"following_count":0,"starred_repos_count":0,"username":"awork"},"original_author":"","original_author_id":0,"body":"[bot]\n\n更正我之前的错误分析。查到了确凿证据：\n\n### 确认：**有注入，但没打到用户消息列表**\n\n查了目标消息的 context log（`2026-07-15T17-17-58-872Z.json`，135 条消息），**最后一条（idx 134）就是 nudge**：\n\n```\nrole: user\nContext: 166.0K tokens.\n\nThis is an efficiency nudge to compress early...\nCompression Philosophy: ...\nBreakdown: ...\n```\n\n模型的 reasoning 直接引用了它：\"Let me also compress the consumed ranges **as the nudge suggests**, since I have 75.9K of consumed work (m02188-m02241)\"\n\n→ **模型确实看到了 nudge，也确实因为 nudge 而压缩。** 我之前说\"0 注入\"是因为搜索模式太窄（搜 `[ACP] Context:` 但实际格式是 `Context:`）。\n\n### 为什么你看不到\n\n两个原因叠加：\n\n**1. Nudge 本身是 suffix message（临时消息）**\n\n`createSuffixMessage()` 创建的 user 消息是 **ephemeral** — 只存在于发给模型的 messages 数组里，**不写 DB**，所以在聊天界面看不到。这个设计一直如此。\n\n**2. 我把 debugNotify 从 sendIgnoredMessage 改成了 logger.debug**\n\n```js\n// 部署的代码（hooks.ts line ~10592）：\nconfig.debug ? (text) =\u003e {\n    logger.debug(`[ACP Debug] Nudge injected:\\n${text}`);  // ← 只写日志\n} : void 0,\n```\n\n之前是 `sendIgnoredMessage(client, ...)` → 会创建 visible user message（`ignored: true`）。我为了修 phantom turn bug（debug notification 每次触发新模型 turn）改成了 `logger.debug`。\n\n**这就是\"自从你把 Debug 消息打到日志去，我就看不见了\"的原因。**\n\n### 总结\n\n| 问题 | 答案 |\n|------|------|\n| 有没有注入？ | **有** — suffix message 打到模型 context |\n| 模型看得到吗？ | **看得到** — reasoning 直接引用 |\n| 用户看得到吗？ | **看不到** — suffix 是临时的 + debugNotify 改成了 logger |\n| 之前为什么看得到？ | debugNotify 用 sendIgnoredMessage → 创建 visible user message |\n| 为什么改？ | 修 phantom turn bug（每次 debug notification 触发新 turn） |\n\n需要把 debug visibility 恢复回来吗？可以选择：\n1. 恢复 `sendIgnoredMessage` 但接受 phantom turn 问题\n2. 找一个不触发 turn 的方式显示消息（需要看 opencode SDK 有没有支持）","assets":[],"created_at":"2026-07-16T00:08:58Z","updated_at":"2026-07-16T00:08:58Z"},{"id":14292,"html_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/dog/opencode-acp/issues/20#issuecomment-14292","pull_request_url":"","issue_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/dog/opencode-acp/issues/20","user":{"id":1,"login":"dog","login_name":"","source_id":0,"full_name":"","email":"dog@noreply.localhost","avatar_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/avatars/707bc216f1ab0193186b3712bbd8b1ad","html_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/dog","language":"","is_admin":false,"last_login":"0001-01-01T00:00:00Z","created":"2026-03-23T02:18:35Z","restricted":false,"active":false,"prohibit_login":false,"location":"","website":"","description":"","visibility":"public","followers_count":1,"following_count":0,"starred_repos_count":0,"username":"dog"},"original_author":"","original_author_id":0,"body":"你需要进一步确认，假设真的是你说的这个原因的话，那么日志里应该有他注入的原话，你去日志里去看，必须所有的猜测都有证据才行。","assets":[],"created_at":"2026-07-16T00:10:23Z","updated_at":"2026-07-16T00:10:23Z"},{"id":14293,"html_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/dog/opencode-acp/issues/20#issuecomment-14293","pull_request_url":"","issue_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/dog/opencode-acp/issues/20","user":{"id":3,"login":"awork","login_name":"","source_id":0,"full_name":"","email":"awork@noreply.localhost","avatar_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/avatars/3a6e67811caadb37b9004123cfec7a13","html_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/awork","language":"","is_admin":false,"last_login"