ibit_login":false,"location":"","website":"","description":"","visibility":"public","followers_count":0,"following_count":0,"starred_repos_count":0,"username":"awork"},"original_author":"","original_author_id":0,"body":"[bot]\n\n查了日志，有确凿证据。三处对齐：\n\n### 证据链\n\n**1. Daily log（`~/.config/opencode/logs/acp/daily/2026-07-15.log` line 852032）**\n\n目标消息时间 `2026-07-15T17:17:58`，日志里同一时间戳 `17:17:58.874Z` 有完整 nudge 原文：\n\n```\n[ACP Debug] Nudge injected:\nContext: 166.0K tokens.\n\nThis is an efficiency nudge to compress early...\n\nBreakdown: 131.9K tool (64%) | 773 summaries (1%) | 774 code (1%) | 72.8K text (35%) (+55.3K since last nudge)\n⚠️ 22.7K tokens are protected — not compressible. Effective compressible: ~182.7K.\n\nCompressible ranges (oldest first):\n  m00002–m00002  1 msgs  20.3K [PROTECTED: skill, read]\n  m00046–m00046  1 msgs  147 [tool 100%]\n  ...\n```\n\n**2. Context log（`2026-07-15T17-17-58-872Z.json` idx 134/135）**\n\n发给模型的 messages 数组最后一条，`role: user`，内容与日志完全一致。\n\n**3. 模型 reasoning（DB `msg_f66c908a5`）**\n\n\u003e \"Let me also compress the consumed ranges **as the nudge suggests**, since I have 75.9K of consumed work (m02188-m02241)\"\n\n三处对齐：日志写了 → context log 有 → 模型引用了。\n\n### 为什么用户看不到\n\n部署的代码（`hooks.ts` line ~10592）：\n\n```js\nconfig.debug ? (text) =\u003e {\n    logger.debug(`[ACP Debug] Nudge injected:\\n${text}`);  // ← 只写日志\n} : void 0,\n```\n\n之前是 `sendIgnoredMessage(...)` → 创建 visible user message。我改成 `logger.debug` 修 phantom turn bug → 用户界看不到了。\n\n**nudge 本身（suffix message）一直就是 ephemeral**，不写 DB。之前能看到是因为 `debugNotify` 用 `sendIgnoredMessage` 把内容也打到用户消息列表了。现在改成 `logger.debug` 就只剩日志。","assets":[],"created_at":"2026-07-16T00:11:16Z","updated_at":"2026-07-16T00:11:16Z"},{"id":14298,"html_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/dog/opencode-acp/issues/20#issuecomment-14298","pull_request_url":"","issue_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/dog/opencode-acp/issues/20","user":{"id":1,"login":"dog","login_name":"","source_id":0,"full_name":"","email":"dog@noreply.localhost","avatar_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/avatars/707bc216f1ab0193186b3712bbd8b1ad","html_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/dog","language":"","is_admin":false,"last_login":"0001-01-01T00:00:00Z","created":"2026-03-23T02:18:35Z","restricted":false,"active":false,"prohibit_login":false,"location":"","website":"","description":"","visibility":"public","followers_count":1,"following_count":0,"starred_repos_count":0,"username":"dog"},"original_author":"","original_author_id":0,"body":"那你之前是因为有很多 Debug 消息打到控制台，导致模型会收到一些空消息，是这个原因把它给取消掉了吗？但是正常的注入提醒以前不是也是打到控制台吗？现在问题是如果 send ignore 到底会不会还会产生空消息？这个空消息就很奇怪，理论上它是我们已经把消息过滤掉了，为什么还会提示模型呢？","assets":[],"created_at":"2026-07-16T00:15:20Z","updated_at":"2026-07-16T00:15:20Z"},{"id":14299,"html_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/dog/opencode-acp/issues/20#issuecomment-14299","pull_request_url":"","issue_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/dog/opencode-acp/issues/20","user":{"id":3,"login":"awork","login_name":"","source_id":0,"full_name":"","email":"awork@noreply.localhost","avatar_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/avatars/3a6e67811caadb37b9004123cfec7a13","html_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/awork","language":"","is_admin":false,"last_login":"0001-01-01T00:00:00Z","created":"2026-05-24T14:49:10Z","restricted":false,"active":false,"prohibit_login":false,"location":"","website":"","description":"","visibility":"public","followers_count":0,"following_count":0,"starred_repos_count":0,"username":"awork"},"original_author":"","original_author_id":0,"body":"[system] ✓ Message broadcasted to: **awork** (`ses_0b89319b1ffeK25eKU3GMfCK8U`, `/home/dog/projects/opencode-acp`).","assets":[],"created_at":"2026-07-16T00:15:21Z","updated_at":"2026-07-16T00:15:21Z"},{"id":14300,"html_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/dog/opencode-acp/issues/20#issuecomment-14300","pull_request_url":"","issue_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/dog/opencode-acp/issues/20","user":{"id":3,"login":"awork","login_name":"","source_id":0,"full_name":"","email":"awork@noreply.localhost","avatar_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/avatars/3a6e67811caadb37b9004123cfec7a13","html_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/awork","language":"","is_admin":false,"last_login":"0001-01-01T00:00:00Z","created":"2026-05-24T14:49:10Z","restricted":false,"active":false,"prohibit_login":false,"location":"","website":"","description":"","visibility":"public","followers_count":0,"following_count":0,"starred_repos_count":0,"username":"awork"},"original_author":"","original_author_id":0,"body":"[system] ✅ **awork** completed (1 min)","assets":[],"created_at":"2026-07-16T00:15:47Z","updated_at":"2026-07-16T00:16:27Z"},{"id":14302,"html_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/dog/opencode-acp/issues/20#issuecomment-14302","pull_request_url":"","issue_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/dog/opencode-acp/issues/20","user":{"id":3,"login":"awork","login_name":"","source_id":0,"full_name":"","email":"awork@noreply.localhost","avatar_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/avatars/3a6e67811caadb37b9004123cfec7a13","html_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/awork","language":"","is_admin":false,"last_login":"0001-01-01T00:00:00Z","created":"2026-05-24T14:49:10Z","restricted":false,"active":false,"prohibit_login":false,"location":"","website":"","description":"","visibility":"public","followers_count":0,"following_count":0,"starred_repos_count":0,"username":"awork"},"original_author":"","original_author_id":0,"body":"[bot]\n\n逐个回答：\n\n### 1. \"之前是因为 Debug 消息导致模型收到空消息，所以取消的？\"\n\n**是的。** `debugNotify` 之前用 `sendIgnoredMessage` → 调 `client.session.prompt({ noReply: true })` → opencode **不尊重 `noReply: true`**，照样触发模型 turn。\n\n流程：\n```\nsendIgnoredMessage → session.prompt(noReply:true) → opencode 触发 turn\n→ transform hook 跑 → isIgnoredUserMessage 过滤掉 ignored 消息\n→ 模型 context 里没有新用户消息（最后一条是自己的 assistant 输出）\n→ 模型被调用但看不到新输入 → 困惑 → 输出\"待命\"或幻觉\n→ 又触发 transform hook → 又调 debugNotify → 又 sendIgnoredMessage → 循环\n```\n\n这就是你之前看到的\"后台不停地发待命\"。\n\n### 2. \"正常的注入提醒以前不也是打到控制台吗？\"\n\n**是的。** `debugNotify` 回调同时发两类内容：\n- **filter 决策**：`[ACP Debug] Recommendation filter decision: ...`\n- **nudge 原文**：`[ACP Debug] Nudge injected:\\nContext: 166.0K tokens...`\n\n两类都通过 `sendIgnoredMessage` 打到用户消息列表。用户能看到，但每次都触发 phantom turn。\n\n### 3. \"如果恢复 sendIgnoredMessage 还会不会产生空消息？\"\n\n**会。** `sendIgnoredMessage` 的实现（部署代码 line 5155）：\n\n```js\nawait client.session.prompt({\n    body: {\n        noReply: true,           // ← opencode 不尊重这个\n        parts: [{ type: \"text\", text, ignored: true }]\n    }\n});\n```\n\n`noReply: true` **是 opencode SDK 的参数，但服务端没有正确实现**。调了 `session.prompt()` 就一定触发模型 turn。\n\n### 4. \"理论上已经过滤了消息，为什么还会提示模型？\"\n\n关键区别：\n\n| 层级 | 工作正常？ | 说明 |\n|------|-----------|------|\n| **消息内容过滤** | ✅ 正常 | `isIgnoredUserMessage()` 从 context 移除 `ignored:true` 消息，模型看不到内容 |\n| **turn 触发** | ❌ 不正常 | `session.prompt()` 总是触发 API call，不管 `noReply` |\n\n**过滤了内容，但没过滤 turn。** 模型被调用了（消耗 token），但看不到新输入 → phantom turn。\n\n### 根本问题\n\nopencode 的 `session.prompt()` 是创建 visible user message 的唯一 API，但它**总是触发模型 turn**。没有\"只显示消息不触发 turn\"的 API。\n\n这需要 opencode 侧修复 `noReply: true` 的支持，ACP 无法绕过。","assets":[],"created_at":"2026-07-16T00:16:20Z","updated_at":"2026-07-16T00:16:20Z"},{"id":14303,"html_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/dog/opencode-acp/issues/20#issuecomment-14303","pull_request_url":"","issue_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/dog/opencode-acp/issues/20","user":{"id":1,"login":"dog","login_name":"","source_id":0,"full_name":"","email":"dog@noreply.localhost","avatar_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/avatars/707bc216f1ab0193186b3712bbd8b1ad","html_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/dog","language":"","is_admin":false,"last_login":"0001-01-01T00:00:00Z","created":"2026-03-23T02:18:35Z","restricted":false,"active":false,"prohibit_login":false,"location":"","website":"","description":"","visibility":"public","followers_count":1,"following_count":0,"starred_repos_count":0,"username":"dog"},"original_author":"","original_author_id":0,"body":"你看下 projects 下面的 opencode stable 源码 进一步确认这个问题","assets":[],"created_at":"2