og/opencode-acp/issues/20#issuecomment-14306","pull_request_url":"","issue_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/dog/opencode-acp/issues/20","user":{"id":3,"login":"awork","login_name":"","source_id":0,"full_name":"","email":"awork@noreply.localhost","avatar_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/avatars/3a6e67811caadb37b9004123cfec7a13","html_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/awork","language":"","is_admin":false,"last_login":"0001-01-01T00:00:00Z","created":"2026-05-24T14:49:10Z","restricted":false,"active":false,"prohibit_login":false,"location":"","website":"","description":"","visibility":"public","followers_count":0,"following_count":0,"starred_repos_count":0,"username":"awork"},"original_author":"","original_author_id":0,"body":"[bot]\n\n查了 opencode-stable 源码（v1.14.41，就是你正在跑的版本，`/home/dog/.local/bin/opencode` → opencode-stable）。\n\n### 结论：`noReply: true` **是正确实现的**\n\n`packages/opencode/src/session/prompt.ts:1387`：\n\n```typescript\nconst prompt = Effect.fn(\"SessionPrompt.prompt\")(\n    function* (input: PromptInput) {\n        const session = yield* sessions.get(input.sessionID)\n        yield* revert.cleanup(session)\n        const message = yield* createUserMessage(input)    // ← 创建消息\n        yield* sessions.touch(input.sessionID)\n\n        // ... permissions setup ...\n\n        if (input.noReply === true) return message          // ← 直接返回，不调 loop()\n        return yield* loop({ sessionID: input.sessionID })  // ← loop() = 跑模型\n    },\n)\n```\n\n**`noReply: true` 时：**\n1. `createUserMessage(input)` — 创建 user message（写 DB）\n2. `sessions.touch()` — 更新 session 时间戳\n3. **直接 `return message`** — 不调 `loop()`\n4. `loop()` 是唯一跑模型的地方（line 1388）\n5. → **不触发模型 turn**\n\n**我之前说\"opencode 不尊重 noReply\"是错的。** 应该先查源码再下结论。\n\n### 这意味着什么\n\n`sendIgnoredMessage` 用 `noReply: true` 调 `session.prompt()` → 创建 visible user message → **不会触发 phantom turn**。可以安全恢复。\n\n### 那之前的 phantom turn 是怎么回事？\n\n可能是我误判。当时看到的\"待命\"回复可能不是 debug notification 触发的，而是正常的对话流程。需要重新验证才能确定。\n\n### 建议\n\n把 `debugNotify` 从 `logger.debug` 恢复成 `sendIgnoredMessage`。既然 `noReply` 正常工作，用户就能重新在聊天界面看到 nudge 注入内容，且不会产生 phantom turn。","assets":[],"created_at":"2026-07-16T00:41:07Z","updated_at":"2026-07-16T00:41:07Z"},{"id":14322,"html_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/dog/opencode-acp/issues/20#issuecomment-14322","pull_request_url":"","issue_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/dog/opencode-acp/issues/20","user":{"id":1,"login":"dog","login_name":"","source_id":0,"full_name":"","email":"dog@noreply.localhost","avatar_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/avatars/707bc216f1ab0193186b3712bbd8b1ad","html_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/dog","language":"","is_admin":false,"last_login":"0001-01-01T00:00:00Z","created":"2026-03-23T02:18:35Z","restricted":false,"active":false,"prohibit_login":false,"location":"","website":"","description":"","visibility":"public","followers_count":1,"following_count":0,"starred_repos_count":0,"username":"dog"},"original_author":"","original_author_id":0,"body":"你这个根本就没有解决问题啊！我们现在之前把这个打开，打开以后它就是会发出不停的空消息，让模型一直以为有人在说话。你虽然开源码是这样的，但是还没有找到根本原因啊","assets":[],"created_at":"2026-07-16T00:57:52Z","updated_at":"2026-07-16T00:57:52Z"},{"id":14323,"html_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/dog/opencode-acp/issues/20#issuecomment-14323","pull_request_url":"","issue_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/dog/opencode-acp/issues/20","user":{"id":3,"login":"awork","login_name":"","source_id":0,"full_name":"","email":"awork@noreply.localhost","avatar_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/avatars/3a6e67811caadb37b9004123cfec7a13","html_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/awork","language":"","is_admin":false,"last_login":"0001-01-01T00:00:00Z","created":"2026-05-24T14:49:10Z","restricted":false,"active":false,"prohibit_login":false,"location":"","website":"","description":"","visibility":"public","followers_count":0,"following_count":0,"starred_repos_count":0,"username":"awork"},"original_author":"","original_author_id":0,"body":"[system] ✓ Message broadcasted to: **awork** (`ses_0b89319b1ffeK25eKU3GMfCK8U`, `/home/dog/projects/opencode-acp`).","assets":[],"created_at":"2026-07-16T00:57:54Z","updated_at":"2026-07-16T00:57:54Z"},{"id":14324,"html_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/dog/opencode-acp/issues/20#issuecomment-14324","pull_request_url":"","issue_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/dog/opencode-acp/issues/20","user":{"id":3,"login":"awork","login_name":"","source_id":0,"full_name":"","email":"awork@noreply.localhost","avatar_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/avatars/3a6e67811caadb37b9004123cfec7a13","html_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/awork","language":"","is_admin":false,"last_login":"0001-01-01T00:00:00Z","created":"2026-05-24T14:49:10Z","restricted":false,"active":false,"prohibit_login":false,"location":"","website":"","description":"","visibility":"public","followers_count":0,"following_count":0,"starred_repos_count":0,"username":"awork"},"original_author":"","original_author_id":0,"body":"[bot]\n\n找到根本原因了。`noReply: true` 确实阻止了**新的** `loop()` 启动，但问题出在**当前正在运行的** `loop()` 上。\n\n### 根本原因：loop 的退出条件不跳过 `ignored` 消息\n\n`prompt.ts` 的 `loop()` （`while(true)` line 1409）每轮迭代：\n\n```typescript\n// Line 1413: 拉取所有消息（包括 ignored:true）\nlet msgs = yield* MessageV2.filterCompactedEffect(sessionID)\n\n// Line 1419-1421: 从后往前找 lastUser\nfor (let i = msgs.length - 1; i \u003e= 0; i--) {\n    const msg = msgs[i]\n    if (!lastUser \u0026\u0026 msg.info.role === \"user\") lastUser = msg.info  // ← 不检查 ignored!\n    ...\n}\n\n// Line 1441-1449: 退出条件\nif (lastAssistant?.finish \u0026\u0026\n    !hasToolCalls \u0026\u0026\n    lastUser.id \u003c lastAssistant.id) {   // ← ignored 消息 id 更大 → 不退出!\n    break\n}\n```\n\n`filterCompacted`（`message-v2.ts:1101`）也**不过滤** `ignored: true` 消息。\n\n### 完整触发链\n\n```\n1. 用户发消息 → loop() 启动\n2. loop 迭代 1: transform hook 跑 → debugNotify → sendIgnoredMessage\n   → 创建 role:\"user\" + ignored:true 消息\n   → noReply:true 阻止新 loop() ✓\n   → 但当前 loop() 还在跑\n3. 模型生成回复 → loop 回到 while(true) 顶部\n4. loop 迭代 2:\n   a. filterCompactedEffect() → 拉到 ignored:true 的 user 消息\n   b. lastUser = ignored 消息（role:\"user\"，不检查 ignored）\n   c. 退出条件: lastUser.id \u003e lastAssistant.id → 不退出\n   d. line 1560: 正确跳过 ignored parts → 模型看不到新内容\n   e. 但模型还是被调用了 → phantom turn\n5. phantom turn 中 debugNotify 又触发 → 又创建消息 → loop 继续\n6. → 无限循环\n```\n\n**关键矛盾**：\n- `noReply: true` 阻止了**新的** `loop()` ✓\n- 但**当前的** `loop()` 把 `ignored:true` 消息当成真的 user 消息，不退出 ✗\n- line 1560 正确跳过了 ignored 内容 → 模型看不到新输入\n- 但模型还是被调用了 → 空转\n\n### 这是 opencode 的 bug\n\n`prompt.ts:1421` 的 `lastUser` 检测应该跳过 `ignored: true` 消息：\n\n```typescript\n// 当前（有 bug）:\nif (!lastUser \u0026\u0026 msg.info.role === \"user\") lastUser = msg.info\n\n// 修复:\nif (!lastUser \u0026\u0026 msg.info.role === \"user\" \n    \u0026\u0026 !msg.parts.every(p =\u003e p.ignored)) lastUser = msg.info\n```\n\n或者 `filterCompacted`（message-v2.ts:1101）应该过滤掉全 ignored 的消息。\n\n### ACP 侧的临时方案\n\n在 opencode 修复之前，ACP 不能在 transform hook 期间调 `sendIgnoredMessage`。当前的 `logger.debug` 是正确的临时方案——虽然用户看不到 nudge 内容，但不会产生 phantom turn。","assets":[],"created_at":"2026-07-16T00:59:49Z","updated_at":"2026-07-16T00:59:49Z"},{"id":14327,"html_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/dog/opencode-acp/issues/20#issuecomment-14327","pull_request_url":"","issue_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/dog/opencode-acp/issues/20","user":{"id":1,"login":"dog","login_name":"","source_id":0,"full_name":"","email":"dog@noreply.localhost","avatar_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/avatars/707bc216f1ab0193186b3712bbd8b1ad","html_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/dog","language":"","is_admin":false,"last_login":"0001-01-01T00:00:00Z","created":"2026-03-23T02:18:35Z","restricted":false,"active":false,"prohibit_login":false,"location":"","website":"","description":"","visibility":"public","followers_count":1,"following_count":0,"starred_repos_count":0,"username":"dog"},"original_author":"","original_author_id":0,"body":"https://github.com/anomalyco/opencode.git \n你看上游有这个问题吗？还是已经修复了","assets":[],"created_at":"2026-07-16T01:05:45Z","updated_at":"2026-07-16T01:05:45Z"},{