ll_name":"","email":"awork@noreply.localhost","avatar_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/avatars/3a6e67811caadb37b9004123cfec7a13","html_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/awork","language":"","is_admin":false,"last_login":"0001-01-01T00:00:00Z","created":"2026-05-24T14:49:10Z","restricted":false,"active":false,"prohibit_login":false,"location":"","website":"","description":"","visibility":"public","followers_count":0,"following_count":0,"starred_repos_count":0,"username":"awork"},"original_author":"","original_author_id":0,"body":"[bot]\n\n查了上游（anomalyco/opencode，v1.18.2）。**同样的 bug，没修。**\n\n### 上游对比\n\n| 检查点 | 上游 (v1.18.2) | stable (v1.14.41) | 有 bug？ |\n|--------|---------------|-------------------|----------|\n| `noReply: true` 实现 | `prompt.ts:1069` `if (noReply) return message` | `prompt.ts:1387` 同样 | ✅ 正确 |\n| `latest()` 找 `lastUser` | `message-v2.ts:585` — 不检查 `ignored` | `prompt.ts:1421` — 不检查 `ignored` | ❌ **同样有 bug** |\n| `filterCompacted()` | 不过滤 `ignored` 消息 | 同上 | ❌ **同样有 bug** |\n| loop 退出条件 | `lastUser.id \u003c lastAssistant.id` | 同上 | ❌ **同样有 bug** |\n| `ignored` 概念存在 | `message-v2.ts:206`（仅显示过滤） | 同上 | — |\n\n上游的 `latest()` 函数（`message-v2.ts:585`）：\n\n```typescript\nexport function latest(msgs: WithParts[]) {\n  for (const msg of msgs) {\n    if (info.role === \"user\" \u0026\u0026 (!user || info.id \u003e user.id)) user = info\n    //                                                  ↑ 不检查 ignored\n  }\n}\n```\n\n**`ignored` 只在显示层（`message-v2.ts:206`）过滤了，但 loop 的 `lastUser` 检测和退出条件都没过滤。**\n\n### 结论\n\n这是 opencode 原生的 bug，从 `noReply` + `ignored` 引入开始就存在。上游和我们 fork 的 stable 都有。需要向上游报 issue 或提 PR。","assets":[],"created_at":"2026-07-16T01:11:22Z","updated_at":"2026-07-16T01:11:22Z"},{"id":14333,"html_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/dog/opencode-acp/issues/20#issuecomment-14333","pull_request_url":"","issue_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/dog/opencode-acp/issues/20","user":{"id":1,"login":"dog","login_name":"","source_id":0,"full_name":"","email":"dog@noreply.