anguage":"","is_admin":false,"last_login":"0001-01-01T00:00:00Z","created":"2026-05-24T14:49:10Z","restricted":false,"active":false,"prohibit_login":false,"location":"","website":"","description":"","visibility":"public","followers_count":0,"following_count":0,"starred_repos_count":0,"username":"awork"},"original_author":"","original_author_id":0,"body":"[bot] 查了上游 anomalyco/opencode，相关 PR/Issue 情况：\n\n## `noReply` 的起源\n- **PR #3433**（merged, 2025-10-26）\"feat: add noReply parameter for silent message insertion\" — 这就是 `noReply` 的来源。核心只改了 6 行：`prompt.ts` 加了 `noReply: z.boolean().optional()` + 早返回逻辑。对应 Issue #3378（closed）\"Silent Message Insertion API\"。\n- 关键细节：作者自己在评论里强调 \"this does not interrupt the agent work, it just injects your message in the context\" —— 也就是说 `noReply` **只阻止调度新的 loop**，不管当前正在跑的 loop。\n\n## 想扩展到 command hook 的尝试（都没合并）\n- **PR #28763**（closed）+ **PR #27521**（closed）：想把 `noReply` 扩展到 `command.execute.before`，都被 automated-pr-cleanup 自动关了，没合并。\n- **Issue #26022**（closed）、**Issue #28417**（open，中文用户）：都在要 \"让插件能跳过 agent turn\" 的能力。说明上游也意识到缺这个能力，但一直没合并。\n\n## 相关但不是同一个 bug\n- **Issue #32010**（open）\"promptAsync message persisted but session loop never scheduled\"：反过来的问题 —— async 消息持久化了但 loop 根本没起来。跟我们 \"loop 不该起来却起来了\" 是镜像问题，都指向 `prompt.ts` 的 loop 调度逻辑有缺陷。\n\n## 我们发现的 bug：上游没人报\n搜了 `ignored message phantom turn loop`、`filterCompacted ignored` 等组合，**零命中**。也就是说：\n\n\u003e `prompt.ts` loop 的 `lastUser` 检测（line 1421: `if (!lastUser \u0026\u0026 msg.info.role === \"user\") lastUser = msg.info`）不跳过 `ignored: true` 的消息 —— 这个 bug **上游从未被报告过，也没有 PR 修复**。\n\n根因链（再确认一遍）：\n1. ACP 的 `sendIgnoredMessage` 用 `noReply: true` 插入 `ignored: true` 的 user 消息 ✓（设计正确）\n2. `noReply: true` 阻止了**新的** loop 调度 ✓（PR #3433 实现正确）\n3. **但是** 如果 `sendIgnoredMessage` 是在**当前 loop 迭代内**（transform hook 里）调用的，当前 loop 还在跑\n4. 当前 loop 下一轮迭代时 `filterCompactedEffect` 拉出所有消息（包括 `ignored`），`lastUser` 命中了那条 ignored 消息\n5. 退出条件 `lastUser.id \u003c lastAssistant.id` 失败 → loop 继续 → 模型被空调用 → 幻觉\n\n## 结论\n- 这是 opencode 上游的 bug，不是 ACP 的。ACP 侧我已经把 `debugNotify` 从 `sendIgnoredMessage` 改成 `logger.debug`，避开了这个触发路径。\n- 长期解法是给上游提 PR：`prompt.ts:1421` 加 `!msg.parts.every(p =\u003e p.ignored)` 判断，或者 `filterCompacted` 直接过滤掉全 ignored 的消息。\n- 要不要我起草一个上游 issue/PR？","assets":[],"created_at":"2026-07-16T01:14:35Z","updated_at":"2026-07-16T01:14:35Z"},{"id":14336,"html_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/dog/opencode-acp/issues/20#issuecomment-14336","pull_request_url":"","issue_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/dog/opencode-acp/issues/20","user":{"id":1,"login":"dog","login_name":"","source_id":0,"full_name":"","email":"dog@noreply.localhost","avatar_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/avatars/707bc216f1ab0193186b3712bbd8b1ad","html_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/dog","language":"","is_admin":false,"last_login":"0001-01-01T00:00:00Z","created":"2026-03-23T02:18:35Z","restricted":false,"active":false,"prohibit_login":false,"location":"","website":"","description":"","visibility":"public","followers_count":1,"following_count":0,"starred_repos_count":0,"username":"dog"},"original_author":"","original_author_id":0,"body":"起草一个上游 issue/PR\n\n搞一个吧，但是我感觉他们可能根本就不会理会这个问题，但是也可以搞一个","assets":[],"created_at":"2026-07-16T01:16:28Z","updated_at":"2026-07-16T01:16:28Z"},{"id":14337,"html_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/dog/opencode-acp/issues/20#issuecomment-14337","pull_request_url":"","issue_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/dog/opencode-acp/issues/20","user":{"id":3,"login":"awork","login_name":"","source_id":0,"full_name":"","email":"awork@noreply.localhost","avatar_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/avatars/3a6e67811caadb37b9004123cfec7a13","html_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/awork","language":"","is_admin":false,"last_login":"0001-01-01T00:00:00Z","created":"2026-05-24T14:49:10Z","restricted":false,"active":false,"prohibit_login":false,"location":"","website":"","description":"","visibility":"public","followers_count":0,"following_count":0,"starred_repos_count":0,"username":"awork"},"original_author