37b9004123cfec7a13","html_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/awork","language":"","is_admin":false,"last_login":"0001-01-01T00:00:00Z","created":"2026-05-24T14:49:10Z","restricted":false,"active":false,"prohibit_login":false,"location":"","website":"","description":"","visibility":"public","followers_count":0,"following_count":0,"starred_repos_count":0,"username":"awork"},"original_author":"","original_author_id":0,"body":"[bot] 分析清楚了，根因比之前理解的更深一层。\n\n## 为什么 turn 被触发\n\n`debugNotify` 回调（`lib/hooks.ts:284`）调用 `sendIgnoredMessage`，而这个调用是**异步不等待**的（`.catch(() =\u003e {})`，没有 `await`）。\n\n时间线（以你报告的 session `ses_0b2cd5a70ffe` 为例）：\n1. Transform hook 运行 → nudge 注入模型上下文 → `debugNotify(text)` 触发 `sendIgnoredMessage(...)` 异步发出\n2. Transform hook 返回 → 模型调用 → 模型生成回复（assistant msg，T=...312）\n3. **72ms 后**，异步 `sendIgnoredMessage` 完成 → ignored user message 写入 DB（T=...384）\n4. Loop 检查：lastUser（T=...384）\u003e lastAssistant（T=...312）→ **判定有新用户消息** → 不退出\n5. 模型再次被调用（无新输入）→ 幻觉回复（T=...363）\n\n`noReply: true` 只阻止**新 loop 调度**（`promptAsync`），不影响**当前 loop 的迭代检查**。`ignored: true` 只在 `toModelMessagesEffect` 里过滤，不影响 `lastUser` 检测。\n\n## 反馈循环（\"不停发待命\"）\n\n每次 phantom turn → 模型生成回复 → 触发 transform hook → 如果上下文仍然高于阈值 → nudge 再次注入 → `sendIgnoredMessage` → 又一个 phantom turn → ...\n\n这就是你看到的\"后台不停地发待命\"——每个 phantom 回复都是模型在无输入时的困惑输出。\n\n## 修复方案：用 toast 代替 sendIgnoredMessage\n\nopencode SDK 提供了 `client.tui.showToast()`——**瞬态通知，不写入 DB**，5 秒后自动消失。压缩完成通知在 `pruneNotificationType: \"toast\"` 时已经用了这个路径（`notification.ts:279`）。\n\n改动：`debugNotify` 回调从 `sendIgnoredMessage` → `client.tui.showToast()`：\n\n```typescript\n// hooks.ts:282-292 改为：\nconfig.debug \u0026\u0026 state.sessionId\n    ? (text: string) =\u003e {\n          client.tui.showToast({\n              body: {\n                  title: \"ACP: Nudge Injected\",\n                  message: text.slice(0, 500),\n                  variant: \"info\",\n                  duration: 5000,\n              },\n          }).catch(() =\u003e {})\n      }\n    : undefined,\n```\n\n效果：\n- ✅ TUI 可见（toast 弹窗，5 秒）\n- ✅ **不写入 DB** → loop 的 `lastUser` 检测看不到 → **零 phantom turn**\n- ✅ 打破反馈循环\n- ✅ 完整 nudge 文本仍在 debug 日志（`~/.config/opencode/logs/acp/`）里\n\n这是上游修复（opencode-stable PR #12 `isFullyIgnored` 检查）合并前的彻底本地解决方案。toast 和 sendIgnoredMessage 的区别就是前者不持久化消息。\n\n要我切分支改吗？改动就 hooks.ts 一处。","assets":[],"created_at":"2026-07-16T02:26:26Z","updated_at":"2026-07-16T02:26:26Z"},{"id":14368,"html_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/dog/opencode-acp/issues/20#issuecomment-14368","pull_request_url":"","issue_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/dog/opencode-acp/issues/20","user":{"id":1,"login":"dog","login_name":"","source_id":0,"full_name":"","email":"dog@noreply.localhost","avatar_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/avatars/707bc216f1ab0193186b3712bbd8b1ad","html_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/dog","language":"","is_admin":false,"last_login":"0001-01-01T00:00:00Z","created":"2026-03-23T02:18:35Z","restricted":false,"active":false,"prohibit_login":false,"location":"","website":"","description":"","visibility":"public","followers_count":1,"following_count":0,"starred_repos_count":0,"username":"dog"},"original_author":"","original_author_id":0,"body":"按照这个改一下吧。你之前是在哪个分支呢？现在你部署了哪个分支呢？要接新分支还是老分支啊？","assets":[],"created_at":"2026-07-16T02:32:31Z","updated_at":"2026-07-16T02:32:31Z"},{"id":14369,"html_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/dog/opencode-acp/issues/20#issuecomment-14369","pull_request_url":"","issue_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/dog/opencode-acp/issues/20","user":{"id":3,"login":"awork","login_name":"","source_id":0,"full_name":"","email":"awork@noreply.localhost","avatar_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/avatars/3a6e67811caadb37b9004123cfec7a13","html_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/awork","language":"","is_admin":false,"last_login":"0001-01-01T00:00:00Z","created":"2026-05-24T14:49:10Z","restricted":false,"active":false,"prohibit_login":false,"location":"","website":"","description":"","visibility":"public","followers_count":0,"following_count":0,"starr