dog/opencode-acp/issues/20","user":{"id":3,"login":"awork","login_name":"","source_id":0,"full_name":"","email":"awork@noreply.localhost","avatar_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/avatars/3a6e67811caadb37b9004123cfec7a13","html_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/awork","language":"","is_admin":false,"last_login":"0001-01-01T00:00:00Z","created":"2026-05-24T14:49:10Z","restricted":false,"active":false,"prohibit_login":false,"location":"","website":"","description":"","visibility":"public","followers_count":0,"following_count":0,"starred_repos_count":0,"username":"awork"},"original_author":"","original_author_id":0,"body":"[bot] 是的，能避免。这个问题已经修复了，正在发布。\n\n## 根因\n\n`sendIgnoredMessage`（用于 debug 通知）虽然在 transform hook 里同步调用，但它是 async 的，且通过 `.catch(()=\u003e{})` 不 await。结果：\n\n1. 通知消息**比模型回复更晚**写入 DB（timestamp 更大）\n2. opencode 主循环的 `lastUser` 检测（`prompt.ts:1421`）**只看 `role===\"user\"`，不看 `ignored` 字段**\n3. 于是循环退出条件 `lastUser.id \u003c lastAssistant.id` 失败 → 触发一次**无新输入的空 LLM 调用** → 模型困惑/幻觉\n4. 幻觉回复再次触发 transform hook → 再次注入 nudge → 再次 sendIgnoredMessage → **反馈循环**（就是你看到的\"不停发待命\"）\n\n`noReply:true` 只能阻止**新循环**调度，不影响**当前正在运行的循环**。`toModelMessagesEffect`（`message-v2.ts:802`）会把 `ignored` parts 过滤掉，所以模型实际看不到通知内容，但它仍然被调用。\n\n## 修复（PR #149 + #150，已 merge 到 master）\n\n**两层修复**：\n\n1. **PR #149**：过滤决策（每个 transform hook 都触发）从 `debugNotify` 改成 `logger.debug()`，只写文件日志，不进消息流。\n2. **PR #150**：`debugNotify` 回调本身从 `sendIgnoredMessage` 改成 `client.tui.showToast()`（瞬时 5s TUI 弹窗，**不写入 DB**）+ `logger.debug()`。从源头切断 phantom turn —— 不再有 ignored user msg 被持久化。\n\n你仍然能在 TUI 看到 nudge 注入通知（toast），但它不会触发新的一轮绘画了。\n\n## 上游 bug\n\n这本质是 opencode 上游的 bug —— `lastUser` 检测应该跳过 `ignored` 的消息。已提 issue：[anomalyco/opencode#37200](https://github.com/anomalyco/opencode/issues/37200)，并提交修复 PR：[ranxianglei/opencode-stable#12](https://github.com/ranxianglei/opencode-stable/pull/12)（`isFullyIgnored` 检查）。上游合并前，我们用 toast 规避。\n\n## 发布\n\nPR #151 已创建（v1.12.7 stable release），包含这 4 个 PR（#142, #147, #149, #150）。等你 merge 后 CI 自动发布到 npm latest。\n\nhttps://github.com/ranxianglei/opencode-acp/pull/151","assets":[],"created_at":"2026-07-17T01:54:55Z","updated_at":"2026-07-17T01:54:55Z"},{"id":14598,"html_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/dog/opencode-acp/issues/20#issuecomment-14598","pull_request_url":"","issue_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/dog/opencode-acp/issues/20","user":{"id":1,"login":"dog","login_name":"","source_id":0,"full_name":"","email":"dog@noreply.localhost","avatar_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/avatars/707bc216f1ab0193186b3712bbd8b1ad","html_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/dog","language":"","is_admin":false,"last_login":"0001-01-01T00:00:00Z","created":"2026-03-23T02:18:35Z","restricted":false,"active":false,"prohibit_login":false,"location":"","website":"","description":"","visibility":"public","followers_count":1,"following_count":0,"starred_repos_count":0,"username":"dog"},"original_author":"","original_author_id":0,"body":"看看现在本地部署和 npm 哪个版本是一个？","assets":[],"created_at":"2026-07-17T06:07:46Z","updated_at":"2026-07-17T06:07:46Z"},{"id":14599,"html_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/dog/opencode-acp/issues/20#issuecomment-14599","pull_request_url":"","issue_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/dog/opencode-acp/issues/20","user":{"id":3,"login":"awork","login_name":"","source_id":0,"full_name":"","email":"awork@noreply.localhost","avatar_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/avatars/3a6e67811caadb37b9004123cfec7a13","html_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/awork","language":"","is_admin":false,"last_login":"0001-01-01T00:00:00Z","created":"2026-05-24T14:49:10Z","restricted":false,"active":false,"prohibit_login":false,"location":"","website":"","description":"","visibility":"public","followers_count":0,"following_count":0,"starred_repos_count":0,"username":"awork"},"original_author":"","original_author_id":0,"body":"[system] ✓ Message broadcasted to: **awork** (`ses_0b89319b1ffeK25eKU3GMfCK8U`, `/home/dog/projects/opencode-acp`).","assets":[],"created_at":"2026-07-17T06:07:47Z","updated_at":