rce_id":0,"full_name":"","email":"awork@noreply.localhost","avatar_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/avatars/3a6e67811caadb37b9004123cfec7a13","html_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/awork","language":"","is_admin":false,"last_login":"0001-01-01T00:00:00Z","created":"2026-05-24T14:49:10Z","restricted":false,"active":false,"prohibit_login":false,"location":"","website":"","description":"","visibility":"public","followers_count":0,"following_count":0,"starred_repos_count":0,"username":"awork"},"original_author":"","original_author_id":0,"body":"[system] ✅ **awork** completed (4 min)","assets":[],"created_at":"2026-07-17T07:10:51Z","updated_at":"2026-07-17T07:13:48Z"},{"id":14608,"html_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/dog/opencode-acp/issues/20#issuecomment-14608","pull_request_url":"","issue_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/dog/opencode-acp/issues/20","user":{"id":3,"login":"awork","login_name":"","source_id":0,"full_name":"","email":"awork@noreply.localhost","avatar_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/avatars/3a6e67811caadb37b9004123cfec7a13","html_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/awork","language":"","is_admin":false,"last_login":"0001-01-01T00:00:00Z","created":"2026-05-24T14:49:10Z","restricted":false,"active":false,"prohibit_login":false,"location":"","website":"","description":"","visibility":"public","followers_count":0,"following_count":0,"starred_repos_count":0,"username":"awork"},"original_author":"","original_author_id":0,"body":"[bot] 分析完成。这是 **phantom block 死循环**（GitHub #93），和之前 Trollgeir 报告的 #135 是同一类 bug。\n\n## 死循环时间线\n\n| 压缩# | 块 | 前→后 | 变化 | 判定 |\n|--------|-----|-------|------|------|\n| #3 | b10 | 162.1K→118.2K | −43.9K | ✅ 正常（69条早期消息） |\n| #4 | b11 | 133.4K→112.7K | −20.7K | ✅ 正常（首次压缩 m00106–m00184） |\n| #5 | b12 | 135.3K→**136.7K** | **+1.4K** | ❌ 幽灵块 |\n| #6 | b13 | 111K→**112.3K** | **+1.3K** | ❌ 幽灵块 |\n| #7 | b14 | 109.6K→**110.7K** | **+1.1K** | ❌ 幽灵块 |\n| #8–#13 | b15–b20 | ~109K→**~110K** | **+0.6~1.1K** | ❌ 幽灵块 × 6 |\n| #14 | — | 用户拒绝 | — | \"别压缩了\" |\n\n**最终铁证**（acp_status line 3877）：\n```\nb20  0→1.1K  2m ago  74 msgs  \"green-point改造edit历史\"\n```\n**`0→1.1K`**：原始 0 token 被压缩，1.1K 摘要被添加。这是纯粹的幽灵块。\n\n## 根因分析\n\n### 1. Phantom Block（主因 — GitHub #93 未修）\n\nb11 **合法地**压缩了 m00106–m00184（79条 edit 历史，真实节省 20.7K）。但之后 b12–b20 **重复压缩同一个范围**。此时这些消息已经处于 `active` 状态（被 b11 覆盖），`applyCompressionState` 发现全部已 active → `newlyCompressedMessageIds = []` → 0 token 节省，但**仍然创建新块** → 每次净增 ~1K 摘要。\n\n**缺失的守卫**：PR #148（`checkPhantomBlock`）会在 `newlyCompressedMessageIds` 为空时拒绝创建块。但 PR #148 还没 merge。\n\n### 2. 推荐列表显示已压缩范围（助推因素）\n\nb11 压缩后，下一轮的推荐列表**仍然显示 `m00106–m00184 79 msgs 343.7K compressible`**。模型看到\"343.7K 可压缩\" → 认为还没压缩过 → 再次调用 compress → 幽灵块。\n\n这是因为 `buildCompressibleRanges` 基于**原始 DB 消息**构建范围，而非 prune 后的消息。原始消息仍在 DB 中（只是被标记为 active），范围识别不感知压缩状态。\n\n### 3. Nudge 反馈循环（放大器）\n\n```\ncontext 高 → nudge → compress → 幽灵块 (+1K) → context 更高 → nudge → compress → ...\n```\n\n`filterRecommendedRanges` 看到有效可压缩 = 343.7K（远超 50K 阈值）→ 不抑制推荐 → nudge 继续触发。\n\n### 4. `dangerous: true` 绕过（次要）\n\n模型在第 5 次开始用 `dangerous: true`（line 3392），绕过了最后一段保护。但这里 m00106–m00184 **不是**最后一段（后面还有 m00186+），所以 `dangerous` 实际没起作用——核心问题是幽灵块，不是最后一段保护。\n\n## 为什么模型意识不到已经压缩了？\n\n模型看到 acp_status 里有 b11（`74 msgs`），但在推荐列表里又看到 `m00106–m00184 79 msgs 343.7K compressible`。两个信息矛盾：\n- \"已经有个块覆盖了 74 条消息\"\n- \"但还有 79 条 343.7K 可压缩\"\n\n模型的推理（line 3337）暴露了困惑：*\"b10是之前压缩的，但当前上下文中m00106-m00184仍然可见\"*。它选择相信推荐列表（\"仍然可压缩\"）而非压缩状态（\"已经被 b11 覆盖\"）。\n\n## 修复方案\n\n| 修复 | PR | 状态 | 效果 |\n|------|-----|------|------|\n| `checkPhantomBlock` — 拒绝压缩已 active 的范围 | #148 | **未 merge** | 直接阻止 b12–b20 的创建 |\n| 推荐列表感知压缩状态 | — | **未实现** | 不在推荐中显示已压缩范围 |\n| `no-recs-skip` — 无推荐时抑制 nudge | #147 | ✅ 已 merge 到 master | 但此案中推荐列表非空（有幽灵推荐），所以没触发 |\n\n**最关键的是 PR #148**。它会让 compress #5 直接返回错误：*\"Compression range 1 covers only already-compressed messages (0 new). Remove it from your batch.\"* 模型看到错误后停止重试。\n\n需要我继续推进 PR #148 的 merge 吗？","assets":[],"created_at":"2026-07-17T07:13:37Z","updated_at":"2026-07-17T07:13:37Z"},{"id":14615,"html_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/dog/opencode-acp/issues/20#issuecomment-14615","pull_request_url":"","issue_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/dog/opencode-acp/issues/20","user":{"id":1,"login":"dog","login_name":"","source_id":0,"full_name":"","email":"dog@noreply.localhost","avatar_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/avatars/707bc216f1ab0193186b3712bbd8b1ad","html_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/dog","language":"","is_admin":false,"last_login":"0001-01-01T00:00:00Z","created":"2026-03-23T02:18:35Z","restricted":false,"active":false,"prohibit_login":false,"location":"","website":"","description":"","visibility":"public","followers_count":1,"following_count":0,"starred_repos_count":0,"username":"dog"},"original_author":"","original_author_id":0,"body":"审查 148 代码 看看改动是否正确","assets":[],"created_at":"2026-07-17T07:18:10Z","updated_at":"2026-07-17T07:18:10Z"},{"id":14616,"html_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/dog/opencode-acp/issues/20#issuecomment-14616","pull_request_url":"","issue_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/dog/opencode-acp/issues/20","user":{"id":3,"login":"awork","login_name":"","source_id":0,"full_name":"","email":"awork@noreply.localhost","avatar_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/avatars/3a6e67811caadb37b9004123cfec7a13","html_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/awork","language":"","is_admin":false,"last_login":"0001-01-01T00:00:00Z","created":"2026-05-24T14:49:10Z","restricted":false,"active":false,"prohibit_login":false,"location":"","website":"","description":"","visibility":"public","followers_count":0,"following_count":0,"starred_repos_count":0,"username":"awork"},"original_author":"","original_author_id":0,"body":"[system] ✓ Message broadcasted to: **awork** (`ses_0b89319b1ffeK25eKU3GMfCK8U`, `/home/dog/projects/opencode-acp`).","assets":[],"created_at":"2026-07-17T07:18:11Z","updated_at":"2026-07-17T07:18:11Z"},{"id":14617,"html_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/dog/opencode-acp/issues/20#issuecomment-14617","pull_request_url":"","issue_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/dog/opencode-acp/issues/20","user":{"id":3,"login":"awork","login_name":"","source_id":0,"full_name":"","email":"awork@noreply.localhost","avatar_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/avatars/3a6e67811caadb37b9004123cfec7a13","html_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/awork","language":"","is_admin":false,"last_login":"0001-01-01T00:00:00Z","created":"2026-05-24T14:49:10Z","restricted":false,"active":false,"prohibit_login":false,"location":"","website":"","description":"","visibility":"public","followers_count":0,"following_count":0,"starred_repos_count":0,"username":"awork"},"original_author":"","original_author_id":0,"body":"[system] ✅ **awork** completed (3 min)","assets":[],"created_at":"2026-07-17T07:20:51Z","updated_at":"2026-07-17T07:22:00Z"},{"id":14618,"html_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/dog/opencode-acp/issues/20#issuecomment-14618","pull_request_url":"","issue_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/dog/opencode-acp/issues/20","user":{"id":3,"login":"awork","login_name":"","source_id":0,"full_name":"","email":"awork@noreply.localhost","avatar_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/avatars/3a6e67811caadb37b9004123cfec7a13","html_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/awork","language":"","is_admin":false,"last_login":"0001-01-01T00:00:00Z","created":"2026-05-24T14:49:10Z","restricted":false,"active":false,"prohibit_login":false,"location":"","website":"","description":"","visibility":"public","followers_count":0,"following_count":0,"starred_repos_count":0,"username":"awork"},"original_author":"","original_author_id":0,"body":"[bot] PR #148 审查完成。**代码正确，可以 merge。**\n\n## 审查结论\n\n| 项目 | 结果 |\n|------|------|\n| 代码正确性 | ✅ PASS — 正确镜像 `applyCompressionState` 的 `newlyCompressedMessageIds` 逻辑 |\n| 类型安全 | ✅ 无 `as any`、`@ts-ignore` |\n| 测试 | ✅ 12/12 phantom-block 测试 + 725/725 全量测试通过 |\n| Typecheck | ✅ 0 错误 |\n| Merge 兼容性 | ✅ 与当前 master (e6def12) 无冲突 |\n\n## 核心逻辑验证\n\n`checkPhantomBlock` 的判定标准：\n```typescript\nconst hasNew = [...effective].some((mid) =\u003e {\n    const entry = state.prune.messages.byMessageId.get(mid)\n    return !entry || entry.activeBlockIds.length === 0\n})\n```\n\n对比 `applyCompressionState`（state.ts:246-260）：\n```typescript\nconst wasActive = initiallyActiveMessages.has(messageId)  // activeBlockIds.length \u003e 0 BEFORE\nif (isNowActive \u0026\u0026 !wasActive) → newly compressed\n```\n\n**两者等价**：\n- `!entry` → `applyCompressionState` 会创建新 entry → `wasActive=false` → newly compressed ✓\n- `activeBlockIds.length === 0` → `wasActive=false` → newly compressed ✓\n- `activeBlockIds.length \u003e 0` → `wasActive=true` → NOT newly compressed ✓（phantom）\n\n### Consumed block 场景验证\n\n消息 `m1` 仅 active 于 consumed block 10：\n- **checkPhantomBlock**: `activeBlockIds=[10]`, length\u003e0 → NOT new → 归入 phantom\n- **applyCompressionState**: `initiallyActiveMessages` 包含 m1 → `wasActive=true` → block 10 被 consume 后 m1 转到新块 → `isNowActive=true` → `isNowActive \u0026\u0026 !wasActive` = `true \u0026\u0026 false` → NOT newly compressed\n\n两者一致 ✓ — 消息已经被 block 10 压缩过，重新标记到新块不算\"新压缩\"（避免 token 双重计算）。\n\n### GC'd 消息场景验证\n\n消息 activeBlockIds=[] (块已 GC)：\n- **checkPhantomBlock**: length===0 → IS new → 不阻止压缩 ✓\n- **applyCompressionState**: `wasActive=false` → newly compressed ✓\n\n两者一致 ✓。\n\n## 测试覆盖\n\n12 个测试覆盖了所有核心场景：\n- ✅ 全新消息 → pass\n- ✅ 新+旧混合 → pass\n- ✅ 全已 active → Error\n- ✅ 单条已 active (message mode) → Error\n- ✅ consumed block 全 active → Error\n- ✅ consumed block + 新消息 → pass\n- ✅ active 于非 consumed 块 + 新消息 → pass\n- ✅ 多 plan 批次，任一 phantom → Error（含正确的 range 索引）\n- ✅ 多 plan 批次，全部有效 → pass\n- ✅ 空 plans → pass\n- ✅ GC'd 消息 (empty activeBlockIds) → pass\n- ✅ 错误消息包含 range 索引\n\n**小遗漏**（非阻塞）：缺少多 consumed block（2+ consumedBlockIds）、孤儿 consumedBlockId 引用测试。但核心逻辑已被现有测试充分覆盖。\n\n## 设计问题（非代码 bug）\n\n**Fail-fast vs skip-phantom**：当前实现是 fail-fast — 10 个 plan 中第 3 个是 phantom → 整个批次被拒绝，错误信息只提\"range 3\"。模型需要逐个排除（whack-a-mole）。\n\n但对于实际场景（如 session-ses_0922 的死循环），每次 compress 只有 **1 个 range**，fail-fast 会立即返回错误 → 模型看到\"0 new direct messages\" → 停止重试。**对这个 bug 的修复是有效的。**\n\nskip-phantom-plans 可以作为后续优化——如果未来发现多 plan 批次中混合 phantom 的情况频繁。\n\n## 建议\n\n1. **可以直接 merge**（rebase 到当前 master 无冲突）\n2. **设计优化**（follow-up）：fail-fast → skip-phantom，如果实际使用中发现多 plan 场景","assets":[],"created_at":"2026-07-17T07:21:49Z","updated_at":"2026-07-17T07:21:49Z"},{"id":14622,"html_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/dog/opencode-acp/issues/20#issuecomment-14622","pull_request_url":"","issue_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/dog/opencode-acp/issues/20","user":{"id":1,"login":"dog","login_name":"","source_id":0,"full_name":"","email":"dog@noreply.localhost","avatar_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/avatars/707bc216f1ab0193186b3712bbd8b1ad","html_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/dog","language":"","is_admin":false,"last_login":"0001-01-01T00:00:00Z","created":"2026-03-23T02:18:35Z","restricted":false,"active":false,"prohibit_login":false,"location":"","website":"","description":"","visibility":"public","followers_count":1,"following_count":0,"starred_repos_count":0,"username":"dog"},"original_author":"","original_author_id":0,"body":"安装到本地","assets":[],"created_at":"2026-07-17T11:58:41Z","updated_at":"2026-07-17T11:58:41Z"},{"id":14623,"html_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/dog/opencode-acp/issues/20#issuecomment-14623","pull_request_url":"","issue_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/dog/opencode-acp/issues/20","user":{"id":3,"login":"awork","login_name":"","source_id":0,"full_name":"","email":"awork@noreply.localhost","avatar_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/avatars/3a6e67811caadb37b9004123cfec7a13","html_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/awork","language":"","is_admin":false,"last_login":"0001-01-01T00:00:00Z","created":"2026-05-24T14:49:10Z","restricted":false,"active":false,"prohibit_login":false,"location":"","website":"","description":"","visibility":"public","followers_count":0,"following_count":0,"starred_repos_count":0,"username":"awork"},"original_author":"","original_author_id":0,"body":"[system] ✓ Message broadcasted to: **awork** (`ses_0