新版直接不显示了。**这就是你说的\"没有了\"——它们被 filter 完全排除了。**\n\n## 是问题吗？\n\n从压缩角度：**不是 bug**。最后一段是当前 turn，不应该被压缩。排除它是正确的。\n\n从透明度角度：**是 UX 回归**。旧版让你看到所有范围 + 标注，你能自己判断。新版替你做了决定，但你不知道少了什么。\n\n## 如果要改\n\n两个选项：\n1. **恢复可见性**：被过滤的范围也显示，但标注 `⚠️ excluded: last segment, too recent`。模型看到但不推荐压缩。\n2. **加一行汇总**：在推荐列表末尾加 `💡 N ranges excluded by filter (last segment, \u003c 100K). Use acp_status to see all.`\n\n要改吗？","assets":[],"created_at":"2026-07-17T12:43:17Z","updated_at":"2026-07-17T12:43:17Z"},{"id":14645,"html_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/dog/opencode-acp/issues/20#issuecomment-14645","pull_request_url":"","issue_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/dog/opencode-acp/issues/20","user":{"id":1,"login":"dog","login_name":"","source_id":0,"full_name":"","email":"dog@noreply.localhost","avatar_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/avatars/707bc216f1ab0193186b3712bbd8b1ad","html_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/dog","language":"","is_admin":false,"last_login":"0001-01-01T00:00:00Z","created":"2026-03-23T02:18:35Z","restricted":false,"active":false,"prohibit_login":false,"location":"","website":"","description":"","visibility":"public","followers_count":1,"following_count":0,"starred_repos_count":0,"username":"dog"},"original_author":"","original_author_id":0,"body":"前面的分支合并了，再发一个小版本。","assets":[],"created_at":"2026-07-17T14:09:46Z","updated_at":"2026-07-17T14:09:46Z"},{"id":14646,"html_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/dog/opencode-acp/issues/20#issuecomment-14646","pull_request_url":"","issue_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/dog/opencode-acp/issues/20","user":{"id":3,"login":"awork","login_name":"","source_id":0,"full_name":"","email":"awork@noreply.localhost","avatar_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/avatars/3a6e67811caadb37b9004123cfec7a13","html_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/awork","language":"","is_admin":false,"last_login":"0001-01-01T00:00:00Z","created":"2026-05-24T14:49:10Z","restricted":false,"active":false,"prohibit_login":false,"location":"","website":"","description":"","visibility":"public"