iginal_author_id":0,"body":"[bot] 已创建 v1.12.8 发布 PR：https://github.com/ranxianglei/opencode-acp/pull/152\n\n## 内容\n\n**PR #148 — 幽灵块拒绝（`checkPhantomBlock`）**\n\n在 `applyCompressionState` 之前增加无状态前置检查，镜像其 `newlyCompressedMessageIds` 计算：如果计划中所有消息都已被活跃块覆盖（即没有\"新\"消息），整个 compress 调用在状态变异前被拒绝。\n\n这直接修复了 #93/#135 的死亡循环：模型对已压缩范围调用 compress 不再产生 0-token 幽灵块。\n\n## 验证\n\n- typecheck: 0 errors\n- tests: **737/737 pass**（比 v1.12.7 多 12 个 phantom-block 测试，随 PR #148 合入 master）\n- build: 401 KB\n- `scripts/ci/check-pr.sh`: 全部通过 ✓\n\n## 合并后\n\nCI `release.yml` 自动打 `v1.12.8` tag、发布到 npm `latest`、创建 GitHub Release。等 CI 绿了就可以 merge。","assets":[],"created_at":"2026-07-17T14:14:14Z","updated_at":"2026-07-17T14:14:14Z"},{"id":14654,"html_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/dog/opencode-acp/issues/20#issuecomment-14654","pull_request_url":"","issue_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/dog/opencode-acp/issues/20","user":{"id":1,"login":"dog","login_name":"","source_id":0,"full_name":"","email":"dog@noreply.localhost","avatar_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/avatars/707bc216f1ab0193186b3712bbd8b1ad","html_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/dog","language":"","is_admin":false,"last_login":"0001-01-01T00:00:00Z","created":"2026-03-23T02:18:35Z","restricted":false,"active":false,"prohibit_login":false,"location":"","website":"","description":"","visibility":"public","followers_count":1,"following_count":0,"starred_repos_count":0,"username":"dog"},"original_author":"","original_author_id":0,"body":"https://github.com/ranxianglei/opencode-acp/pull/138 前面已经合并了，你看一下这个 有没有问题","assets":[],"created_at":"2026-07-17T14:25:41Z","updated_at":"2026-07-17T14:25:41Z"},{"id":14655,"html_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/dog/opencode-acp/issues/20#issuecomment-14655","pull_request_url":"","issue_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/dog/opencode-acp/issues/20","user":{"id":3,"login":"awork","login_name":"","source_id":0,"full_name":"","email":"awork@noreply.localhost","avatar_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/avatars/3a6e67811caadb