"0001-01-01T00:00:00Z","created":"2026-05-24T14:49:10Z","restricted":false,"active":false,"prohibit_login":false,"location":"","website":"","description":"","visibility":"public","followers_count":0,"following_count":0,"starred_repos_count":0,"username":"awork"},"original_author":"","original_author_id":0,"body":"[bot] 审查了 PR #138（`feat: remove GC mechanism, compress-as-anchor, emergency pruning`）。\n\n## 概要\n\nPR #138 是一个**重大架构变更**（45 文件，+370/-2226 行），基于 `101a741`（v1.12.5 之前的 master），与 v1.12.6–v1.12.8 的大量工作冲突。\n\n三个核心改动：\n1. **完全移除 GC**（`gc/truncate.ts` + `gc/merge.ts` 删除）\n2. **移除 synthetic recap 注入**（`filterCompressedRanges` 不再注入 `createSyntheticToolRecap`），改为 compress 工具调用本身作为锚点\n3. **新增 emergency-prune**（`lib/messages/emergency-prune.ts`，95% 阈值时裁剪工具输出）\n\n## 架构评估\n\n### ✅ 正确的部分\n\n1. **GC 移除**：合理。GC 在截断摘要（有价值的蒸馏）而非工具输出（占大头），方向错误。移除后简化了大量代码。\n\n2. **sync.ts 改动**：用 `compressMessageId ?? anchorMessageId` 作为失活判断 — 正确。`compressMessageId` 在 `range.ts:291` / `message.ts:209` 通过 `toolCtx.messageID` 设置，向后兼容老状态。\n\n3. **emergency-prune 逻辑**：阈值 95% → 目标 85%，按优先级裁剪（工具输出优先，摘要最后），跳过受保护工具。逻辑正确。\n\n### ⚠️ 关键问题\n\n**问题 1：ref 泄漏重新引入（与 v1.12.7 PR #150 冲突）**\n\nPR #138 移除了 `stripStaleCompressCalls`，让 compress 工具调用保持可见。但 compress 工具调用的 **input 包含 `startId: \"m00106\"`, `endId: \"m00184\"`** — 这正是 v1.12.7 PR #150 修复的 ref 泄漏问题！\n\n- **v1.12.x 方案**：compress 调用被剥离 + synthetic recap 只显示 `messages: \u003ccount\u003e`\n- **PR #138 方案**：compress 调用保持可见 → 模型看到 `startId`/`endId` ref → 尝试重新压缩 → phantom block\n\n`checkPhantomBlock`（v1.12.8 PR #148）会拒绝 phantom block，但每次拒绝都浪费一次 API 调用。**当前 v1.12.x 方案在这个问题上更优**。\n\n**问题 2：emergency-prune 原地变异（Bug 38 模式）**\n\n`emergency-prune.ts:73`: `part.state.output = EMERGENCY_PRUNE_STUB` — 原地变异工具输出，这正是 Bug 38（破坏 GLM prefix cache）的模式。95%+ 阈值下可以接受（cache 本身已失效），但应加注释说明。\n\n**问题 3：rebase 复杂度高**\n\nPR #138 基于 v1.12.5 之前的 master，之后 master 新增了：\n- v1.12.6（stale anchor fix）→ inject.ts\n- v1.12.7（smart filter + ref-leak + phantom turn）→ hooks.ts, prune.ts, inject.ts, utils.ts\n- v1.12.8（phantom block）→ pipeline.ts, range.ts, message.ts\n\n如果合并 PR #138，以下 v1.12.7 工作变成**死代码**：\n- ref-leak fix（`computeBlockCoverage`）→ 不再有 recap 注入\n- `createSyntheticToolRecap` 的 `messageCount` 参数改动 → 不再调用\n- `system.ts` COMPRESSION SUMMARIES 段落 → 需要重写\n\n**问题 4：无摘要裁剪逃生阀**\n\nGC 移除后，如果工具输出已被 emergency-prune 裁完但 context 仍 \u003e95%，emergency-prune 无法继续（只裁工具输出）。嵌套压缩是唯一出路，但依赖模型主动调用 compress。\n\n## 结论\n\nPR #138 的 compress-as-anchor 方案**架构上有创意**，但与 v1.12.x 线冲突严重。移除 `stripStaleCompressCalls` 重新引入了 v1.12.7 刚修复的 ref 泄漏问题。\n\n**建议**：\n1. **emergency-prune 模块**可以独立提取为一个单独 PR — 这部分与现有架构兼容，价值明确\n2. **compress-as-anchor 方向**需要更多评估 — 如果要走这条路，需要同时保留 `stripStaleCompressCalls` 或找到替代方案防止 ref 泄漏\n3. **不建议直接 merge** — 需要 rebase 到当��� master + 解决 ref 泄漏冲突\n\n要我先提取 emergency-prune 作为独立 PR 吗？还是你有其他想法？","assets":[],"created_at":"2026-07-17T14:29:43Z","updated_at":"2026-07-17T14:29:43Z"},{"id":14661,"html_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/dog/opencode-acp/issues/20#issuecomment-14661","pull_request_url":"","issue_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/dog/opencode-acp/issues/20","user":{"id":1,"login":"dog","login_name":"","source_id":0,"full_name":"","email":"dog@noreply.localhost","avatar_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/avatars/707bc216f1ab0193186b3712bbd8b1ad","html_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/dog","language":"","is_admin":false,"last_login":"0001-01-01T00:00:00Z","created":"2026-03-23T02:18:35Z","restricted":false,"active":false,"prohibit_login":false,"location":"","website":"","description":"","visibility":"public","followers_count":1,"following_count":0,"starred_repos_count":0,"username":"dog"},"original_author":"","original_author_id":0,"body":"我理解这个，可以只提一个问题，其他的都不管。这个问题主要就是我们在压缩的时候会把这个工具叫compress工具，然后有输入有输出，但是后面会把这个工具隐藏掉，然后会发送一个消息。这个消息用来作为模型的上下文。\n\n这样就会导致一些问题。虽然这个消息是一个工具调用的消息，但是它只有输入没有输出。我忘记还是没有输出，还是只有输入了\n\n所以你看是不是只集成了一个功能？你可以新开分支搞这个。先对齐一下","assets":[],"created_at":"2026-07-17T14:33:11Z","updated_at":"2026-07-17T14:33:11Z"},{"id":14662,"html_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/dog/opencode-acp/issues/20#issuecomment-14662","pull_request_url":"","issue_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/dog/opencode-acp/issues/20","user":{"id":3,"login":"awork","login_name":"","source_id":0,"full_name":"","email":"awork@noreply.localhost","avatar_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/avatars/3a6e67811caadb37b9004123cfec7a13","html_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/awork","language":"","is_admin":false,"last_login":"0001-01-01T00:00:00Z","created":"2026-05-24T14:49:10Z","restricted":false,"active":false,"prohibit_login":false,"location":"","website":"","description":"","visibility":"public","followers_count":0,"following_count":0,"starred_repos_count":0,"username":"awork"},"original_author":"","original_author_id":0,"body":"[system] ✓ Message broadcasted to: **awork** (`ses_0b89319b1ffeK25eKU3GMfCK8U`, `/home/dog/projects/opencode-acp`).","assets":[],"created_at":"2026-07-17T14:33:12Z","updated_at":"2026-07-17T14:33:12Z"},{"id":14663,"html_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/dog/opencode-acp/issues/20#issuecomment-14663","pull_request_url":"","issue_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/dog/opencode-acp/issues/20","user":{"id":3,"login":"awork","login_name":"","source_id":0,"full_name":"","email":"awork@noreply.localhost","avatar_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/avatars/3a6e67811caadb37b9004123cfec7a13","html_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/awork","language":"","is_admin":false,"last_login":"0001-01-01T00:00:00Z","created":"2026-05-24T14:49:10Z","restricted":false,"active":false,"prohibit_login":false,"location":"","website":"","description":"","visibility":"public","followers_count":0,"following_count":0,"starred_repos_count":0,"username":"awork"},"original_author":"","original_author_id":0,"body":"[bot] 对齐一下我的理解：\n\n## 问题\n\n当前流程：\n1. 模型调用 `compress` → assistant 消息（tool-call，input=summary）+ tool result（output=确认信息）✓ 结构完整\n2. `stripStaleCompressCalls` 把旧的 compress 工具调用**剥离掉**\n3. `filterCompressedRanges` 注入一个 **synthetic recap**（`createSyntheticToolRecap`）\n\n问题出在第 3 步。synthetic recap 是一个 AssistantMessage，里面只有一个 ToolPart（`type:\"tool\"`, `state.status:\"completed\"`），tool 名是 `acp_context_recap`。虽然 state 里同时有 `input` 和 `output`，但它是**单条 assistant 消息**——不是一个标准的 tool-call + tool-result 对。\n\n你说的\"只有输入没有输出\"——我理解你的意思是：模型看到的不是一个正常的\"assistant 调了工具 → tool 返回结果\"的对话结构，而是一个结构不完整的消息。这会让模型困惑。\n\n## PR #138 对这个问题的修复\n\n是的，PR #138 对这个问题就集成了**一个功能**：\n\n1. **移除 `stripStaleCompressCalls`** → compress 工具调用保持可见\n2. **移除 `filterCompressedRanges` 的 recap 注入** → 不再有 synthetic 消息\n3. compress 工具调用**本身就是摘要锚点**——它的 input 包含 summary，output 包含确认信息，结构天然完整\n\nGC 移除和 emergency-prune 是独立的，不在这次范围内。\n\n## 新分支范围\n\n只改这一个：\n- `lib/hooks.ts`：移除 `stripStaleCompressCalls` 调用 + import\n- `lib/messages/prune.ts`：移除 recap 注入 + `stripStaleCompressCalls` 函数 + `createSyntheticToolRecap` import\n- `lib/messages/sync.ts`：失活判断改用 `compressMessageId`（因为 compress 调用不再被剥离，用它的 messageId 做锚点）\n- 测试：更新 `prune.test.ts`、`e2e-message-transform.test.ts` 等\n\n理解对吗？确认后我切分支。","assets":[],"created_at":"2026-07-17T14:35:27Z","updated_at":"2026-07-17T14:35:27Z"},{"id":14670,"html_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/dog/opencode-acp/issues/20#issuecomment-14670","pull_request_url":"","issue_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/dog/opencode-acp/issues/20","user":{"id":1,"login":"dog","login_name":"","source_id":0,"full_name":"","email":"dog@noreply.localhost","avatar_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/avatars/707bc216f1ab0193186b3712bbd8b1ad","html_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/dog","language":"","is_admin":false,"last_login":"0001-01-01T00:00:00Z","created":"2026-03-23T02:18:35Z","restricted":false,"active":false,"prohibit_login":false,"location":"","website":"","description":"","visibility":"public","followers_count":1,"following_count":0,"starred_repos_count":0,"username":"dog"},"original_author":"","original_author_id":0,"body":"对，就只做最小化改动量保定可以切分支搞","assets":[],"created_at":"2026-07-17T14:39:02Z","updated_at":"2026-07-17T14:39:02Z"},{"id":14671,"html_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/dog/opencode-acp/iss