ecap**：只在 transform hook 内存中生成，从未持久化。升级后自动消失，不需要迁移。\n- **旧 compress 工具调用**：仍在 DB 中。活跃块的调用自然显示为锚点。被消费块的调用由 `filterCompressedRanges` 隐藏（和其他被压缩消息一样的机制）。\n- **过渡**：跨版本的长会话，模型看到的 summary 内容不变，只是交付格式从 synthetic recap 变成真实 tool 调用。无缝。\n\n## 4. 顺带验证\n\n- 部署版本：**v1.12.9** ✓\n- `createSyntheticToolRecap` / `stripStaleCompressCalls` / `ACP_RECAP_TOOL_NAME` 在 bundle 中 **0 匹配** ✓\n- 旧的 `acp_context_recap` 作为**模型可调用手动查询工具**仍然注册（正确，与已移除的自动注入是两回事）","assets":[],"created_at":"2026-07-17T15:22:41Z","updated_at":"2026-07-17T15:22:41Z"},{"id":14685,"html_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/dog/opencode-acp/issues/20#issuecomment-14685","pull_request_url":"","issue_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/dog/opencode-acp/issues/20","user":{"id":1,"login":"dog","login_name":"","source_id":0,"full_name":"","email":"dog@noreply.localhost","avatar_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/avatars/707bc216f1ab0193186b3712bbd8b1ad","html_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/dog","language":"","is_admin":false,"last_login":"0001-01-01T00:00:00Z","created":"2026-03-23T02:18:35Z","restricted":false,"active":false,"prohibit_login":false,"location":"","website":"","description":"","visibility":"public","followers_count":1,"following_count":0,"starred_repos_count":0,"username":"dog"},"original_author":"","original_author_id":0,"body":"你自己刚刚压缩过，你检查一下你的结果是否正常。另外如果是在压缩块的基础上继续压缩会产生什么呢？我们这个有兼容吗","assets":[],"created_at":"2026-07-17T15:24:30Z","updated_at":"2026-07-17T15:24:30Z"},{"id":14686,"html_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/dog/opencode-acp/issues/20#issuecomment-14686","pull_request_url":"","issue_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/dog/opencode-acp/issues/20","user":{"id":3,"login":"awork","login_name":"","source_id":0,"full_name":"","email":"awork@noreply.localhost","avatar_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/avatars/3a6e67811caadb37b9004123cfec7a13","html_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/awork","language":"","is_admin":false,"last_login":"0001-01-01T00:00:00Z","created":"2026-05-24T14:49:10Z","restricted":false,"active":false,"proh