K chars）、m00033（34K chars）、m00010（32K chars）\n\n### 结论\n\nACP 的 `chars/4` 估算系统性低估约 12%。如果需要更精确的计数，可以用 `@anthropic-ai/tokenizer`（ACP 内部已用，但只用于 `token-utils.ts` 的 `countMessageTokens`，没用于 breakdown 展示）。要不要我改成用真实 tokenizer 来报 breakdown？","assets":[],"created_at":"2026-07-18T00:37:33Z","updated_at":"2026-07-18T00:37:33Z"},{"id":14785,"html_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/dog/opencode-acp/issues/20#issuecomment-14785","pull_request_url":"","issue_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/dog/opencode-acp/issues/20","user":{"id":1,"login":"dog","login_name":"","source_id":0,"full_name":"","email":"dog@noreply.localhost","avatar_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/avatars/707bc216f1ab0193186b3712bbd8b1ad","html_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/dog","language":"","is_admin":false,"last_login":"0001-01-01T00:00:00Z","created":"2026-03-23T02:18:35Z","restricted":false,"active":false,"prohibit_login":false,"location":"","website":"","description":"","visibility":"public","followers_count":1,"following_count":0,"starred_repos_count":0,"username":"dog"},"original_author":"","original_author_id":0,"body":"已经合并了，你再发一个小版本。","assets":[],"created_at":"2026-07-18T04:17:24Z","updated_at":"2026-07-18T04:17:24Z"},{"id":14786,"html_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/dog/opencode-acp/issues/20#issuecomment-14786","pull_request_url":"","issue_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/dog/opencode-acp/issues/20","user":{"id":3,"login":"awork","login_name":"","source_id":0,"full_name":"","email":"awork@noreply.localhost","avatar_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/avatars/3a6e67811caadb37b9004123cfec7a13","html_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/awork","language":"","is_admin":false,"last_login":"0001-01-01T00:00:00Z","created":"2026-05-24T14:49:10Z","restricted":false,"active":false,"prohibit_login":false,"location":"","website":"","description":"","visibility":"public","followers_count":0,"following_count":0,"starred_repos_count":0,"username":"awork"},"original_author":"","original_author_id":0,"body":"[system] ✓ Message bro