_url":"","issue_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/dog/opencode-acp/issues/20","user":{"id":3,"login":"awork","login_name":"","source_id":0,"full_name":"","email":"awork@noreply.localhost","avatar_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/avatars/3a6e67811caadb37b9004123cfec7a13","html_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/awork","language":"","is_admin":false,"last_login":"0001-01-01T00:00:00Z","created":"2026-05-24T14:49:10Z","restricted":false,"active":false,"prohibit_login":false,"location":"","website":"","description":"","visibility":"public","followers_count":0,"following_count":0,"starred_repos_count":0,"username":"awork"},"original_author":"","original_author_id":0,"body":"[bot] 只剩 2 个 open PR：\n\n| PR | 标题 | 状态 | 说明 |\n|---|---|---|---|\n| **#82** | design: batch sweep + age-based protection (v2) | ✅ MERGEABLE | 纯设计文档（3 devlog 文件，0 代码），可直接合 |\n| **#127** | feat: batch compress + cooldown rate-limit | ❌ CONFLICTING | 23 文件，8 commits，与 v1.12.7–v1.12.9 核心改动冲突 |\n\n**详细分析**:\n\n**PR #82** — 维护者 @dog 确认的 v2 设计。两个特性：A) age-based protection（旧内容压缩后可被 GC 截断，新内容保护期）；B) batch sweep（批量扫描可压缩范围）。纯文档，无代码改动，合了就是存档设计决策。\n\n**PR #127** — batch compress interface + cooldown。这个 PR 基于 v1.12.6 之前的代码，23 个文件，跟后续的 phantom block fix (PR #148)、compress-as-anchor (PR #153)、token classification (PR #155)、decompress range mode (PR #73) 都有冲突。功能本身（批量压缩 + 冷却限速）是好的，但需要完全重做——基于当前 master 重新实现。\n\n**建议**:\n1. PR #82 直接合（设计文档归档）\n2. PR #127 关掉，需要时基于当前 master 重新开 PR\n\n要继续处理哪个？","assets":[],"created_at":"2026-07-18T12:17:37Z","updated_at":"2026-07-18T12:17:37Z"},{"id":14951,"html_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/dog/opencode-acp/issues/20#issuecomment-14951","pull_request_url":"","issue_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/dog/opencode-acp/issues/20","user":{"id":1,"login":"dog","login_name":"","source_id":0,"full_name":"","email":"dog@noreply.localhost","avatar_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/avatars/707bc216f1ab0193186b3712bbd8b1ad","html_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/dog","language":"","is_admin":false,"last_login":"0001-01-01T00:00:00Z","created":"2026-03-23T02:18:35Z","restricted":false,"active":false,"prohibit_login":false,"location":"","website":"","description":"","visibility":"public","followers_count":1,"following_count":0,"starred_repos_count":0,"username":"dog"},"original_author":"","original_author_id":0,"body":"这个两个，我觉得只有那个批量压缩是有意义的。所谓批量压缩，其实现在压缩的时候只能传一个 Topic，一个 Topic 里面有很多子项。但是模型有可能有的时候，他看推荐列表特别多，他要分几次压缩才行。但是他压完以后，再要去压的时候，我们已经没有那个压缩提示了。这个时候他就可能不知道要压哪些，随便压一些。所以说最好让模型一次性全都压完。\n\n这样的话避免两个极端。第一个极端就是他直接只压其中的一个 Topic，后面的就随便压不管了。第二个极端就是他为了一次性能压完，他就把所有的 Topic 不相关的压到一起了，这样就会降低压缩的一个效果。\n\n我理解你可以单独开分支完成这个，你看可行不可行？","assets":[],"created_at":"2026-07-18T12:22:33Z","updated_at":"2026-07-18T12:22:33Z"},{"id":14952,"html_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/dog/opencode-acp/issues/20#issuecomment-14952","pull_request_url":"","issue_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/dog/opencode-acp/issues/20","user":{"id":3,"login":"awork","login_name":"","source_id":0,"full_name":"","email":"awork@noreply.localhost","avatar_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/avatars/3a6e67811caadb37b9004123cfec7a13","html_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/awork","language":"","is_admin":false,"last_login":"0001-01-01T00:00:00Z","created":"2026-05-24T14:49:10Z","restricted":false,"active":false,"prohibit_login":false,"location":"","website":"","description":"","visibility":"public","followers_count":0,"following_count":0,"starred_repos_count":0,"username":"awork"},"original_author":"","original_author_id":0,"body":"[system] ✓ Message broadcasted to: **awork** (`ses_0b89319b1ffeK25eKU3GMfCK8U`, `/home/dog/projects/opencode-acp`).","assets":[],"created_at":"2026-07-18T12:22:33Z","updated_at":"2026-07-18T12:22:33Z"},{"id":14953,"html_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/dog/opencode-acp/issues/20#issuecomment-14953","pull_request_url":"","issue_url":"http://192.168.10.96:3300/dog/opencode-acp/issues/20","user":{"id":3,"login":"awork","login_name":"","source_id":0,"full_name":"","email":"awork@noreply.localhost","avatar_url":"http: